msgid "<bookmark_value>Help; extended tips on/off</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>extended tips in Help</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>tips;extended tips in Help</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>tooltips;extended tips</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>activating;extended help tips</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ; ເປີດ/ປິດ ຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມໃນຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຄຳແນະນຳ; ຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມໃນຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>tooltip; ຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການເປີດໃຊ້; ຄຳແນະນຳຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອເພີ່ມເຕີມ</bookmark_value>"

#. syrD2
#: active_help_on_off.xhp
msgctxt ""
"active_help_on_off.xhp\n"
"hd_id3156414\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"active_help_on_off\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/active_help_on_off.xhp\">Turning Extended Tips On and Off</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"active_help_on_off\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/active_help_on_off.xhp\">ການເປີດ ແລະ ປິດຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມ</link></variable>"

#. Q57zF
#: active_help_on_off.xhp
msgctxt ""
"active_help_on_off.xhp\n"
"par_id3157958\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Extended tips</emph> provide a brief description of the function of a particular icon, text box or menu command when you rest your cursor on that item."
msgstr "<emph>ຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມ</emph> ຈະໃຫ້ລາຍລະອຽດສັ້ນໆກ່ຽວກັບຟັງຊັນຂອງໄອຄອນໃດໜຶ່ງ, ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ຄຳສັ່ງເມນູ ເມື່ອທ່ານວາງເຄີເຊີໄວ້ເທິງລາຍການນັ້ນ."

#. BpAEj
#: active_help_on_off.xhp
msgctxt ""
"active_help_on_off.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155339\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To turn Extended Tips on and off:"
msgstr "ວິທີການເປີດ ແລະ ປິດຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມ:"

#. WcXBt
#: active_help_on_off.xhp
msgctxt ""
"active_help_on_off.xhp\n"
"par_id3154823\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME - General</emph>, and check <emph>Extended tips</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ສິ່ງທີ່ມັກ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME - ທົ່ວໄປ</emph>, ແລະ ໝາຍເອົາ <emph>ຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມ</emph>."

#. Efdny
#: active_help_on_off.xhp
msgctxt ""
"active_help_on_off.xhp\n"
"par_id3149398\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A check mark indicates that the extended tips are activated."
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຖືກສະແດງວ່າໄດ້ເປີດໃຊ້ຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມແລ້ວ."

#. KaXUm
#: active_help_on_off.xhp
msgctxt ""
"active_help_on_off.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149811\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To turn Extended Tips on temporarily:"
msgstr "ວິທີການເປີດຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມຊົ່ວຄາວ:"

#. jjAmg
#: active_help_on_off.xhp
msgctxt ""
"active_help_on_off.xhp\n"
"par_id3153541\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press the shortcut keys Shift+F1 to activate extended tips once."
msgstr "ກົດປຸ່ມລັດ Shift+F1 ເພື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມໜຶ່ງຄັ້ງ."

#. GjoTE
#: active_help_on_off.xhp
msgctxt ""
"active_help_on_off.xhp\n"
"par_id3153825\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A question mark appears beside the mouse pointer. You can move this <emph>Help Mouse Pointer</emph> over all controls, icons and menu commands to obtain a description of the command. The <emph>Help Mouse Pointer</emph> is disabled the next time you click the mouse."
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳຖາມຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນຂ້າງຕົວຊີ້ເມົາສ໌. ທ່ານສາມາດຍ້າຍ <emph>ຕົວຊີ້ເມົາສ໌ຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ</emph> ນີ້ໄປເທິງທຸກການຄວບຄຸມ, ໄອຄອນ ແລະ ຄຳສັ່ງເມນູ ເພື່ອອ່ານລາຍລະອຽດຂອງຄຳສັ່ງນັ້ນ. <emph>ຕົວຊີ້ເມົາສ໌ຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ</emph> ຈະຖືກປິດໃຊ້ງານເມື່ອທ່ານຄລິກເມົາສ໌ໃນຄັ້ງຕໍ່ໄປ."

#. nnk23
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "ActiveX Control to Display Documents in Internet Explorer"
msgstr "ການຄວບຄຸມ ActiveX ເພື່ອສະແດງເອກະສານໃນ Internet Explorer"

#. fD6Kr
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"bm_id3143267\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>ActiveX control</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>installing;ActiveX control</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>Internet; Internet Explorer for displaying $[officename] documents</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>$[officename] documents;viewing and editing in Internet Explorer</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>viewing;%PRODUCTNAME documents in Internet Explorer</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>editing;%PRODUCTNAME documents in Internet Explorer</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການຄວບຄຸມ ActiveX</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການຕິດຕັ້ງ; ການຄວບຄຸມ ActiveX</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ອິນເຕີເນັດ; Internet Explorer ສຳລັບສະແດງເອກະສານ $[officename]</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ເອກະສານ $[officename]; ການເບິ່ງ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂໃນ Internet Explorer</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການເບິ່ງ; ເອກະສານ %PRODUCTNAME ໃນ Internet Explorer</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການແກ້ໄຂ; ເອກະສານ %PRODUCTNAME ໃນ Internet Explorer</bookmark_value>"

#. gYmyS
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"hd_id3143267\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"activex\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/activex.xhp\">ActiveX Control to Display Documents in Internet Explorer</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"activex\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/activex.xhp\">ການຄວບຄຸມ ActiveX ເພື່ອສະແດງເອກະສານໃນ Internet Explorer</link></variable>"

#. tSxBG
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3166410\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Under Windows only, you can view any $[officename] document in a window of the Microsoft Internet Explorer. Install the ActiveX control in the $[officename] Setup program."
msgstr "ສະເພາະໃນ Windows ເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ທ່ານສາມາດເບິ່ງເອກະສານ $[officename] ໃດໜຶ່ງໃນໜ້າຕ່າງຂອງ Microsoft Internet Explorer. ຕິດຕັ້ງການຄວບຄຸມ ActiveX ໃນໂປຣແກຣມຕິດຕັ້ງ $[officename]."

#. sBkWq
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"hd_id3156346\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Installing the ActiveX control"
msgstr "ການຕິດຕັ້ງການຄວບຄຸມ ActiveX"

#. QMuag
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3153821\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Close $[officename] and the Quickstarter."
msgstr "ປິດ $[officename] ແລະ Quickstarter."

#. BYuEA
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3150771\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the Start button on the Windows taskbar. Choose <emph>Settings</emph>."
msgstr "ຄລິກປຸ່ມ Start ໃນແຖບວຽກຂອງ Windows. ເລືອກ <emph>ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ</emph>."

#. u7g6Z
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_idN106E8\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In Settings, click <emph>Apps</emph>."
msgstr "ໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່າ, ຄລິກ <emph>ແອັບ</emph>."

#. 3UNE4
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3156155\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Apps & features</emph> list, click %PRODUCTNAME, then click <emph>Change</emph>."
msgstr "ໃນລາຍຊື່ <emph>ແອັບ ແລະ ຄຸນສົມບັດ</emph>, ຄລິກ %PRODUCTNAME, ແລ້ວຄລິກ <emph>ປ່ຽນແປງ</emph>."

#. CaXPY
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_idN10706\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the Installation Wizard, select <emph>Modify</emph>."
msgstr "ໃນຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງການຕິດຕັ້ງ, ເລືອກ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂ (Modify)</emph>."

#. cuFZi
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3159399\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open the <emph>Optional Components</emph> entry and find the <emph>ActiveX Control</emph> entry. Open the sub menu of the icon and select to install the feature."
msgstr "ເປີດລາຍການ <emph>ສ່ວນປະກອບເສີມ (Optional Components)</emph> ແລະ ຊອກຫາລາຍການ <emph>ການຄວບຄຸມ ActiveX</emph>. ເປີດເມນູຍ່ອຍຂອງໄອຄອນ ແລະ ເລືອກເພື່ອຕິດຕັ້ງຄຸນສົມບັດ."

#. eJA5C
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3153561\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click <emph>Next</emph> and <emph>Install</emph>."
msgstr "ຄລິກ <emph>ຖັດໄປ</emph> ແລະ <emph>ຕິດຕັ້ງ</emph>."

#. zFGAh
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"hd_id3151384\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Viewing $[officename] documents"
msgstr "ການເບິ່ງເອກະສານ $[officename]"

#. 3Dr4e
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3149669\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In Internet Explorer, browse to a web page that contains a link to a $[officename] Writer document, for example."
msgstr "ໃນ Internet Explorer, ໄປທີ່ໜ້າເວັບທີ່ມີລິ້ງໄປຫາເອກະສານ $[officename] Writer ເປັນຕົວຢ່າງ."

#. uwxNF
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3148550\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the link to view the document in the Internet Explorer window."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ລິ້ງເພື່ອເບິ່ງເອກະສານໃນໜ້າຕ່າງ Internet Explorer."

#. J7s8u
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3154072\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You may still right-click the link to save the file on your harddisk."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດຄລິກຂວາທີ່ລິ້ງເພື່ອບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ລົງໃນຮາດດິດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. AKWH5
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153361\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Editing $[officename] documents"
msgstr "ການແກ້ໄຂເອກະສານ $[officename]"

#. f5aH7
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3154367\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The $[officename] document inside the Internet Explorer shows a set of read-only toolbar icons."
msgstr "ເອກະສານ $[officename] ພາຍໃນ Internet Explorer ຈະສະແດງຊຸດໄອຄອນແຖບເຄື່ອງມືແບບອ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງດຽວ."

#. QCshc
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3148451\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the <emph>Edit file</emph> icon in the document's toolbar to open a copy of the document in a new $[officename] window."
msgstr "ຄລິກໄອຄອນ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂໄຟລ໌</emph> ໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມືຂອງເອກະສານເພື່ອເປີດສຳເນົາຂອງເອກະສານໃນໜ້າຕ່າງ $[officename] ໃໝ່."

#. miAna
#: activex.xhp
msgctxt ""
"activex.xhp\n"
"par_id3144760\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Edit the copy of the document."
msgstr "ແກ້ໄຂສຳເນົາຂອງເອກະສານ."

#. MaKia
#: assistive.xhp
msgctxt ""
"assistive.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Assistive Tools in $[officename]"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອໃນ $[officename]"

#. vxKJG
#: assistive.xhp
msgctxt ""
"assistive.xhp\n"
"bm_id3147399\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>accessibility; $[officename] assistive technology</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>assistive technology in $[officename]</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>screen readers</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>screen magnifiers</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>magnifiers</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການເຂົ້າເຖິງ; ເຕັກໂນໂລຊີຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຂອງ $[officename]</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ເຕັກໂນໂລຊີຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອໃນ $[officename]</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ເຄື່ອງອ່ານໜ້າຈໍ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ເຄື່ອງຂະຫຍາຍໜ້າຈໍ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ແວ່ນຂະຫຍາຍ</bookmark_value>"

#. PQ7FT
#: assistive.xhp
msgctxt ""
"assistive.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147399\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"assistive\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/assistive.xhp\">Assistive Tools in $[officename]</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"assistive\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/assistive.xhp\">ເຄື່ອງມືຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອໃນ $[officename]</link></variable>"

#. c7ceE
#: assistive.xhp
msgctxt ""
"assistive.xhp\n"
"par_id3143267\n"
"help.text"
msgid "$[officename] supports some assistive technology tools like screen magnification software, screen readers, and on-screen keyboards."
msgstr "$[officename] ຮອງຮັບເຄື່ອງມືເຕັກໂນໂລຊີຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອບາງຢ່າງ ເຊັ່ນ: ຊອບແວຂະຫຍາຍໜ້າຈໍ, ເຄື່ອງອ່ານໜ້າຈໍ ແລະ ຄີບອດເທິງໜ້າຈໍ."

#. 83o65
#: assistive.xhp
msgctxt ""
"assistive.xhp\n"
"par_id8847010\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A current list of supported assistive tools can be found on the Wiki at <link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Accessibility\">https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Accessibility</link>."
msgstr "ລາຍຊື່ເຄື່ອງມືຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອທີ່ຮອງຮັບໃນປັດຈຸບັນສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ທີ່ Wiki ທີ່ <link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Accessibility\">https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Accessibility</link>."

#. vENZ6
#: assistive.xhp
msgctxt ""
"assistive.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153061\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Supported Input Devices"
msgstr "ອຸປະກອນປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຮອງຮັບ"

#. VK7vq
#: assistive.xhp
msgctxt ""
"assistive.xhp\n"
"par_id3156024\n"
"help.text"
msgid "$[officename] provides the ability to use alternative input devices for access to all functions of $[officename]."
msgstr "$[officename] ໃຫ້ຄວາມສາມາດໃນການໃຊ້ອຸປະກອນປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນທາງເລືອກເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກຟັງຊັນຂອງ $[officename]."

#. 6BAQ6
#: assistive.xhp
msgctxt ""
"assistive.xhp\n"
"par_id3149045\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Screen magnification software allow users with low vision to work in $[officename] with caret and focus tracking."
msgstr "ຊອບແວຂະຫຍາຍໜ້າຈໍຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ທີ່ມີສາຍຕາຜິດປົກກະຕິສາມາດເຮັດວຽກໃນ $[officename] ດ້ວຍການຕິດຕາມ caret ແລະ ຈຸດໂຟກັດ."

#. pcQXA
#: assistive.xhp
msgctxt ""
"assistive.xhp\n"
"par_id3152811\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On-screen keyboards enable users to perform almost all data input and commands with a mouse."
msgstr "ຄີບອດເທິງໜ້າຈໍຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງເກືອບທັງໝົດໄດ້ດ້ວຍເມົາສ໌."

#. ZEFBh
#: assistive.xhp
msgctxt ""
"assistive.xhp\n"
"par_id3153379\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Screen readers allow visually impaired users to access $[officename] with text-to-speech and Braille displays."
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງອ່ານໜ້າຈໍຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຜູ້ພິການທາງສາຍຕາສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງ $[officename] ດ້ວຍລະບົບສຽງອ່ານຂໍ້ຄວາມ ແລະ ຈໍສະແດງຜົນອັກສອນເບຣວ."

