#. YC2Pp
#: autocorr_url.xhp
msgctxt ""
"autocorr_url.xhp\n"
"par_id3166410\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you enter text, $[officename] automatically recognizes a word that may be a <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000002.xhp#url\">URL</link> and replaces the word with a hyperlink. $[officename] formats the hyperlink with direct font attributes (color and underline) the properties of which are obtained from certain Character Styles."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານປ້ອນຂໍ້ຄວາມ, $[officename] ຈະຮັບຮູ້ຄຳສັບທີ່ອາດຈະເປັນ <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000002.xhp#url\">URL</link> ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ແລະ ແທນທີ່ຄຳນັ້ນດ້ວຍໄຮເປີລິ້ງ. $[officename] ຈະຈັດຮູບແບບໄຮເປີລິ້ງດ້ວຍຄຸນລັກສະນະຕົວອັກສອນໂດຍກົງ (ສີ ແລະ ຂີດກ້ອງ) ເຊິ່ງຄຸນສົມບັດເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນແມ່ນໄດ້ມາຈາກຮູບແບບຕົວອັກສອນບາງຢ່າງ."

