#. 6vSTS
#: autocorr_url.xhp
msgctxt ""
"autocorr_url.xhp\n"
"par_id3153561\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you do not want $[officename] to automatically recognize URLs as you are typing, there are several ways of turning off this feature."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານບໍ່ຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ $[officename] ຮັບຮູ້ URL ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດໃນຂະນະທີ່ທ່ານພິມ, ມີຫຼາຍວິທີໃນການປິດຄຸນສົມບັດນີ້."

#. RGjwG
#: autocorr_url.xhp
