msgid "Turn off URL Recognition"
msgstr "ປິດການຮັບຮູ້ URL"

#. gFoDA
#: autocorr_url.xhp
msgctxt ""
"autocorr_url.xhp\n"
"par_id3149514\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Load a document of the type for which you want to modify the URL recognition."
msgstr "ໂຫຼດເອກະສານປະເພດທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແກ້ໄຂການຮັບຮູ້ URL."

#. D7Cmm
#: autocorr_url.xhp
msgctxt ""
"autocorr_url.xhp\n"
"par_id3151246\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you want to modify the URL recognition for text documents, open a text document."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການແກ້ໄຂການຮັບຮູ້ URL ສຳລັບເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ໃຫ້ເປີດເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#. DhVCA
#: autocorr_url.xhp
msgctxt ""
"autocorr_url.xhp\n"
"par_id3159413\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Tools - AutoCorrect - AutoCorrect Options</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ແກ້ໄຂອັດຕະໂນມັດ - ຕົວເລືອກການແກ້ໄຂອັດຕະໂນມັດ</emph>."

#. JuDz9
#: autocorr_url.xhp
msgctxt ""
"autocorr_url.xhp\n"
"par_id3148550\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>AutoCorrect</emph> dialog, select the <emph>Options</emph> tab."
msgstr "ໃນກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂອັດຕະໂນມັດ</emph>, ເລືອກແຖບ <emph>ຕົວເລືອກ</emph>."

#. 9cL5j
#: autocorr_url.xhp
msgctxt ""
"autocorr_url.xhp\n"
"par_id3153360\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you unmark <emph>URL Recognition</emph>, words will no longer be automatically replaced with hyperlinks."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຍົກເລີກການໝາຍ <emph>ການຮັບຮູ້ URL</emph>, ຄຳສັບຈະບໍ່ຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍໄຮເປີລິ້ງໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດອີກຕໍ່ໄປ."

#. 9MrpY
#: autocorr_url.xhp
msgctxt ""
"autocorr_url.xhp\n"
"par_id3156423\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In $[officename] Writer there are two check boxes in front of <emph>URL Recognition</emph>. The box in the first column is for later post-editing and the box in the second column is for AutoCorrect as you type."
msgstr "ໃນ $[officename] Writer ຈະມີສອງຊ່ອງໝາຍຢູ່ຕໍ່ໜ້າ <emph>ການຮັບຮູ້ URL</emph>. ຊ່ອງໃນຖັນທຳອິດແມ່ນສຳລັບການແກ້ໄຂພາຍຫຼັງ ແລະ ຊ່ອງໃນຖັນທີສອງແມ່ນສຳລັບການແກ້ໄຂອັດຕະໂນມັດໃນຂະນະທີ່ທ່ານພິມ."

