#. KEnze
#: autohide.xhp
msgctxt ""
"autohide.xhp\n"
"par_id3147242\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Some windows in $[officename] are dockable, such as the Navigator window. You can move these windows, re-size them or dock them to an edge."
msgstr "ໜ້າຕ່າງບາງຢ່າງໃນ $[officename] ສາມາດຕິດຂັດໄດ້ ເຊັ່ນ: ໜ້າຕ່າງຕົວນຳທາງ. ທ່ານສາມາດຍ້າຍໜ້າຕ່າງເຫຼົ່ານີ້, ປັບຂະໜາດ ຫຼື ຕິດພວກມັນໄວ້ທີ່ຂອບ."

#. tfQCX
#: autohide.xhp
msgctxt ""
