msgstr "ເຮັດຊ້ຳສອງຂັ້ນຕອນສຸດທ້າຍສຳລັບແຕ່ລະຂອບ."

#. ySPzX
#: border_paragraph.xhp
msgctxt ""
"border_paragraph.xhp\n"
"par_id3150793\n"
"help.text"
