"hd_id101702511392350\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Installing from Third-party Repositories"
msgstr "ການຕິດຕັ້ງຈາກຄັງເກັບຊອບແວຂອງພາກສ່ວນທີສາມ"

#. EYRit
#: builtin_help.xhp
msgctxt ""
"builtin_help.xhp\n"
"par_id731702511460352\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Linux distributions usually provide their own %PRODUCTNAME packages, hence the method to install the built-in help will be different for each distribution."
msgstr "ການແຈກຢາຍ Linux ປົກກະຕິແລ້ວຈະສະໜອງແພັກເກັດ %PRODUCTNAME ຂອງພວກເຂົາເອງ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນວິທີການຕິດຕັ້ງຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອໃນຕົວຈະແຕກຕ່າງກັນໄປຕາມແຕ່ລະລະບົບ."

#. Qf5GN
#: builtin_help.xhp
msgctxt ""
"builtin_help.xhp\n"
"par_id481702513590717\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Next are the installation instructions for help packages provided by Ubuntu and Fedora."
msgstr "ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ແມ່ນຄຳແນະນຳການຕິດຕັ້ງສຳລັບແພັກເກັດຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອທີ່ສະໜອງໂດຍ Ubuntu ແລະ Fedora."

#. qEYFv
