#. NXWEC
#: chart_axis.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_axis.xhp\n"
"par_id3156426\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To edit the axes of a chart that you have inserted:"
msgstr "ເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂແກນຂອງແຜນພູມທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ແຊກໄວ້:"

#. sgAWE
#: chart_axis.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_axis.xhp\n"
"par_id3155535\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Double-click on the chart."
msgstr "ດັບເບິນຄລິກທີ່ແຜນພູມ."

#. ppDep
#: chart_axis.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_axis.xhp\n"
"par_id3147242\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A gray border appears around the chart and the menu bar now contains commands for editing the objects in the chart."
msgstr "ຂອບສີເທົາຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນອ້ອມແຜນພູມ ແລະ ແຖບເມນູໃນປັດຈຸບັນຈະມີຄຳສັ່ງສຳລັບການແກ້ໄຂວັດຖຸໃນແຜນພູມ."

#. DyEzK
#: chart_axis.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_axis.xhp\n"
"par_id3154749\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Format - Axis</emph>, then select the axis (or axes) that you would like to edit. A dialog appears."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ຮູບແບບ - ແກນ</emph>, ແລ້ວເລືອກແກນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແກ້ໄຂ. ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນ."

#. 2afHm
#: chart_axis.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_axis.xhp\n"
"par_id3154285\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select from the available sections and make the required changes (for example, select the <emph>Scale</emph> tab if you want to modify the scale of the axis)."
msgstr "ເລືອກຈາກພາກສ່ວນທີ່ມີໃຫ້ ແລະ ປ່ຽນແປງຕາມທີ່ຕ້ອງການ (ຕົວຢ່າງ: ເລືອກແຖບ <emph>ມາດຕາສ່ວນ</emph> ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການແກ້ໄຂມາດຕາສ່ວນຂອງແກນ)."

#. YzGcK
#: chart_axis.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_axis.xhp\n"
"par_id3156327\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click <emph>OK</emph>. In your document, click outside the chart to exit chart editing mode."
msgstr "ຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>. ໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກຂ້າງນອກແຜນພູມເພື່ອອອກຈາກໂໝດແກ້ໄຂແຜນພູມ."

#. QzS9F
#: chart_axis.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_axis.xhp\n"
"par_id3147335\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/schart/01/05010000.xhp\">Format - Object properties</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/schart/01/05010000.xhp\">ຮູບແບບ - ຄຸນສົມບັດວັດຖຸ</link>"

