#. 3ZmxR
#: chart_barformat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_barformat.xhp\n"
"par_id3156136\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can add texture to the bars in a graph or chart (instead of the default colors) via graphics:"
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມພື້ນຜິວໃຫ້ກັບແຖບໃນກຣາບ ຫຼື ແຜນພູມ (ແທນທີ່ສີເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ) ຜ່ານຮູບພາບ:"

#. 4UEfD
#: chart_barformat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_barformat.xhp\n"
"par_id3153748\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter edit mode by double-clicking on the chart."
msgstr "ເຂົ້າສູ່ໂໝດແກ້ໄຂໂດຍການດັບເບິນຄລິກທີ່ແຜນພູມ."

#. ZSriQ
#: chart_barformat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_barformat.xhp\n"
"par_id3149182\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click on any bar of the bar series you want to edit. All bars of this series are now selected."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ແຖບໃດໜຶ່ງຂອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແກ້ໄຂ. ແຖບທັງໝົດໃນຊຸດນັ້ນຈະຖືກເລືອກ."

#. ELqcm
#: chart_barformat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_barformat.xhp\n"
"par_id720847\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you want to edit only one bar, click again on that bar."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການແກ້ໄຂພຽງແຕ່ແຖບດຽວ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໃສ່ແຖບນັ້ນອີກຄັ້ງ."

#. d2csF
#: chart_barformat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_barformat.xhp\n"
"par_id3147275\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the context menu choose <emph>Object Properties</emph>. Then choose the <emph>Area</emph> tab."
msgstr "ໃນເມນູຄລິກຂວາ ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <emph>ຄຸນສົມບັດວັດຖຸ</emph>. ແລ້ວເລືອກແຖບ <emph>ພື້ນທີ່</emph>."

#. uLD5N
#: chart_barformat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_barformat.xhp\n"
"par_id3146797\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click on <emph>Image</emph>. In the list box select an image as a texture for the currently selected bars. Click <emph>OK</emph> to accept the setting."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ <emph>ຮູບພາບ</emph>. ໃນລາຍຊື່ໃຫ້ເລືອກຮູບພາບເພື່ອເປັນພື້ນຜິວສຳລັບແຖບທີ່ເລືອກ. ຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph> ເພື່ອຍອມຮັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າ."

#. rgZEg
#: chart_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_insert.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
