msgstr "ປະຕິບັດຕາມຄຳແນະນຳໃນ <link href=\"text/schart/01/wiz_chart_type.xhp\">ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງແຜນພູມ</link> ເພື່ອສ້າງແຜນພູມ."

#. jP5b5
#: chart_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_insert.xhp\n"
"hd_id6436658\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Chart based on values of its own"
msgstr "ແຜນພູມໂດຍອີງຕາມຄ່າຂອງມັນເອງ"

#. 54iGB
#: chart_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_insert.xhp\n"
"par_id6944792\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In Writer, Draw or Impress, choose <emph>Insert - Chart</emph> to insert a chart based on default data."
msgstr "ໃນ Writer, Draw ຫຼື Impress, ເລືອກ <emph>ແຊກ - ແຜນພູມ</emph> ເພື່ອແຊກແຜນພູມໂດຍອີງຕາມຂໍ້ມູນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ."

#. kVMbn
#: chart_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chart_insert.xhp\n"
"par_id3152960\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can change the default data values by double-clicking on the chart and then choosing <link href=\"text/schart/01/03010000.xhp\"><emph>View - Chart Data Table</emph></link>."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດປ່ຽນຄ່າຂໍ້ມູນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໄດ້ໂດຍການດັບເບິນຄລິກທີ່ແຜນພູມ ແລ້ວເລືອກ <link href=\"text/schart/01/03010000.xhp\"><emph>ມຸມເບິ່ງ - ຕາຕະລາງຂໍ້ມູນແຜນພູມ</emph></link>."

#. uWC3o
