msgstr "ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ ໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ ຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນ."

#. zWiGB
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id170820161605417597\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the file and click <emph>Open</emph> or press <emph>Enter</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກໄຟລ໌ ແລະ ຄລິກ <emph>ເປີດ</emph> ຫຼື ກົດ <emph>Enter</emph>."

#. Fc3Ju
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id150820161816053974\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The Remote Files dialog which then appears has many parts. The upper list box contains the list of remote servers you have previously defined. The line below the list box shows the path to access the folder. On the left is the folder structure of the user space in the server. The main pane displays the files in the remote folder."
msgstr "ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ ໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ ທີ່ປະກົດຂຶ້ນມີຫຼາຍພາກສ່ວນ. ລາຍຊື່ທາງເທິງປະກອບມີເຊີບເວີໄລຍະໄກທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ກຳນົດໄວ້ກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້. ແຖວລຸ່ມລາຍຊື່ສະແດງເສັ້ນທາງການເຂົ້າເຖິງໂຟນເດີ. ທາງດ້ານຊ້າຍແມ່ນໂຄງສ້າງໂຟນເດີໃນເຊີບເວີ. ສ່ວນຫຼັກຈະສະແດງໄຟລ໌ໃນໂຟນເດີໄລຍະໄກ."

#. RTJHm
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"bm_id190820161721082861\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>remote file service;file lock</bookmark_value>  <bookmark_value>remote file service;version control</bookmark_value>  <bookmark_value>remote file service;working copy</bookmark_value>  <bookmark_value>remote file service;checkout</bookmark_value>  <bookmark_value>remote file service;checkin</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ບໍລິການໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ; ການລັອກໄຟລ໌</bookmark_value>  <bookmark_value>ບໍລິການໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ; ການຄວບຄຸມເວີຊັນ</bookmark_value>  <bookmark_value>ບໍລິການໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ; check-out</bookmark_value>  <bookmark_value>ບໍລິການໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ; check-in</bookmark_value>"

#. j47pX
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"hd_id170820161605421283\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Checking out and checking in files"
msgstr "ການ Checking out ແລະ Checking in ໄຟລ໌"

#. rERTB
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id170820161605429941\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The Check Out and Check In actions control updates to the document and prevent unwanted overwrites in a CMIS remote service."
msgstr "ການກະທຳ Check Out ແລະ Check In ຈະຄວບຄຸມການອັບເດດເອກະສານ ແລະ ປ້ອງກັນການຂຽນທັບທີ່ບໍ່ຕ້ອງການໃນບໍລິການໄລຍະໄກ CMIS."

#. DC5JZ
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id17082016160542203\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Checking out a document locks it, preventing other users from writing changes to it. Only one user can have a particular document checked out (locked) at any time. Checking in a document or canceling the checkout unlocks the document."
msgstr "ການ Checking out ເອກະສານຈະລັອກມັນໄວ້, ເພື່ອປ້ອງກັນບໍ່ໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນແກ້ໄຂມັນ. ມີພຽງແຕ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຄົນດຽວເທົ່ານັ້ນທີ່ສາມາດ check out (ລັອກ) ເອກະສານໃດໜຶ່ງໄດ້ໃນເວລາດຽວກັນ. ການ Checking in ຫຼື ການຍົກເລີກການ check out ຈະເປັນການປົດລັອກເອກະສານ."

#. iz2Yh
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id170820161605426690\n"
"help.text"
msgid "There are no checkin/checkout controls for remote files in Windows Shares, WebDAV and SSH services."
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີການຄວບຄຸມ check-in/check-out ສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກໃນບໍລິການ Windows Shares, WebDAV ແລະ SSH."

#. ykFEK
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id170820161605428976\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When a file is open from a CMIS remote file service, %PRODUCTNAME displays a <emph>Check Out</emph> button on the top message area. Click the <emph>Check Out</emph> button to lock the file in the server to prevent edition by another user. Alternatively choose <item type=\"menuitem\">File - Check Out</item>."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເປີດໄຟລ໌ຈາກບໍລິການໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ CMIS, %PRODUCTNAME ຈະສະແດງປຸ່ມ <emph>Check Out</emph> ຢູ່ສ່ວນຂໍ້ຄວາມທາງເທິງ. ຄລິກປຸ່ມ <emph>Check Out</emph> ເພື່ອລັອກໄຟລ໌ໃນເຊີບເວີເພື່ອປ້ອງກັນການແກ້ໄຂໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນ. ຫຼື ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ໄຟລ໌ - Check Out</item>."

#. 33JmH
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id190820161707153804\n"
"help.text"
msgid "%PRODUCTNAME creates a working copy of the file in the server (and inserts the string <item type=\"literal\">(Working Copy)</item> in the file name) when a file is checked out. Every edition and save operation is done in the working copy. You can save your file as many times you want. When you finished your changes, check in the file."
msgstr "%PRODUCTNAME ຈະສ້າງສຳເນົາໄຟລ໌ສຳລັບເຮັດວຽກໃນເຊີບເວີ (ແລະ ເພີ່ມຂໍ້ຄວາມ <item type=\"literal\">(Working Copy)</item> ໃນຊື່ໄຟລ໌) ເມື່ອໄຟລ໌ຖືກ checked out. ທຸກການແກ້ໄຂ ແລະ ການບັນທຶກຈະເຮັດຢູ່ໃນສຳເນົານີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ໄດ້ຫຼາຍຄັ້ງຕາມທີ່ຕ້ອງການ. ເມື່ອສຳເລັດການແກ້ໄຂແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ check in ໄຟລ໌."

#. 27HBp
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id190820161707156843\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To check in the file, choose <item type=\"menuitem\">File - Check In</item>. A dialog opens to insert comments about the last edition. These comments are recorded in the CMIS server for version control. The working copy replaces the existing file and its version number is updated."
msgstr "ເພື່ອ check in ໄຟລ໌, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ໄຟລ໌ - Check In</item>. ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນເພື່ອໃຫ້ປ້ອນຄຳເຫັນກ່ຽວກັບການແກ້ໄຂຫຼ້າສຸດ. ຄຳເຫັນເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະຖືກບັນທຶກໄວ້ໃນເຊີບເວີ CMIS ເພື່ອຄວບຄຸມເວີຊັນ. ສຳເນົາທີ່ເຮັດວຽກຈະໄປແທນທີ່ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຢູ່ ແລະ ເລກເວີຊັນຈະຖືກອັບເດດ."

#. umXQV
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id190820161707155303\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To cancel a checkout, choose <item type=\"menuitem\">File - Cancel Checkout</item>. A warning message will inform that the latest edition will be discarded. If confirmed, no version updates occurs."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຍົກເລີກການ checkout, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ໄຟລ໌ - ຍົກເລີກ Checkout</item>. ຂໍ້ຄວາມເຕືອນຈະແຈ້ງວ່າການແກ້ໄຂຫຼ້າສຸດຈະຖືກຍົກເລີກ. ຖ້າຢືນຢັນ, ຈະບໍ່ມີການອັບເດດເວີຊັນ."

#. XSAgF
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id19082016170715785\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Remember to check in the file when finishing using it. Not doing so will lock the file and no other user will be allowed to modify it."
msgstr "ຢ່າລືມ check in ໄຟລ໌ເມື່ອໃຊ້ງານສຳເລັດ. ຖ້າບໍ່ເຮັດ, ໄຟລ໌ຈະຖືກລັອກໄວ້ ແລະ ຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນຈະບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂມັນໄດ້."

#. Bx5Ma
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"bm_id190820161722159908\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>remote file service;saving to remote server</bookmark_value>  <bookmark_value>remote file service;saving</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ບໍລິການໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ; ການບັນທຶກລົງເຊີບເວີໄລຍະໄກ</bookmark_value>  <bookmark_value>ບໍລິການໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ; ການບັນທຶກ</bookmark_value>"

#. VAG8Z
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"hd_id170820161605423820\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To save a file in a remote file server"
msgstr "ວິທີບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ໃນເຊີບເວີໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ"

#. ko6Yu
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id170820161605428770\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Do one of the following"
msgstr "ໃຫ້ເຮັດຢ່າງໃດຢ່າງໜຶ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້"

#. DAyrU
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id170820161605423872\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the file was opened from a CMIS server, choose <item type=\"menuitem\">File - Save</item>, click on the <emph>Save</emph> button or hit <item type=\"literal\">Ctrl + S</item>."
msgstr "ຖ້າໄຟລ໌ຖືກເປີດຈາກເຊີບເວີ CMIS, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ໄຟລ໌ - ບັນທຶກ</item>, ຄລິກປຸ່ມ <emph>ບັນທຶກ</emph> ຫຼື ກົດ <item type=\"literal\">Ctrl + S</item>."

#. QnkqB
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id190820161707166344\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the file is not stored in a CMIS server, choose <item type=\"menuitem\">File - Save Remote</item> or long-click the <emph>Save</emph> icon and select <emph>Save Remote File</emph>."
msgstr "ຖ້າໄຟລ໌ບໍ່ໄດ້ເກັບໄວ້ໃນເຊີບເວີ CMIS, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ໄຟລ໌ - ບັນທຶກໄລຍະໄກ</item> ຫຼື ຄລິກຄ້າງທີ່ໄອຄອນ <emph>ບັນທຶກ</emph> ແລ້ວເລືອກ <emph>ບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ</emph>."

#. DaEPC
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id170820161605428591\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <emph>Remote files</emph> dialog appears. Select the remote file server."
msgstr "ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ</emph> ຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນ. ໃຫ້ເລືອກເຊີບເວີໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ."

#. wQjzG
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id170820161605425024\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Filter</emph> list box, select the desired format."
msgstr "ໃນລາຍຊື່ <emph>ຕົວແຍກ (Filter)</emph>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຮູບແບບທີ່ຕ້ອງການ."

#. pXSLP
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id170820161605424622\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter a name in the File name box and click <emph>Save</emph>."
msgstr "ປ້ອນຊື່ໃນຊ່ອງ ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ ແລ້ວຄລິກ <emph>ບັນທຶກ</emph>."

#. 4rWP7
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id190820161707163121\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you finish working with the file, check it in. To do so, choose <item type=\"menuitem\">File - Check In</item>."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເຮັດວຽກກັບໄຟລ໌ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ check it in. ໂດຍເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ໄຟລ໌ - Check In</item>."

#. 9coLF
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"bm_id19082016172305788\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>remote file service;CMIS properties</bookmark_value>  <bookmark_value>remote file service;file properties</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ບໍລິການໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ; ຄຸນສົມບັດ CMIS</bookmark_value>  <bookmark_value>ບໍລິການໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ; ຄຸນສົມບັດໄຟລ໌</bookmark_value>"

#. YVHQz
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"hd_id190820161707169171\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Properties of files stored in CMIS servers"
msgstr "ຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເກັບໄວ້ໃນເຊີບເວີ CMIS"

#. AxDxx
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id19082016170716519\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Files stored in CMIS server have properties and metadata not available in a local storage. These metadata are important for controls and debugging of the CMIS connection and server implementation. All parameters displayed are read-only."
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເກັບໄວ້ໃນເຊີບເວີ CMIS ຈະມີຄຸນສົມບັດ ແລະ ເມຕາດາຕາທີ່ບໍ່ມີໃນບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນທ້ອງຖິ່ນ. ເມຕາດາຕາເຫຼົ່ານີ້ສຳຄັນສຳລັບການຄວບຄຸມ ແລະ ການແກ້ໄຂຈຸດບົກພ່ອງຂອງການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ CMIS. ຄ່າທັງໝົດທີ່ສະແດງແມ່ນແບບອ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງດຽວ."

#. ALdGF
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id190820161707161708\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <item type=\"menuitem\">File - Properties</item>, CMIS tab."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ໄຟລ໌ - ຄຸນສົມບັດ</item>, ແຖບ CMIS."

#. ETwS2
#: cmis-remote-files.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cmis-remote-files.xhp\n"
"par_id210820161033581776\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/guide/cmis-remote-files-setup.xhp\">Setting up a remote file service</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/guide/cmis-remote-files-setup.xhp\">ການຕັ້ງຄ່າບໍລິການໄຟລ໌ໄລຍະໄກ</link>"

#. eFgFA
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Collaboration"
msgstr "ການຮ່ວມມື"

#. n3jUD
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"bm_id4459669\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>sharing documents</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>collaboration</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>file locking with collaboration</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>locked documents</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການແບ່ງປັນເອກະສານ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການຮ່ວມມື</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການລັອກໄຟລ໌ໃນການຮ່ວມມື</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ເອກະສານທີ່ຖືກລັອກ</bookmark_value>"

#. pAGSG
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id130008\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"collab\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/collab.xhp\">Collaboration</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"collab\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/collab.xhp\">ການຮ່ວມມື</link></variable>"

#. 4kNX2
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id5821710\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In %PRODUCTNAME Writer, Impress, and Draw, only one user at a time can open any document for writing. In Calc, many users can open the same spreadsheet for writing at the same time."
msgstr "ໃນ %PRODUCTNAME Writer, Impress, ແລະ Draw, ສາມາດເປີດເອກະສານເພື່ອຂຽນໄດ້ພຽງແຕ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ດຽວໃນເວລາດຽວກັນ. ໃນ Calc, ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຫຼາຍຄົນສາມາດເປີດຕາຕະລາງຄຳນວນດຽວກັນເພື່ອຂຽນພ້ອມກັນໄດ້."

#. yLhB5
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id6917020\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Collaboration in Calc"
msgstr "ການຮ່ວມມືໃນ Calc"

#. 69hqk
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id4411145\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In %PRODUCTNAME Calc, document sharing allows simultaneous write access for many users. Every user who wants to collaborate should enter a name on the <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME - User Data</emph> tab page."
msgstr "ໃນ %PRODUCTNAME Calc, ການແບ່ງປັນເອກະສານຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຫຼາຍຄົນເຂົ້າເຖິງການຂຽນໄດ້ພ້ອມກັນ. ຜູ້ໃຊ້ທຸກຄົນທີ່ຕ້ອງການຮ່ວມມືກັນຄວນປ້ອນຊື່ໃນໜ້າແຖບ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ສິ່ງທີ່ມັກ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME - ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້</emph>."

#. uFAoi
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id6799218\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Some commands are not available (grayed out) when change tracking or document sharing is activated. For a new spreadsheet you cannot apply or insert the grayed out elements."
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງບາງຢ່າງຈະໃຊ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ (ເປັນສີເທົາ) ເມື່ອມີການເປີດໃຊ້ການຕິດຕາມການປ່ຽນແປງ ຫຼື ການແບ່ງປັນເອກະສານ."

#. Gz4ca
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id3274941\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Creating a new spreadsheet"
msgstr "ການສ້າງຕາຕະລາງຄຳນວນໃໝ່"

#. nywCg
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id9804681\n"
"help.text"
msgid "User A creates a new spreadsheet document. The following conditions can apply:"
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ສ້າງເອກະສານຕາຕະລາງຄຳນວນໃໝ່. ເງື່ອນໄຂຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ອາດຈະເກີດຂຶ້ນ:"

#. MtT9R
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id2109744\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The user does not want to share the spreadsheet for collaboration."
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ບໍ່ຕ້ອງການແບ່ງປັນຕາຕະລາງຄຳນວນສຳລັບການຮ່ວມມື."

#. Vmhzh
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id5374614\n"
"help.text"
msgid "User A opens, edits, and saves the document as described above for Writer, Impress, and Draw document."
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ເປີດ, ແກ້ໄຂ ແລະ ບັນທຶກເອກະສານຕາມທີ່ອະທິບາຍໄວ້ຂ້າງເທິງສຳລັບເອກະສານ Writer, Impress ແລະ Draw."

#. 6CcTG
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id768761\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The user wants to share the document for collaboration."
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຕ້ອງການແບ່ງປັນເອກະສານສຳລັບການຮ່ວມມື."

#. sXZAB
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id6844691\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The user chooses <item type=\"menuitem\">Tools - Share Document</item> to activate the collaboration features for this document. A dialog opens where the user can choose to enable or disable sharing. If the user enables sharing, the document will be saved in shared mode, which is also shown on the title bar."
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ເຄື່ອງມື - ແບ່ງປັນເອກະສານ</item> ເພື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ຄຸນສົມບັດການຮ່ວມມືສຳລັບເອກະສານນີ້. ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນເພື່ອໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ເລືອກເປີດ ຫຼື ປິດການແບ່ງປັນ. ຖ້າຜູ້ໃຊ້ເປີດການແບ່ງປັນ, ເອກະສານຈະຖືກບັນທຶກໃນໂໝດແບ່ງປັນ, ເຊິ່ງຈະສະແດງຢູ່ໃນແຖບຊື່ເລື່ອງນຳ."

#. Qb62w
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id5288857\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <item type=\"menuitem\">Tools - Share Document</item> command can be used to switch the mode for the current document from unshared mode to shared mode. If you want to use a shared document in unshared mode, you would save the shared document using another name or path. This creates a copy of the spreadsheet that is not shared."
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງ <item type=\"menuitem\">ເຄື່ອງມື - ແບ່ງປັນເອກະສານ</item> ສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອສະຫຼັບໂໝດສຳລັບເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນຈາກໂໝດບໍ່ແບ່ງປັນເປັນໂໝດແບ່ງປັນ. ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຊ້ເອກະສານທີ່ແບ່ງປັນໃນໂໝດບໍ່ແບ່ງປັນ, ໃຫ້ທ່ານບັນທຶກເອກະສານນັ້ນໂດຍໃຊ້ຊື່ ຫຼື ເສັ້ນທາງອື່ນ. ນີ້ຈະເປັນການສ້າງສຳເນົາຂອງຕາຕະລາງຄຳນວນທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ແບ່ງປັນ."

#. HjkXK
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id8842127\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opening a spreadsheet"
msgstr "ການເປີດຕາຕະລາງຄຳນວນ"

#. ZndGw
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id7276528\n"
"help.text"
msgid "User A opens a spreadsheet document. The following conditions can apply:"
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ເປີດເອກະສານຕາຕະລາງຄຳນວນ. ເງື່ອນໄຂຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ອາດຈະເກີດຂຶ້ນ:"

#. kPAsq
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id8363902\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The spreadsheet document is not in shared mode."
msgstr "ເອກະສານສະເປຣດຊີດບໍ່ໄດ້ຢູ່ໃນໂໝດແບ່ງປັນ."

#. caEvR
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id5974303\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The user can open, edit, and save the document as described above for Writer, Impress, and Draw documents."
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດເປີດ, ແກ້ໄຂ, ແລະ ບັນທຶກເອກະສານຕາມທີ່ໄດ້ອະທິບາຍໄວ້ຂ້າງເທິງສຳລັບເອກະສານ Writer, Impress, ແລະ Draw."

#. 8HPhR
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id5323343\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The spreadsheet document is in shared mode."
msgstr "ເອກະສານສະເປຣດຊີດຢູ່ໃນໂໝດແບ່ງປັນ."

#. mw8FB
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id5824457\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The user sees a message that the document is in shared mode and that some features are not available in this mode. The user can disable this message for the future. After clicking OK, the document is opened in shared mode."
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຈະເຫັນຂໍ້ຄວາມວ່າເອກະສານຢູ່ໃນໂໝດແບ່ງປັນ ແລະ ບາງຄຸນສົມບັດບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ໃນໂໝດນີ້. ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດປິດຂໍ້ຄວາມນີ້ສຳລັບຄັ້ງຕໍ່ໄປໄດ້. ຫຼັງຈາກຄລິກ ຕົກລົງ, ເອກະສານຈະຖືກເປີດໃນໂໝດແບ່ງປັນ."

#. uCtRi
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id401704727687777\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Resolve Conflicts dialog"
msgstr "ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ຂັດແຍ່ງ"

#. vSBHr
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id5800653\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">If the same contents are changed by different users, the Resolve Conflicts dialog opens. For each conflict, decide which changes to keep.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຖ້າເນື້ອໃນອັນດຽວກັນຖືກປ່ຽນແປງໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້ທີ່ຕ່າງກັນ, ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ຂັດແຍ່ງຈະຖືກເປີດຂຶ້ນ. ສຳລັບແຕ່ລະຂໍ້ຂັດແຍ່ງ, ໃຫ້ຕັດສິນໃຈວ່າຈະເກັບຮັກສາການປ່ຽນແປງໃດໄວ້.</ahelp>"

#. GPWds
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id1001704727711775\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Keep Mine"
msgstr "ເກັບຂອງຂ້ອຍໄວ້"

#. QVkZk
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id6263924\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Keeps your change, voids the other change.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ເກັບການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງທ່ານໄວ້, ຍົກເລີກການປ່ຽນແປງອື່ນ.</ahelp>"

#. EBzEe
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id781704727739081\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Keep Other"
msgstr "ເກັບຂອງຜູ້ອື່ນໄວ້"

#. qsr52
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id3609118\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Keeps the change of the other user, voids your change.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ເກັບການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນໄວ້, ຍົກເລີກການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງທ່ານ.</ahelp>"

#. tA4eD
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id931704727781391\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Keep All Mine"
msgstr "ເກັບຂອງຂ້ອຍໄວ້ທັງໝົດ"

#. 2JEYD
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id7184057\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Keeps all your changes, voids all other changes.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ເກັບທຸກການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງທ່ານໄວ້, ຍົກເລີກທຸກການປ່ຽນແປງອື່ນ.</ahelp>"

#. m5UUm
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id681704727819702\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Keep All Others"
msgstr "ເກັບຂອງຜູ້ອື່ນໄວ້ທັງໝົດ"

#. i8MDM
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id786767\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Keeps the changes of all other users, voids your changes.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ເກັບການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນທັງໝົດໄວ້, ຍົກເລີກການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງທ່ານ.</ahelp>"

#. 4fXQR
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id2934965\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Saving a shared spreadsheet document"
msgstr "ການບັນທຶກເອກະສານສະເປຣດຊີດທີ່ແບ່ງປັນ"

#. SZpDm
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id1174657\n"
"help.text"
msgid "User A saves a shared document. The following conditions can apply:"
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ບັນທຶກເອກະສານທີ່ແບ່ງປັນ. ເງື່ອນໄຂຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ອາດຈະເກີດຂຶ້ນ:"

#. 7aKzY
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id2577593\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The document was not modified and saved by another user since user A opened the document."
msgstr "ເອກະສານບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກປ່ຽນແປງ ແລະ ບັນທຶກໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນ ນັບຕັ້ງແຕ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ເປີດເອກະສານ."

#. QRFGC
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id5883968\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The document is saved."
msgstr "ເອກະສານຖືກບັນທຶກແລ້ວ."

#. NMdsc
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id9049653\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The document was modified and saved by another user since user A opened the document."
msgstr "ເອກະສານຖືກປ່ຽນແປງ ແລະ ບັນທຶກໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນ ນັບຕັ້ງແຕ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ເປີດເອກະສານ."

#. DCGUE
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id1976683\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the changes do not conflict, the document is saved."
msgstr "ຖ້າການປ່ຽນແປງບໍ່ຂັດແຍ່ງກັນ, ເອກະສານຈະຖືກບັນທຶກ."

#. smLfo
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id43946\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the changes conflict, the Resolve Conflicts dialog will be shown. User A must decide for the conflicts which version to keep, \"Keep Mine\" or \"Keep Other\". When all conflicts are resolved, the document is saved. While user A resolves the conflicts, no other user is able to save the shared document."
msgstr "ຖ້າການປ່ຽນແປງຂັດແຍ່ງກັນ, ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ຂັດແຍ່ງຈະສະແດງຂຶ້ນ. ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ຕ້ອງຕັດສິນໃຈວ່າຈະເກັບເວີຊັນໃດໄວ້ ລະຫວ່າງ \"ເກັບຂອງຂ້ອຍໄວ້\" ຫຼື \"ເກັບຂອງຜູ້ອື່ນໄວ້\". ເມື່ອແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ຂັດແຍ່ງທັງໝົດແລ້ວ, ເອກະສານຈະຖືກບັນທຶກ. ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ກຳລັງແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ຂັດແຍ່ງ, ຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນຈະບໍ່ສາມາດບັນທຶກເອກະສານທີ່ແບ່ງປັນນີ້ໄດ້."

#. Zpv8Z
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id6449171\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Another user tries to save the shared document and resolves conflicts in this moment."
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນພະຍາຍາມບັນທຶກເອກະສານທີ່ແບ່ງປັນ ແລະ ກຳລັງແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ຂັດແຍ່ງໃນເວລານີ້."

#. KAkFu
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id7101046\n"
"help.text"
msgid "User A sees a message that a merge-in is in progress. User A can choose to cancel the save command for now, or retry saving some time later."
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ຈະເຫັນຂໍ້ຄວາມວ່າກຳລັງດຳເນີນການຮວມຂໍ້ມູນ. ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ສາມາດເລືອກຍົກເລີກການບັນທຶກໃນຕອນນີ້ ຫຼື ລອງບັນທຶກໃໝ່ໃນພາຍຫຼັງ."

#. CXioE
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id7186498\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When a user successfully saves a shared spreadsheet, the document will be reloaded after the save command, so that the spreadsheet shows the latest version of all changes that got saved by all users. A message shows that \"foreign changes have been added\" when another user did change some contents."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຜູ້ໃຊ້ບັນທຶກສະເປຣດຊີດທີ່ແບ່ງປັນສຳເລັດ, ເອກະສານຈະຖືກໂຫຼດໃໝ່ຫຼັງຈາກຄຳສັ່ງບັນທຶກ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ສະເປຣດຊີດສະແດງເວີຊັນຫຼ້າສຸດຂອງທຸກການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ບັນທຶກໂດຍທຸກຜູ້ໃຊ້. ຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະສະແດງວ່າ \"ມີການເພີ່ມການປ່ຽນແປງຈາກພາຍນອກ\" ເມື່ອມີຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນປ່ຽນແປງເນື້ອໃນບາງຢ່າງ."

#. 7bzGD
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id2871791\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Collaboration in Writer, Impress, and Draw"
msgstr "ການເຮັດວຽກຮ່ວມກັນໃນ Writer, Impress, ແລະ Draw"

#. 94ZGM
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id2675862\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For all modules Writer, Impress, Draw, and for Calc when document sharing is not enabled, a file locking is possible. This file locking is available even when accessing the same document from different operating systems:"
msgstr "ສຳລັບທຸກໂມດູນ Writer, Impress, Draw ແລະ ສຳລັບ Calc ເມື່ອບໍ່ໄດ້ເປີດໃຊ້ການແບ່ງປັນເອກະສານ, ສາມາດໃຊ້ການລັອກໄຟລ໌ໄດ້. ການລັອກໄຟລ໌ນີ້ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າຈະເຂົ້າເຖິງເອກະສານດຽວກັນຈາກລະບົບປະຕິບັດການທີ່ຕ່າງກັນ:"

#. 2AFCR
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id7333597\n"
"help.text"
msgid "User A opens a document. The following conditions can apply:"
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ເປີດເອກະສານ. ເງື່ອນໄຂຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ອາດຈະເກີດຂຶ້ນ:"

#. PTvX3
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id9976195\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The document is not locked by any other user."
msgstr "ເອກະສານບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກລັອກໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນ."

#. HsShu
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id2507400\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This document will be opened for read and write access by user A. The document will be locked for other users until user A closes the document."
msgstr "ເອກະສານນີ້ຈະຖືກເປີດເພື່ອໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ອ່ານ ແລະ ຂຽນໄດ້. ເອກະສານຈະຖືກລັອກສຳລັບຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນ ຈົນກວ່າຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ຈະປິດເອກະສານ."

#. ydPnu
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id216681\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The document is marked as \"read-only\" by the file system."
msgstr "ເອກະສານຖືກກຳນົດໃຫ້ \"ອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ\" ໂດຍລະບົບໄຟລ໌."

#. dwEXL
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id7709585\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This document will be opened in read-only mode. Editing is not allowed. User A can save the document using another document name or another path. User A can edit this copy."
msgstr "ເອກະສານນີ້ຈະຖືກເປີດໃນໂໝດອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ. ບໍ່ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ແກ້ໄຂ. ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ສາມາດບັນທຶກເອກະສານໂດຍໃຊ້ຊື່ໃໝ່ ຫຼື ທີ່ຢູ່ໃໝ່ໄດ້ ແລະ ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂສະບັບສຳເນົານັ້ນໄດ້."

#. E2fQ9
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id4309518\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The document is locked by another user."
msgstr "ເອກະສານຖືກລັອກໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນ."

#. r7ows
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id206610\n"
"help.text"
msgid "User A sees a dialog that tells the user the document is locked. The dialog offers to open the document in read-only mode, or to open a copy for editing, or to cancel the Open command."
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ A ຈະເຫັນກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມແຈ້ງວ່າເອກະສານຖືກລັອກ. ກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະສະເໜີໃຫ້ເປີດເອກະສານໃນໂໝດອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ, ຫຼື ເປີດສຳເນົາເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂ, ຫຼື ຍົກເລີກຄຳສັ່ງເປີດ."

#. 2v6Po
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"hd_id29349651\n"
"help.text"
msgid "User access permissions and sharing documents"
msgstr "ສິດການເຂົ້າເຖິງຂອງຜູ້ໃຊ້ ແລະ ການແບ່ງປັນເອກະສານ"

#. 6gGwN
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id11746571\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Some conditions must be met on operating systems with a user permission management."
msgstr "ເງື່ອນໄຂບາງຢ່າງຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການຕອບສະໜອງໃນລະບົບປະຕິບັດການທີ່ມີການຈັດການສິດຜູ້ໃຊ້."

#. 8Dbaw
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id25775931\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The shared file needs to reside in a location which is accessible by all collaborators."
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ແບ່ງປັນຕ້ອງຢູ່ໃນຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ທຸກຄົນທີ່ເຮັດວຽກຮ່ວມກັນສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້."

#. J8DiS
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id90496531\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The file permissions for both the document and the corresponding lock file need to be set so that all collaborators can create, delete, and change the files."
msgstr "ສິດຂອງໄຟລ໌ທັງເອກະສານ ແລະ ໄຟລ໌ລັອກທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ ຕ້ອງຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າເພື່ອໃຫ້ທຸກຄົນສາມາດສ້າງ, ລຶບ, ແລະ ປ່ຽນແປງໄຟລ໌ໄດ້."

#. 5kTtj
#: collab.xhp
msgctxt ""
"collab.xhp\n"
"par_id71864981\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Write access also enables other users to (accidentally or deliberately) delete or change a file."
msgstr "ສິດການຂຽນຍັງເຮັດໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ອື່ນສາມາດລຶບ ຫຼື ປ່ຽນແປງໄຟລ໌ໄດ້ (ບໍ່ວ່າຈະໂດຍບັງເອີນ ຫຼື ຕັ້ງໃຈ)."

