msgstr "ໃນ %PRODUCTNAME, ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງຟອມໃໝ່ໂດຍໃຊ້ <link href=\"text/shared/autopi/01090000.xhp\">ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງຟອມ</link>:"

#. xuFRu
#: data_forms.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_forms.xhp\n"
"par_idN10632\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open the database file where you want to create the new form."
msgstr "ເປີດໄຟລ໌ຖານຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການສ້າງຟອມໃໝ່."

#. DMEb3
#: data_forms.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_forms.xhp\n"
"par_idN10636\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the left pane of the database window, click the <emph>Forms</emph> icon."
msgstr "ໃນແຖບດ້ານຊ້າຍຂອງປ່ອງຢ້ຽມຖານຂໍ້ມູນ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໄອຄອນ <emph>ຟອມ</emph>."

#. EtQEf
