"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id1886959\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Started by \"Use Wizard to Create Report\" command."
msgstr "ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍຄຳສັ່ງ \"ໃຊ້ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງເພື່ອສ້າງລາຍງານ\"."

#. xtNyg
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id455030\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Full flexibility to use report headers and footers, page headers and footers, multi-column reports."
msgstr "ມີຄວາມຢືດຢຸ່ນຢ່າງເຕັມທີ່ໃນການໃຊ້ຫົວ ແລະ ທ້າຍລາຍງານ, ຫົວ ແລະ ທ້າຍໜ້າ, ແລະ ລາຍງານແບບຫຼາຍຖັນ."

#. zFQWV
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id8409985\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Uses a Writer template to generate a report document."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ແມ່ແບບ Writer ເພື່ອສ້າງເອກະສານລາຍງານ."

#. xhCiE
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id5931272\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use drag-and-drop to position the record fields or other design elements like pictures or lines."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ການລາກແລ້ວວາງເພື່ອວາງຕຳແໜ່ງຟິລບັນທຶກ ຫຼື ອົງປະກອບການອອກແບບອື່ນໆ ເຊັ່ນ ຮູບພາບ ຫຼື ເສັ້ນ."

#. eZ9KJ
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id9869075\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select from several given choices to arrange the data records."
msgstr "ເລືອກຈາກຫຼາຍຕົວເລືອກທີ່ມີໃຫ້ເພື່ອຈັດລຽງບັນທຶກຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. cDZAT
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id8611713\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Generates a one-time snapshot of the data. To see an updated report, execute the same report again to create a Writer document with the updated data."
msgstr "ສ້າງພາບຖ່າຍຂໍ້ມູນ (Snapshot) ພຽງຄັ້ງດຽວ. ເພື່ອເບິ່ງລາຍງານທີ່ອັບເດດແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ປະມວນຜົນລາຍງານເດີມອີກຄັ້ງເພື່ອສ້າງເອກະສານ Writer ດ້ວຍຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່."

#. mE89k
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id2866908\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can choose to generate a one-time snapshot with fixed data, or a \"live\" report with links to the current data at the time when you open the Base file."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກສ້າງພາບຖ່າຍຂໍ້ມູນຄັ້ງດຽວທີ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນຄົງທີ່, ຫຼື ລາຍງານແບບ \"ສົດ\" ທີ່ມີລິ້ງໄປຫາຂໍ້ມູນປັດຈຸບັນໃນເວລາທີ່ທ່ານເປີດໄຟລ໌ Base."

#. nfLCt
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id4169743\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Saves the report as a Writer text document. Stores the information how to create the report inside the Base file."
msgstr "ບັນທຶກລາຍງານເປັນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ Writer. ເກັບກຳຂໍ້ມູນວິທີການສ້າງລາຍງານໄວ້ໃນໄຟລ໌ Base."

#. qePiD
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id408948\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Saves the report and the information how to create the report inside the Base file."
msgstr "ບັນທຶກລາຍງານ ແລະ ຂໍ້ມູນວິທີການສ້າງລາຍງານໄວ້ໃນໄຟລ໌ Base."

#. j3Ymg
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id2891933\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose Open in the context menu or double-click the report name to create a new report with the current data."
msgstr "ເລືອກ ເປີດ ໃນເມນູຄລິກຂວາ ຫຼື ດັບເບິລຄລິກທີ່ຊື່ລາຍງານເພື່ອສ້າງລາຍງານໃໝ່ດ້ວຍຂໍ້ມູນປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. drzFt
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id6142765\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose Open in the context menu or double-click the report name to either see again the static snapshot of the data from first creation time, or to create a new report with the current data. This depends on your choice on the last page of the wizard."
msgstr "ເລືອກ ເປີດ ໃນເມນູຄລິກຂວາ ຫຼື ດັບເບິລຄລິກທີ່ຊື່ລາຍງານ ເພື່ອເບິ່ງພາບຖ່າຍຂໍ້ມູນຄົງທີ່ຈາກຕອນທີ່ສ້າງຄັ້ງທຳອິດ ຫຼື ເພື່ອສ້າງລາຍງານໃໝ່ດ້ວຍຂໍ້ມູນປັດຈຸບັນ. ນີ້ແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບທາງເລືອກຂອງທ່ານໃນໜ້າສຸດທ້າຍຂອງຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງ."

#. u9FdV
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id1757560\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose Edit in the context menu of a report name to open the Report Builder window, with the report's information loaded."
msgstr "ເລືອກ ແກ້ໄຂ ໃນເມນູຄລິກຂວາຂອງຊື່ລາຍງານເພື່ອເປີດໜ້າຕ່າງຕົວສ້າງລາຍງານ ພ້ອມກັບໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນຂອງລາຍງານນັ້ນມາ."

#. aEfC3
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"par_id4649189\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose Edit in the context menu of a report name to edit the Writer template file that was used to create the report."
msgstr "ເລືອກ ແກ້ໄຂ ໃນເມນູຄລິກຂວາຂອງຊື່ລາຍງານເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂໄຟລ໌ແມ່ແບບ Writer ທີ່ຖືກໃຊ້ເພື່ອສ້າງລາຍງານນັ້ນ."

#. wCo9W
#: data_reports.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_reports.xhp\n"
"hd_id8414258\n"
