"help.text"
msgid "Apply Filter"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຕົວການກັ່ນຕອງ"

#. u3opy
#: data_search2.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_search2.xhp\n"
"par_id3146898\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The filter that has been set can be removed by clicking <link href=\"text/shared/02/12040000.xhp\"><emph>Reset Filter/Sort</emph></link> icon."
msgstr "ຕົວການກັ່ນຕອງທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ສາມາດເອົາອອກໄດ້ໂດຍການຄລິກທີ່ໄອຄອນ <link href=\"text/shared/02/12040000.xhp\"><emph>ລ້າງຕົວການກັ່ນຕອງ/ການຈັດລຽງ</emph></link>."

#. 5giVo
