#. HPTAM
#: data_tables.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_tables.xhp\n"
"par_idN10650\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the left pane of the database window, click the <emph>Tables</emph> icon."
msgstr "ໃນແຖບດ້ານຊ້າຍຂອງໜ້າຕ່າງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ, ຄລິກທີ່ໄອຄອນ <emph>ຕາຕະລາງ</emph>."

#. QyEwS
#: data_tables.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_tables.xhp\n"
"par_idN10658\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click <emph>Create Table in Design View</emph>."
msgstr "ຄລິກ <emph>ສ້າງຕາຕະລາງໃນມຸມມອງການອອກແບບ</emph>."

#. BCDNg
