"par_id0821200912504010\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id0821200912421569\" src=\"xmlsecurity/res/certificate_16.svg\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id0821200912421569\">Icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id0821200912421569\" src=\"xmlsecurity/res/certificate_16.svg\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id0821200912421569\">ໄອຄອນ</alt></image>"

#. YC276
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id0821200912504189\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The signature is valid."
msgstr "ລາຍເຊັນຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. 742D2
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id082120091250418\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id0821200912431081\" src=\"xmlsecurity/res/notcertificate_16.svg\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id0821200912431081\">Icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id0821200912431081\" src=\"xmlsecurity/res/notcertificate_16.svg\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id0821200912431081\">ໄອຄອນ</alt></image>"

#. FE8hU
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id0821200912504133\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The signature is OK, but the certificates could not be validated."
msgstr "ລາຍເຊັນປົກກະຕິ, ແຕ່ບໍ່ສາມາດກວດສອບໃບຢັ້ງຢືນໄດ້."

#. zeGdn
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id0821200912504165\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The signature and the certificate are OK, but not all parts of the document are signed. (For documents that were signed with old versions of the software, see note below.)"
msgstr "ລາຍເຊັນ ແລະ ໃບຢັ້ງຢືນປົກກະຕິ, ແຕ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນທຸກພາກສ່ວນຂອງເອກະສານທີ່ຖືກເຊັນ. (ສຳລັບເອກະສານທີ່ເຊັນດ້ວຍຊອບແວເວີຊັນເກົ່າ, ໃຫ້ເບິ່ງໝາຍເຫດດ້ານລຸ່ມ.)"

#. cbqD3
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id0821200912504237\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id0821200912435090\" src=\"svx/res/caution_11x16.png\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id0821200912435090\">Icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id0821200912435090\" src=\"svx/res/caution_11x16.png\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id0821200912435090\">ໄອຄອນ</alt></image>"

#. h98zw
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id0821200912504233\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The signature is invalid."
msgstr "ລາຍເຊັນບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. NPFGu
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"hd_id0821200910191787\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Signatures and software versions"
msgstr "ລາຍເຊັນ ແລະ ເວີຊັນຊອບແວ"

#. MfHxN
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id0821200910191747\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The signing of contents got changed with OpenOffice.org 3.2 and StarOffice 9.2. Now all contents of the files, except the signature file itself (META-INF/documentsignatures.xml) are signed."
msgstr "ວິທີການເຊັນເນື້ອໃນໄດ້ປ່ຽນແປງຕັ້ງແຕ່ OpenOffice.org 3.2 ແລະ StarOffice 9.2. ຕອນນີ້ເນື້ອໃນທັງໝົດຂອງໄຟລ໌, ຍົກເວັ້ນໄຟລ໌ລາຍເຊັນ (META-INF/documentsignatures.xml), ຈະຖືກເຊັນທັງໝົດ."

#. sebAM
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id0821200910191774\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you sign a document with OpenOffice.org 3.2 or StarOffice 9.2 or a later version, and you open that document in an older version of the software, the signature will be displayed as \"invalid\". Signatures created with older versions of the software will be marked with \"only parts of the document are signed\" when loaded in the newer software."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານເຊັນເອກະສານດ້ວຍ OpenOffice.org 3.2 ຫຼື StarOffice 9.2 ຫຼື ເວີຊັນໃໝ່ກວ່າ, ແລ້ວນຳໄປເປີດໃນຊອບແວເວີຊັນເກົ່າ, ລາຍເຊັນຈະສະແດງເປັນ \"ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ\". ສ່ວນລາຍເຊັນທີ່ສ້າງດ້ວຍຊອບແວເວີຊັນເກົ່າ ເມື່ອມາເປີດໃນຊອບແວເວີຊັນໃໝ່ ຈະຖືກໝາຍວ່າ \"ມີພຽງບາງສ່ວນຂອງເອກະສານທີ່ຖືກເຊັນ\"."

#. oct56
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id0821200910191775\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you sign an OOXML document, then the signature will be always marked with \"only parts of the document are signed\". Metadata of OOXML files are never signed, to be compatible with Microsoft Office."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານເຊັນເອກະສານ OOXML, ລາຍເຊັນຈະຖືກໝາຍວ່າ \"ມີພຽງບາງສ່ວນຂອງເອກະສານທີ່ຖືກເຊັນ\" ສະເໝີ. ເນື່ອງຈາກ Metadata ຂອງໄຟລ໌ OOXML ຈະບໍ່ຖືກເຊັນ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ສາມາດໃຊ້ຮ່ວມກັບ Microsoft Office ໄດ້."

#. s8DpC
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id0821200910191776\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you sign a PDF document, then this marking is not used. Signing only parts of the document is simply an invalid signature."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານເຊັນເອກະສານ PDF, ຈະບໍ່ມີການໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງໝາຍນີ້. ການເຊັນພຽງບາງສ່ວນຂອງເອກະສານ PDF ຖືວ່າເປັນລາຍເຊັນທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. vtpDw
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id0821200910191777\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Signing other document formats is not supported at the moment."
msgstr "ໃນເວລານີ້ ຍັງບໍ່ທັນຮອງຮັບການເຊັນໃນຮູບແບບເອກະສານອື່ນໆ."

#. ASs3q
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id2008200911583098\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you load an ODF document, you might see an icon in the status bar and the status field in the dialog that indicates that the document is only partially signed. This status will appear when the signature and certificate are valid, but they were created with a version of OpenOffice.org before 3.2 or StarOffice before 9.2. In versions of OpenOffice.org before 3.0 or StarOffice before 9.0, the document signature was applied to the main contents, pictures and embedded objects only and some contents, like macros, were not signed. In OpenOffice.org 3.0 and StarOffice 9.0 the document signature was applied to most content, including macros. However, the mimetype and the content of the META-INF folder were not signed. And in OpenOffice.org 3.2, StarOffice 9.2, and all versions of LibreOffice all contents, except the signature file itself (META-INF/documentsignatures.xml), are signed."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານໂຫຼດເອກະສານ ODF, ທ່ານອາດຈະເຫັນໄອຄອນໃນແຖບສະຖານະທີ່ບົ່ງບອກວ່າເອກະສານຖືກເຊັນພຽງບາງສ່ວນ. ສະຖານະນີ້ຈະປາກົດເມື່ອລາຍເຊັນ ແລະ ໃບຢັ້ງຢືນຖືກຕ້ອງ, ແຕ່ຖືກສ້າງດ້ວຍ OpenOffice.org ເວີຊັນກ່ອນ 3.2 ຫຼື StarOffice ກ່ອນ 9.2. ໃນເວີຊັນກ່ອນ 3.0, ລາຍເຊັນຈະຖືກໃຊ້ກັບເນື້ອໃນຫຼັກ, ຮູບພາບ ແລະ ວັດຖຸຝັງຕົວເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ແຕ່ມາໂຄຣຈະບໍ່ຖືກເຊັນ. ໃນ OpenOffice.org 3.0, ລາຍເຊັນຈະກວມເອົາເນື້ອໃນສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ລວມທັງມາໂຄຣ, ແຕ່ mimetype ແລະ ໂຟນເດີ META-INF ຍັງບໍ່ຖືກເຊັນ. ແລະ ໃນເວີຊັນ 3.2 ເປັນຕົ້ນມາ, ເນື້ອໃນທັງໝົດຍົກເວັ້ນໄຟລ໌ລາຍເຊັນເອງ ຈະຖືກເຊັນທັງໝົດ."

#. ATyHA
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"hd_id9354228\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Security Warnings"
msgstr "ຄຳເຕືອນຄວາມປອດໄພ"

#. aEJFT
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id2372508\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you receive a signed document, and the software reports that the signature is valid, this does not mean that you can be absolutely sure that the document is the same that the sender has sent. Signing documents with software certificates is not a perfectly secure method. Numerous ways are possible to circumvent the security features."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບເອກະສານທີ່ເຊັນແລ້ວ ແລະ ຊອບແວແຈ້ງວ່າລາຍເຊັນຖືກຕ້ອງ, ນັ້ນບໍ່ໄດ້ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າທ່ານຈະໝັ້ນໃຈໄດ້ເຕັມຮ້ອຍວ່າເອກະສານນັ້ນແມ່ນອັນດຽວກັບທີ່ຜູ້ສົ່ງສົ່ງມາ. ການເຊັນເອກະສານດ້ວຍໃບຢັ້ງຢືນຊອບແວບໍ່ແມ່ນວິທີທີ່ປອດໄພທີ່ສຸດ, ເພາະຍັງມີຫຼາຍວິທີທີ່ຈະຫຼົບຫຼີກຄຸນສົມບັດຄວາມປອດໄພໄດ້."

#. HbiMb
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id7953123\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Example: Think about someone who wants to camouflage his identity to be a sender from your bank. He can easily get a certificate using a false name, then send you any signed email pretending he is working for your bank. You will get that email, and the email or the document within has the \"valid signed\" icon."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ: ສົມມຸດວ່າມີຄົນຕ້ອງການປອມແປງຕົວຕົນເປັນຜູ້ສົ່ງຈາກທະນາຄານຂອງທ່ານ. ເຂົາສາມາດຂໍໃບຢັ້ງຢືນໂດຍໃຊ້ຊື່ປອມໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ, ແລ້ວສົ່ງອີເມລ໌ທີ່ເຊັນແລ້ວມາຫາທ່ານໂດຍອ້າງວ່າເຮັດວຽກຢູ່ທະນາຄານ. ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຮັບອີເມລ໌ນັ້ນ ແລະ ມັນຈະສະແດງໄອຄອນ \"ລາຍເຊັນຖືກຕ້ອງ\"."

#. DGz9C
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id6195257\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Do not trust the icon. Inspect and verify the certificates."
msgstr "ຢ່າໄວ້ວາງໃຈພຽງແຕ່ໄອຄອນ. ໃຫ້ກວດສອບ ແລະ ຢັ້ງຢືນໃບຢັ້ງຢືນໃຫ້ລະອຽດ."

#. 86jSG
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id8635517\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The validation of a signature is not a legally binding guarantee of any kind."
msgstr "ການກວດສອບລາຍເຊັນບໍ່ແມ່ນການຮັບປະກັນທີ່ມີຜົນຜູກພັນທາງກົດໝາຍແຕ່ຢ່າງໃດ."

#. RxBMt
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id6075624\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On Windows operating systems, the Windows features of validating a signature are used. On Solaris and Linux systems, files that are supplied by Thunderbird, Mozilla or Firefox are used. You must ensure that the files that are in use within your system are really the original files that were supplied by the original developers. For malevolent intruders, there are numerous ways to replace original files with other files that they supply."
msgstr "ໃນລະບົບ Windows, ຈະໃຊ້ຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງ Windows ໃນການກວດສອບລາຍເຊັນ. ໃນລະບົບ Solaris ແລະ Linux, ຈະໃຊ້ໄຟລ໌ຈາກ Thunderbird, Mozilla ຫຼື Firefox. ທ່ານຕ້ອງໝັ້ນໃຈວ່າໄຟລ໌ທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນລະບົບຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ແທ້ຈາກຜູ້ພັດທະນາ, ເພາະຜູ້ບຸກລຸກອາດມີຫຼາຍວິທີໃນການປ່ຽນໄຟລ໌ແທ້ເປັນໄຟລ໌ທີ່ພວກເຂົາສ້າງຂຶ້ນ."

#. ey4VP
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id6819971\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The messages about validation of a signature that you see in %PRODUCTNAME are the messages that the validation files return. The %PRODUCTNAME software has no way to ensure that the messages reflect the true status of any certificate. The %PRODUCTNAME software only displays the messages that other files that are not under control of %PRODUCTNAME report. There is no legal responsibility of %PRODUCTNAME that the displayed messages reflect the true status of a digital signature."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຄວາມກ່ຽວກັບການກວດສອບລາຍເຊັນທີ່ທ່ານເຫັນໃນ %PRODUCTNAME ແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ສົ່ງຄືນມາຈາກໄຟລ໌ກວດສອບ. ຊອບແວ %PRODUCTNAME ບໍ່ມີວິທີການໃດທີ່ຈະຢັ້ງຢືນໄດ້ວ່າຂໍ້ຄວາມເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນສະທ້ອນເຖິງສະຖານະທີ່ແທ້ຈິງຂອງໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ. %PRODUCTNAME ພຽງແຕ່ສະແດງຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ລາຍງານໂດຍໄຟລ໌ອື່ນທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ຢູ່ພາຍໃຕ້ການຄວບຄຸມຂອງ %PRODUCTNAME. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, %PRODUCTNAME ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ມີຄວາມຮັບຜິດຊອບທາງກົດໝາຍຕໍ່ຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງຂອງສະຖານະລາຍເຊັນທີ່ສະແດງອອກມາ."

#. DsCBF
#: digital_signatures.xhp
msgctxt ""
"digital_signatures.xhp\n"
"par_id3204443\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/How_to_use_digital_Signatures\">English Wiki page on digital signatures</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/How_to_use_digital_Signatures\">ໜ້າ English Wiki ກ່ຽວກັບລາຍເຊັນດິຈິຕອນ</link>"

