msgstr "ເລືອກ <menuitem>ໄຟລ໌ – ເປີດ</menuitem>"

#. AAFFU
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
"par_id210820160859353525\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose<menuitem> File – Open Remote</menuitem>"
msgstr "ເລືອກ <menuitem>ໄຟລ໌ – ເປີດຈາກທາງໄກ</menuitem>"

#. QWFLw
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
"par_id210820160901392820\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Do a long click in the <emph>Open</emph> icon on the standard toolbar and select <emph>Open Remote File</emph> in the bottom of the list."
msgstr "ຄລິກຄ້າງໄວ້ທີ່ໄອຄອນ <emph>ເປີດ</emph> ໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມືມາດຕະຖານ ແລະ ເລືອກ <emph>ເປີດໄຟລ໌ຈາກທາງໄກ</emph> ຢູ່ທາງລຸ່ມຂອງລາຍການ."

#. DCCtG
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
"par_id3149164\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the file you want to open and click <emph>Open</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກໄຟລ໌ທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເປີດ ແລະ ຄລິກ <emph>ເປີດ</emph>."

#. 4WgFF
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149234\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Restrict Files to Display"
msgstr "ຈຳກັດການສະແດງຜົນຂອງໄຟລ໌"

#. UBkeK
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
"par_id3150985\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To restrict the display of files in the <emph>Open</emph> dialog to a certain type select the corresponding <emph>File type</emph> from the list. Select <emph>All Files</emph> to display all files."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຈຳກັດການສະແດງຜົນຂອງໄຟລ໌ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ເປີດ</emph> ໃຫ້ສະແດງສະເພາະບາງປະເພດ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <emph>ປະເພດໄຟລ໌</emph> ທີ່ຕ້ອງການຈາກລາຍການ. ເລືອກ <emph>ທຸກໄຟລ໌</emph> ເພື່ອສະແດງໄຟລ໌ທັງໝົດ."

#. eHAhk
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
