msgstr "ຕຳແໜ່ງເຄີເຊີ"

#. rB6C2
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
"par_id5509201\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In general, all documents open with the cursor at the start of the document."
msgstr "ໂດຍທົ່ວໄປແລ້ວ, ທຸກເອກະສານຈະຖືກເປີດຂຶ້ນມາໂດຍມີເຄີເຊີຢູ່ທີ່ຕອນຕົ້ນຂອງເອກະສານ."

#. DBPFu
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
"par_id6594744\n"
"help.text"
msgid "One exception appears when the author of a Writer text document saves and reopens a document: The cursor will be at the same position where it has been when the document was saved. This only works when the name of the author was entered in <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>Tools - Options</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline><menuitem> - %PRODUCTNAME - User Data</menuitem>."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຍົກເວັ້ນໜຶ່ງຄື ເມື່ອຜູ້ຂຽນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ Writer ບັນທຶກ ແລະ ເປີດເອກະສານຄືນໃໝ່: ເຄີເຊີຈະຢູ່ທີ່ຕຳແໜ່ງເດີມກ່ອນການບັນທຶກ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະໃຊ້ໄດ້ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອມີການລະບຸຊື່ຜູ້ຂຽນໄວ້ໃນ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline><menuitem> - %PRODUCTNAME - ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້</menuitem>."

#. aLKzF
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
"par_id3422650\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <keycode>Shift+F5</keycode> to set the cursor to the last saved position."
msgstr "ກົດ <keycode>Shift+F5</keycode> ເພື່ອຕັ້ງເຄີເຊີໄປທີ່ຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ບັນທຶກໄວ້ຫຼ້າສຸດ."

#. FRWxv
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148453\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opening an Empty Document"
msgstr "ການເປີດເອກະສານຫວ່າງເປົ່າ"

#. 75a2A
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
"par_id3147287\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the <emph>New</emph> icon on the Standard bar or choose <emph>File - New</emph>. This opens a document of the document type specified."
msgstr "ຄລິກໄອຄອນ <emph>ສ້າງໃໝ່</emph> ໃນແຖບມາດຕະຖານ ຫຼື ເລືອກ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ສ້າງໃໝ່</emph>. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະເປີດເອກະສານຕາມປະເພດທີ່ລະບຸໄວ້."

#. Rcfnt
#: doc_open.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_open.xhp\n"
"par_id3153092\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you click the arrow next to the <emph>New</emph> icon, a submenu opens in which you can select another document type."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຄລິກລູກສອນຂ້າງໄອຄອນ <emph>ສ້າງໃໝ່</emph>, ເມນູຍ່ອຍຈະເປີດຂຶ້ນມາເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານເລືອກປະເພດເອກະສານອື່ນ."

#. RFE99
