"par_id3155450\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id3152349\" src=\"cmd/sc_save.png\" width=\"0.222inch\" height=\"0.222inch\"><alt id=\"alt_id3152349\">This icon is for tips on how to use the program more effectively.</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id3152349\" src=\"cmd/sc_save.png\" width=\"0.222inch\" height=\"0.222inch\"><alt id=\"alt_id3152349\">ໄອຄອນນີ້ສຳລັບຄຳແນະນຳໃນການໃຊ້ໂປຣແກຣມໃຫ້ມີປະສິດທິພາບຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນ.</alt></image>"

#. Ax4rn
#: doc_save.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_save.xhp\n"
"par_id3148685\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The document is saved under its path and name on the current local data medium or network drive or on the Internet, overwriting any file of the same name."
msgstr "ເອກະສານຈະຖືກບັນທຶກຕາມເສັ້ນທາງ ແລະ ຊື່ຂອງມັນໄວ້ໃນບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນພາຍໃນເຄື່ອງ, ໄດຣຟ໌ເຄືອຂ່າຍ ຫຼື ອິນເຕີເນັດ, ໂດຍຈະຂຽນທັບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຊື່ດຽວກັນ."

#. nXqWZ
#: doc_save.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_save.xhp\n"
"par_id3150984\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you save a new file for the first time, the <link href=\"text/shared/01/01070000.xhp\">Save As</link> dialog opens, in which you can enter a name, folder and drive or volume for the file. To open this dialog, choose <emph>File - Save As</emph>."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ໃໝ່ເປັນຄັ້ງທຳອິດ, ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <link href=\"text/shared/01/01070000.xhp\">ບັນທຶກເປັນ</link> ຈະເປີດຂຶ້ນມາ, ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນຊື່, ໂຟນເດີ ແລະ ໄດຣຟ໌ສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ນັ້ນ. ເພື່ອເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບນີ້, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ບັນທຶກເປັນ</emph>."

#. P2oCF
#: doc_save.xhp
msgctxt ""
"doc_save.xhp\n"
"par_id3152472\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can set the automatic creation of a backup copy under <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - </emph><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010200.xhp\"><emph>Load/Save - General</emph></link>."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າການສ້າງສຳເນົາສຳຮອງອັດຕະໂນມັດໄດ້ທີ່ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - </emph><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010200.xhp\"><emph>ໂຫຼດ/ບັນທຶກ - ທົ່ວໄປ</emph></link>."

