msgctxt ""
"doc_save.xhp\n"
"par_id9359111\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When saving a file, %PRODUCTNAME always appends an extension to the file name, except when the file name already has an extension that matches the file type. See the list of <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000021.xhp\">ODF extensions</link>."
msgstr "ໃນເວລາບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌, %PRODUCTNAME ຈະຕື່ມນາມສະກຸນໃຫ້ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ສະເໝີ, ຍົກເວັ້ນເມື່ອຊື່ໄຟລ໌ນັ້ນມີນາມສະກຸນທີ່ກົງກັບປະເພດໄຟລ໌ຢູ່ແລ້ວ. ເບິ່ງລາຍການຂອງ <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000021.xhp\">ນາມສະກຸນ ODF</link>."

