#. DccCG
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3151111\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A fast way of copying from a data source into a text or spreadsheet document, or of creating forms based on a data source, is by drag-and-drop."
msgstr "ວິທີທີ່ໄວໃນການສຳເນົາຈາກແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນເຂົ້າໃນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ສະເປຣດຊີດ, ຫຼື ການສ້າງແບບຟອມໂດຍອີງໃສ່ແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ ຄືການລາກ ແລະ ວາງ."

#. E7H73
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3147335\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id3155390\" src=\"media/helpimg/copydata.png\" width=\"8.47mm\" height=\"8.47mm\"><alt id=\"alt_id3155390\">Mouse pointer copying data</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id3155390\" src=\"media/helpimg/copydata.png\" width=\"8.47mm\" height=\"8.47mm\"><alt id=\"alt_id3155390\">ຕົວຊີ້ເມົ້າກຳລັງສຳເນົາຂໍ້ມູນ</alt></image>"

#. QMv2i
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3145315\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Copying with Drag-and-Drop"
msgstr "ການສຳເນົາດ້ວຍການລາກ ແລະ ວາງ"

#. Fv3t2
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3149233\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you want to reverse a drag-and-drop, position the cursor in your document and choose <emph>Edit - Undo</emph>."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການຍົກເລີກການລາກ ແລະ ວາງ, ໃຫ້ວາງເຄີເຊີໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ເລືອກ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂ - ກັບຄືນ</emph>."

#. QFekQ
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3149656\n"
"help.text"
msgid "It is also possible to copy by drag-and-drop from a document into a data source:"
msgstr "ນອກຈາກນີ້ຍັງສາມາດສຳເນົາໂດຍການລາກ ແລະ ວາງ ຈາກເອກະສານເຂົ້າໃນແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ:"

#. wUEpZ
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3153379\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A text table or the selected range of a spreadsheet can be dragged using drag-and-drop to a table container in the data source explorer."
msgstr "ຕາຕະລາງຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ຊ່ວງທີ່ເລືອກໃນສະເປຣດຊີດ ສາມາດລາກໂດຍໃຊ້ການລາກ ແລະ ວາງ ໄປທີ່ບ່ອນເກັບຕາຕະລາງໃນຕົວສຳຫຼວດແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. fHvuU
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3151211\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Plain text can be copied using drag-and-drop from one document to a data field in the data source view."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຄວາມທຳມະດາສາມາດສຳເນົາໄດ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ການລາກ ແລະ ວາງ ຈາກເອກະສານໜຶ່ງໄປຫາຟີລຂໍ້ມູນໃນມຸມມອງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. oqs3E
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145421\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Using data in a text document"
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ຂໍ້ມູນໃນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ"

#. YtpUf
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3154685\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can insert a database field in a text document by dragging a field name from the column header of the data source view into the document. This is especially useful when designing form letters. Simply drag the desired fields - home address, form of address, and so on - into your document."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດແຊກຟີລຖານຂໍ້ມູນໃນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມໄດ້ໂດຍການລາກຊື່ຟີລຈາກຫົວຖັນຂອງມຸມມອງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນເຂົ້າໄປໃນເອກະສານ. ສິ່ງນີ້ມີປະໂຫຍດຫຼາຍໃນເວລາອອກແບບຈົດໝາຍວຽນ. ພຽງແຕ່ລາກຟີລທີ່ຕ້ອງການ - ເຊັ່ນ ທີ່ຢູ່, ຄຳນຳໜ້າຊື່ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ - ເຂົ້າໄປໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ."

#. XtqH7
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3153105\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To insert a complete record, select the corresponding header and drag it into the document. When you release the mouse button, the <link href=\"text/shared/02/12070000.xhp\"><emph>Insert database columns</emph></link> dialog appears, in which you can decide whether to use all database fields, and whether to copy the data into the document as text, a table or fields. All currently selected records will be inserted."
msgstr "ເພື່ອແຊກຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດໃນແຖວນັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກສ່ວນຫົວທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ ແລະ ລາກມັນເຂົ້າໄປໃນເອກະສານ. ເມື່ອທ່ານປ່ອຍປຸ່ມເມົ້າ, ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <link href=\"text/shared/02/12070000.xhp\"><emph>ແຊກຖັນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ</emph></link> ຈະປາກົດຂຶ້ນ, ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດຕັດສິນໃຈໄດ້ວ່າຈະໃຊ້ທຸກຟີລຖານຂໍ້ມູນ ຫຼື ຈະສຳເນົາຂໍ້ມູນເຂົ້າໃນເອກະສານໃນຮູບແບບຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ຕາຕະລາງ ຫຼື ຟີລ. ທຸກແຖວຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ຈະຖືກແຊກເຂົ້າໄປ."

#. FfBFe
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147230\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Applying data to a table document"
msgstr "ການນຳໃຊ້ຂໍ້ມູນກັບເອກະສານຕາຕະລາງ"

#. LE87C
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3125864\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can insert one or more records into the current sheet of a spreadsheet by selecting the rows in the data source view and dragging and dropping them into the spreadsheet. The data is inserted at the place where you release the mouse button."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດແຊກຂໍ້ມູນໜຶ່ງແຖວ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍກວ່ານັ້ນເຂົ້າໃນແຜ່ນງານປັດຈຸບັນຂອງສະເປຣດຊີດໄດ້ໂດຍການເລືອກແຖວໃນມຸມມອງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ ແລ້ວລາກ ແລະ ວາງ ພວກມັນລົງໃນສະເປຣດຊີດ. ຂໍ້ມູນຈະຖືກແຊກລົງໃນຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ທ່ານປ່ອຍປຸ່ມເມົ້າ."

#. cC3Uk
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149766\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Inserting controls in a text form"
msgstr "ການແຊກຕົວຄວບຄຸມໃນແບບຟອມຂໍ້ຄວາມ"

#. fhwzN
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3155132\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you create a text form linked to a database, you can generate controls by drag-and-drop from the data source view."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານສ້າງແບບຟອມຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບຖານຂໍ້ມູນ, ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງຕົວຄວບຄຸມໄດ້ໂດຍການລາກ ແລະ ວາງ ຈາກມຸມມອງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. hpF4V
#: dragdrop_beamer.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_beamer.xhp\n"
"par_id3149562\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you drag a database column into the text document, you insert a field. If you hold down Shift+<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline> while dragging, a text field is inserted, grouped with an appropriate label field. The text field already contains all the database information that you need for the form."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານລາກຖັນຖານຂໍ້ມູນເຂົ້າໃນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ທ່ານກຳລັງແຊກຟີລ. ຖ້າທ່ານກົດ Shift+<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ລາກ, ຟີລຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກແຊກເຂົ້າໄປ ແລະ ຈັດກຸ່ມກັບຟີລປ້າຍຊື່ທີ່ເໝາະສົມ. ຟີລຂໍ້ຄວາມນັ້ນຈະມີຂໍ້ມູນຖານຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດທີ່ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງໃຊ້ສຳລັບແບບຟອມ."

#. 6HANC
#: dragdrop_gallery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_gallery.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Adding Graphics to the Gallery"
msgstr "ການເພີ່ມຮູບພາບເຂົ້າໃນຄັງຮູບ"

#. abH9P
#: dragdrop_gallery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_gallery.xhp\n"
"bm_id3154927\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>drag and drop;to Gallery</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>copying;to Gallery</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>Gallery; adding pictures</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>pictures;adding to Gallery</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>inserting;pictures in Gallery</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>pasting;to Gallery</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ລາກ ແລະ ວາງ; ໄປທີ່ຄັງຮູບ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການສຳເນົາ; ໄປທີ່ຄັງຮູບ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຄັງຮູບ; ການເພີ່ມຮູບພາບ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຮູບພາບ; ການເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນຄັງຮູບ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການແຊກ; ຮູບພາບໃນຄັງຮູບ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການວາງ; ໄປທີ່ຄັງຮູບ</bookmark_value>"

#. jz7Ss
#: dragdrop_gallery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_gallery.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154927\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"dragdrop_gallery\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/dragdrop_gallery.xhp\">Adding Graphics to the Gallery</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"dragdrop_gallery\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/dragdrop_gallery.xhp\">ການເພີ່ມຮູບພາບເຂົ້າໃນຄັງຮູບ</link></variable>"

#. uTcum
#: dragdrop_gallery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_gallery.xhp\n"
"par_id3143267\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can place a graphic from a document such as an HTML page in the Gallery by drag-and-drop."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດວາງຮູບພາບຈາກເອກະສານ ເຊັ່ນ ໜ້າ HTML ລົງໃນຄັງຮູບໄດ້ໂດຍການລາກ ແລະ ວາງ."

#. VF5Eh
#: dragdrop_gallery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_gallery.xhp\n"
"par_id3154823\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Display the Gallery theme to which you want to add the graphic."
msgstr "ສະແດງຫົວຂໍ້ຄັງຮູບທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເພີ່ມຮູບພາບເຂົ້າໄປ."

#. 4e3Bd
#: dragdrop_gallery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_gallery.xhp\n"
"par_id3153748\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Position the mouse pointer above the graphic, without clicking."
msgstr "ວາງຕົວຊີ້ເມົ້າໄວ້ເທິງຮູບພາບ ໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງຄລິກ."

#. Cqj8v
#: dragdrop_gallery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_gallery.xhp\n"
"par_id3156346\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the mouse pointer changes to a hand symbol, the graphic refers to a hyperlink. In this case, click the graphic while pressing the <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> key to select it without executing the respective link."
msgstr "ຖ້າຕົວຊີ້ເມົ້າປ່ຽນເປັນຮູບມື, ສະແດງວ່າຮູບພາບນັ້ນມີໄຮເປີລິ້ງ. ໃນກໍລະນີນີ້, ໃຫ້ຄລິກທີ່ຮູບພາບໃນຂະນະທີ່ກົດປຸ່ມ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> ເພື່ອເລືອກມັນໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງເປີດລິ້ງນັ້ນ."

#. dHgTd
#: dragdrop_gallery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_gallery.xhp\n"
"par_id3149578\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the mouse pointer does not change to a hand symbol, you can simply click the graphic to select it."
msgstr "ຖ້າຕົວຊີ້ເມົ້າບໍ່ປ່ຽນເປັນຮູບມື, ທ່ານສາມາດຄລິກທີ່ຮູບພາບເພື່ອເລືອກມັນໄດ້ເລີຍ."

#. g9rmw
#: dragdrop_gallery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_gallery.xhp\n"
"par_id3145120\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Once the graphic is selected, release the mouse button. Click again on the graphic image, keeping the mouse button pressed for more than two seconds. The graphic image is copied to the internal memory."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເລືອກຮູບພາບແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ປ່ອຍປຸ່ມເມົ້າ. ຈາກນັ້ນຄລິກໃສ່ຮູບພາບອີກຄັ້ງໂດຍກົດປຸ່ມເມົ້າຄ້າງໄວ້ຫຼາຍກວ່າສອງວິນາທີ. ຮູບພາບຈະຖືກສຳເນົາໄວ້ໃນໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳພາຍໃນ."

#. 5CZ9c
#: dragdrop_gallery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_gallery.xhp\n"
"par_id3150772\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Without releasing the mouse button, drag the graphic into the Gallery."
msgstr "ໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງປ່ອຍປຸ່ມເມົ້າ, ໃຫ້ລາກຮູບພາບນັ້ນເຂົ້າໄປໃນຄັງຮູບ."

#. d55VF
#: dragdrop_graphic.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_graphic.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Copying Graphics Between Documents"
msgstr "ການສຳເນົາຮູບພາບລະຫວ່າງເອກະສານ"

#. rp8Bd
#: dragdrop_graphic.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_graphic.xhp\n"
"bm_id3159201\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>drag and drop; pictures</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>pictures; drag and drop between documents</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>copying;pictures, between documents</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>pasting;pictures from other documents</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ລາກ ແລະ ວາງ; ຮູບພາບ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຮູບພາບ; ລາກ ແລະ ວາງ ລະຫວ່າງເອກະສານ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການສຳເນົາ; ຮູບພາບ, ລະຫວ່າງເອກະສານ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການວາງ; ຮູບພາບຈາກເອກະສານອື່ນ</bookmark_value>"

#. wvBaB
#: dragdrop_graphic.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_graphic.xhp\n"
"hd_id3159201\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"dragdrop_graphic\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/dragdrop_graphic.xhp\">Copying Graphics Between Documents</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"dragdrop_graphic\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/dragdrop_graphic.xhp\">ການສຳເນົາຮູບພາບລະຫວ່າງເອກະສານ</link></variable>"

#. uY53F
#: dragdrop_graphic.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_graphic.xhp\n"
"par_id3155805\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can copy a graphic from one document to another by drag-and-drop. If you plan to publish your document, please observe copyright laws and obtain the consent of the authors."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດສຳເນົາຮູບພາບຈາກເອກະສານໜຶ່ງໄປຫາອີກເອກະສານໜຶ່ງໄດ້ໂດຍການລາກ ແລະ ວາງ. ຖ້າທ່ານມີແຜນຈະເຜີຍແຜ່ເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ, ກະລຸນາປະຕິບັດຕາມກົດໝາຍລິຂະສິດ ແລະ ຂໍອະນຸຍາດຈາກຜູ້ຂຽນ."

#. BDXTz
#: dragdrop_graphic.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_graphic.xhp\n"
"par_id3147576\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open the document in which you want to insert the graphic object."
msgstr "ເປີດເອກະສານທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແຊກວັດຖຸຮູບພາບ."

#. rgfLj
#: dragdrop_graphic.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_graphic.xhp\n"
"par_id3155338\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open the document from which you want to copy the graphic."
msgstr "ເປີດເອກະສານທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການສຳເນົາຮູບພາບອອກມາ."

#. u9EK5
#: dragdrop_graphic.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_graphic.xhp\n"
"par_id3149182\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the graphic while pressing the <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> key, to select it without executing any hyperlinks it may refer to."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ຮູບພາບໃນຂະນະທີ່ກົດປຸ່ມ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> ເພື່ອເລືອກມັນໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງເປີດໄຮເປີລິ້ງໃດໆ."

#. GAFBF
#: dragdrop_graphic.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_graphic.xhp\n"
"par_id3151110\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Keep the mouse button pressed and wait a moment while the object is copied to an internal memory."
msgstr "ກົດປຸ່ມເມົ້າຄ້າງໄວ້ ແລະ ລໍຖ້າຈັກໜ້ອຍເພື່ອໃຫ້ວັດຖຸຖືກສຳເນົາໄວ້ໃນໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳພາຍໃນ."

#. erDMd
#: dragdrop_graphic.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_graphic.xhp\n"
"par_id3149763\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Drag the graphic into the other document. <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"WIN\">If the documents are not visible side by side, first move the mouse pointer to the button of the target document while keeping the mouse button pressed. The document in question is then displayed and you can move the mouse pointer into the document.</caseinline></switchinline>"
msgstr "ລາກຮູບພາບເຂົ້າໄປໃນອີກເອກະສານໜຶ່ງ. <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"WIN\">ຖ້າເອກະສານທັງສອງບໍ່ໄດ້ສະແດງຄຽງຂ້າງກັນ, ໃຫ້ເລື່ອນຕົວຊີ້ເມົ້າໄປທີ່ປຸ່ມຂອງເອກະສານປາຍທາງໃນຂະນະທີ່ຍັງກົດປຸ່ມເມົ້າຄ້າງໄວ້. ເອກະສານນັ້ນຈະປາກົດຂຶ້ນມາ ແລະ ທ່ານສາມາດເລື່ອນຕົວຊີ້ເມົ້າເຂົ້າໄປໃນເອກະສານໄດ້.</caseinline></switchinline>"

#. gJ2Zh
#: dragdrop_graphic.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_graphic.xhp\n"
"par_id3155628\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Release the mouse button as soon as the gray text cursor indicates the position where you want to insert a copy of the picture."
msgstr "ປ່ອຍປຸ່ມເມົ້າເມື່ອເຄີເຊີຂໍ້ຄວາມສີເທົາສະແດງຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແຊກສຳເນົາຂອງຮູບພາບ."

#. QiMzE
#: dragdrop_graphic.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_graphic.xhp\n"
"par_id3150276\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the graphic is connected with a hyperlink, the hyperlink and not the graphic is inserted."
msgstr "ຖ້າຮູບພາບນັ້ນເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບໄຮເປີລິ້ງ, ໄຮເປີລິ້ງຈະຖືກແຊກເຂົ້າໄປແທນທີ່ຮູບພາບ."

#. isBwa
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Copying Spreadsheet Areas to Text Documents"
msgstr "ການສຳເນົາຊ່ວງສະເປຣດຊີດໄປຫາເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ"

#. odK27
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"bm_id3154927\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>spreadsheets; copying areas to text documents</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>copying; sheet areas, to text documents</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>pasting;sheet areas in text documents</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ສະເປຣດຊີດ; ການສຳເນົາຊ່ວງໄປຫາເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການສຳເນົາ; ຊ່ວງແຜ່ນງານ, ໄປຫາເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການວາງ; ຊ່ວງແຜ່ນງານໃນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ</bookmark_value>"

#. BAXmU
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154927\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"dragdrop_table\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/dragdrop_table.xhp\">Copying Spreadsheet Areas to Text Documents</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"dragdrop_table\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/dragdrop_table.xhp\">ການສຳເນົາຊ່ວງສະເປຣດຊີດໄປຫາເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ</link></variable>"

#. eFT4S
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"par_id3155892\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open both the text document and the spreadsheet."
msgstr "ເປີດທັງເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ ແລະ ສະເປຣດຊີດ."

#. rKqKR
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"par_id3147088\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the sheet area you want to copy."
msgstr "ເລືອກຊ່ວງແຜ່ນງານທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການສຳເນົາ."

#. KeAKQ
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"par_id3149827\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Point to the selected area and press the mouse button. Keep the mouse button pressed for a moment, then drag the area into the text document."
msgstr "ຊີ້ໄປທີ່ຊ່ວງທີ່ເລືອກ ແລະ ກົດປຸ່ມເມົ້າ. ກົດປຸ່ມເມົ້າຄ້າງໄວ້ຈັກໜ້ອຍ, ຈາກນັ້ນລາກຊ່ວງນັ້ນເຂົ້າໄປໃນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#. sqkQt
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"par_id3152780\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"WIN\">If the documents are not visible next to each other, first drag the mouse pointer to the destination document button. Continue to hold down the mouse button. The document is displayed, and you can move the mouse pointer within the document.</caseinline></switchinline>"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"WIN\">ຖ້າເອກະສານທັງສອງບໍ່ໄດ້ສະແດງຄຽງຂ້າງກັນ, ໃຫ້ລາກຕົວຊີ້ເມົ້າໄປທີ່ປຸ່ມຂອງເອກະສານປາຍທາງກ່ອນ. ກົດປຸ່ມເມົ້າຄ້າງໄວ້ຕໍ່ໄປ. ເອກະສານນັ້ນຈະປາກົດຂຶ້ນມາ ແລະ ທ່ານສາມາດເລື່ອນຕົວຊີ້ເມົ້າພາຍໃນເອກະສານໄດ້.</caseinline></switchinline>"

#. tBJFk
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"par_id3156346\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Once the cursor is located in the place where you want to insert the sheet area, release the mouse button. The sheet area is inserted as an OLE object."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເຄີເຊີຢູ່ໃນຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແຊກຊ່ວງແຜ່ນງານແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ປ່ອຍປຸ່ມເມົ້າ. ຊ່ວງແຜ່ນງານນັ້ນຈະຖືກແຊກເປັນວັດຖຸ OLE."

#. BH35W
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"par_id3154047\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can select and edit the OLE object at any time."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂວັດຖຸ OLE ໄດ້ທຸກເວລາ."

#. QqoNM
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"par_id3149164\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To edit the OLE object, double-click on it."
msgstr "ເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂວັດຖຸ OLE, ໃຫ້ດັບເບິນຄລິກທີ່ວັດຖຸນັ້ນ."

#. 8DbMH
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"par_id3155389\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Alternatively, select the object and choose <menuitem>Edit - OLE Object - Edit</menuitem> or choose <menuitem>Edit</menuitem> from the context menu. You edit the object in its own frame within the text document, but you see the icons and menu commands needed for spreadsheets."
msgstr "ຫຼື ໃຫ້ເລືອກວັດຖຸນັ້ນ ແລະ ເລືອກ <menuitem>ແກ້ໄຂ - ວັດຖຸ OLE - ແກ້ໄຂ</menuitem> ຫຼື ເລືອກ <menuitem>ແກ້ໄຂ</menuitem> ຈາກເມນູລັດ. ທ່ານຈະແກ້ໄຂວັດຖຸໃນກອບຂອງມັນເອງພາຍໃນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ແຕ່ທ່ານຈະເຫັນໄອຄອນ ແລະ ຄຳສັ່ງເມນູທີ່ຈຳເປັນສຳລັບສະເປຣດຊີດ."

#. uFCGU
#: dragdrop_table.xhp
msgctxt ""
"dragdrop_table.xhp\n"
"par_id3154860\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Open</emph> to open the source document of the OLE object."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ເປີດ</emph> ເພື່ອເປີດເອກະສານຕົ້ນສະບັບຂອງວັດຖຸ OLE."

#. DLDrf
#: edit_symbolbar.xhp
msgctxt ""
"edit_symbolbar.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Adding Buttons to Toolbars"
msgstr "ການເພີ່ມປຸ່ມໃສ່ແຖບເຄື່ອງມື"

#. Cs2pQ
#: edit_symbolbar.xhp
msgctxt ""
"edit_symbolbar.xhp\n"
"bm_id3159201\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>customizing; toolbars</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>buttons;toolbars</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>toolbars;adding buttons</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>configuring; toolbars</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>editing; toolbars</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>inserting;buttons in toolbars</bookmark_value>"
