#. EE7PR
#: fax.xhp
msgctxt ""
"fax.xhp\n"
"par_id3156410\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To send a fax directly from $[officename], you need a fax modem and a fax driver that allows applications to communicate with the fax modem."
msgstr "ເພື່ອສົ່ງແຟັກໂດຍກົງຈາກ $[officename], ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີແຟັກໂມເດັມ ແລະ ໄດຣເວີແຟັກທີ່ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ແອັບພລິເຄຊັນສາມາດສື່ສານກັບແຟັກໂມເດັມໄດ້."

#. QrwDB
#: fax.xhp
msgctxt ""
"fax.xhp\n"
"hd_id3166410\n"
"help.text"
