#: fax.xhp
msgctxt ""
"fax.xhp\n"
"par_id3152996\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open the <emph>Print</emph> dialog by choosing <emph>File - Print</emph> and select the fax driver in the <emph>Name</emph> list box."
msgstr "ເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ພິມ</emph> ໂດຍການເລືອກ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ພິມ</emph> ແລະ ເລືອກໄດຣເວີແຟັກໃນຊ່ອງລາຍການ <emph>ຊື່</emph>."

#. jeN2h
#: fax.xhp
msgctxt ""
"fax.xhp\n"
"par_id3155135\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Clicking <emph>OK</emph> opens the dialog for your fax driver, where you can select the fax recipient."
msgstr "ການຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph> ຈະເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບສຳລັບໄດຣເວີແຟັກຂອງທ່ານ, ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກຜູ້ຮັບແຟັກໄດ້."

