#. tEXZD
#: fax.xhp
msgctxt ""
"fax.xhp\n"
"par_idN10712\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the <emph>Toolbars</emph> tab page, click the down arrow button to position the new icon where you want it. Click <emph>OK</emph>."
msgstr "ໃນແຖບ <emph>ແຖບເຄື່ອງມື</emph>, ໃຫ້ຄລິກປຸ່ມລູກສອນລົງເພື່ອວາງໄອຄອນໃໝ່ໃນຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ. ຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>."

#. rwhYF
#: fax.xhp
msgctxt ""
"fax.xhp\n"
"par_idN10715\n"
