"par_idN1069C\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the <emph>Drawing</emph> toolbar or on the <emph>Fontwork</emph> toolbar, click the <emph>Fontwork Gallery</emph> icon."
msgstr "ໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມື <emph>ການແຕ້ມ</emph> ຫຼື ໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມື <emph>Fontwork</emph>, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໄອຄອນ <emph>ຄັງ Fontwork</emph>."

