msgstr "<image id=\"img_id7040009\" src=\"cmd/lc_fontworkgalleryfloater.svg\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id7040009\">ໄອຄອນ ຄັງ Fontwork</alt></image>"

#. B5fwe
