msgctxt ""
"fontwork.xhp\n"
"par_idN106A0\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Fontwork Gallery</emph> dialog, select a Fontwork style and click <widget>OK</widget>."
msgstr "ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ຄັງ Fontwork</emph>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຮູບແບບ Fontwork ແລະ ຄລິກ <widget>ຕົກລົງ</widget>."

#. cMgr5
#: fontwork.xhp
msgctxt ""
"fontwork.xhp\n"
"par_idN10755\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The Fontwork object is inserted into your document. Fontwork objects are Custom Shapes. Using the <emph>3D Settings</emph> toolbar, you can switch the view at any time from 2D to 3D and back."
msgstr "ວັດຖຸ Fontwork ຈະຖືກແຊກເຂົ້າໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ. ວັດຖຸ Fontwork ແມ່ນຮູບຊົງທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງໄດ້. ໂດຍການໃຊ້ແຖບເຄື່ອງມື <emph>ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ 3 ມິຕິ</emph>, ທ່ານສາມາດສະຫຼັບມຸມມອງລະຫວ່າງ 2 ມິຕິ ແລະ 3 ມິຕິ ໄປມາໄດ້ທຸກເວລາ."

#. RcKoz
#: fontwork.xhp
msgctxt ""
"fontwork.xhp\n"
"par_idN106A4\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Double-click the object to enter text edit mode."
msgstr "ດັບເບິນຄລິກທີ່ວັດຖຸເພື່ອເຂົ້າສູ່ໂໝດແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

