msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ວັດຖຸ Fontwork. ຖ້າວັດຖຸ Fontwork ຖືກແຊກໄວ້ໃນພື້ນຫຼັງ, ໃຫ້ກົດປຸ່ມ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຄລິກ."

#. Zgax9
#: fontwork.xhp
msgctxt ""
"fontwork.xhp\n"
"par_idN106B8\n"
"help.text"
