"bm_id6888027\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>groups;entering/exiting/ungrouping</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>frames; selection frames</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>selecting;objects</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>exiting;groups</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>entering groups</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ungrouping groups</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>selection frames</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>multiple selection</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>marking, see selecting</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ກຸ່ມ; ການເຂົ້າ/ການອອກ/ການຍົກເລີກກຸ່ມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ກອບ; ກອບການເລືອກ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການເລືອກ; ວັດຖຸ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການອອກຈາກກຸ່ມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການເຂົ້າສູ່ກຸ່ມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການຍົກເລີກການຈັດກຸ່ມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ກອບການເລືອກ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການເລືອກຫຼາຍອັນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການໝາຍ, ເບິ່ງ ການເລືອກ</bookmark_value>"

#. ELar7
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"hd_id2454298\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"groups\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/groups.xhp\">Working with Groups</link> </variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"groups\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/groups.xhp\">ການເຮັດວຽກກັບກຸ່ມ</link> </variable>"

#. iUNFX
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id2307199\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can combine several graphic objects into a group so that you can use them like a single object."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດຮວມເອົາຫຼາຍວັດຖຸຮູບພາບເຂົ້າເປັນກຸ່ມດຽວ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ພວກມັນເປັນຄືກັບວັດຖຸດຽວ."

#. WFAZD
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id9983825\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can move, transform, resize, distort, or convert all objects in a group together, and you can enter the group any time to change the individual objects."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດຍ້າຍ, ປ່ຽນຮູບຮ່າງ, ປ່ຽນຂະໜາດ, ບິດເບືອນ ຫຼື ແປງທຸກວັດຖຸໃນກຸ່ມໄປພ້ອມກັນໄດ້, ແລະ ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າໄປໃນກຸ່ມໄດ້ທຸກເວລາເພື່ອປ່ຽນແປງແຕ່ລະວັດຖຸ."

#. EeStU
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id5734733\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can change the properties (line size, fill color, and more) of all objects in a group together, and you can enter the group and change the individual objects."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດປ່ຽນຄຸນສົມບັດ (ຂະໜາດເສັ້ນ, ສີພື້ນ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ) ຂອງທຸກວັດຖຸໃນກຸ່ມໄປພ້ອມກັນໄດ້, ແລະ ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າໄປໃນກຸ່ມເພື່ອປ່ຽນແປງແຕ່ລະວັດຖຸໄດ້."

#. sRgyC
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id561540\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Groups can also be nested to form groups within other groups."
msgstr "ກຸ່ມຍັງສາມາດຈັດຊ້ອນກັນເພື່ອສ້າງເປັນກຸ່ມຍ່ອຍຢູ່ພາຍໃນກຸ່ມອື່ນໄດ້."

#. GpBu3
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"hd_id7705618\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To group objects"
msgstr "ວິທີການຈັດກຸ່ມວັດຖຸ"

#. kXEhk
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id607013\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the objects together that you want to group. Hold down Shift while you click the individual objects."
msgstr "ເລືອກບັນດາວັດຖຸທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຈັດກຸ່ມພ້ອມກັນ. ກົດປຸ່ມ Shift ຄ້າງໄວ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ທ່ານຄລິກເລືອກແຕ່ລະວັດຖຸ."

#. uEyzA
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id1399578\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Right-click any of the selected objects to open the context menu. In Calc or Writer, commands are in a submenu <emph>Group</emph>, while in Impress or Draw, they are at the toplevel of the context menu."
msgstr "ຄລິກຂວາໃສ່ວັດຖຸໃດໜຶ່ງທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ເພື່ອເປີດເມນູລັດ. ໃນ Calc ຫຼື Writer, ຄຳສັ່ງຈະຢູ່ໃນເມນູຍ່ອຍ <emph>ກຸ່ມ</emph>, ສ່ວນໃນ Impress ຫຼື Draw, ພວກມັນຈະຢູ່ຊັ້ນເທິງສຸດຂອງເມນູລັດ."

#. 6g7hu
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id598162\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Group</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ກຸ່ມ</emph>."

#. XxjEG
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id6738792\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To select the objects, you can also drag a selection frame around the objects."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເລືອກວັດຖຸ, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດລາກກອບການເລືອກອ້ອມຮອບວັດຖຸເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນໄດ້."

#. NcEXE
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id7309793\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For example, you can group all of the objects in a company logo to move and resize the logo as a single object."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ, ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດກຸ່ມທຸກວັດຖຸໃນໂລໂກ້ບໍລິສັດເພື່ອຍ້າຍ ແລະ ປ່ຽນຂະໜາດໂລໂກ້ເປັນຄືກັບວັດຖຸດຽວ."

#. AZLFx
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id1227759\n"
"help.text"
msgid "After you have grouped objects, selecting any part of the group selects the entire group."
msgstr "ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ທ່ານຈັດກຸ່ມວັດຖຸແລ້ວ, ການເລືອກສ່ວນໃດໜຶ່ງຂອງກຸ່ມຈະເປັນການເລືອກທັງໝົດກຸ່ມ."

#. o8ypz
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"hd_id7424237\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To enter a group"
msgstr "ວິທີເຂົ້າສູ່ກຸ່ມ"

#. eAUtE
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id1388592\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Right-click any object of the group. In Calc or Writer, commands are in a submenu <emph>Group</emph>, while in Impress or Draw, they are at the toplevel of the context menu."
msgstr "ຄລິກຂວາໃສ່ວັດຖຸໃດໜຶ່ງໃນກຸ່ມ. ໃນ Calc ຫຼື Writer, ຄຳສັ່ງຈະຢູ່ໃນເມນູຍ່ອຍ <emph>ກຸ່ມ</emph>, ສ່ວນໃນ Impress ຫຼື Draw, ພວກມັນຈະຢູ່ຊັ້ນເທິງສຸດຂອງເມນູລັດ."

#. WGDzk
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id343943\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Enter Group</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ເຂົ້າສູ່ກຸ່ມ</emph>."

#. PdLkF
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id8726767\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Now you can select and edit a single object in the group."
msgstr "ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂແຕ່ລະວັດຖຸໃນກຸ່ມໄດ້ແລ້ວ."

#. DpDPq
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id691549\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can add or delete objects to and from a group in this mode."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມ ຫຼື ລຶບວັດຖຸເຂົ້າ ແລະ ອອກຈາກກຸ່ມໃນໂໝດນີ້ໄດ້."

#. pbMff
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id9909665\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The objects that are not part of the group are shown with dimmed colors."
msgstr "ວັດຖຸທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ຢູ່ໃນກຸ່ມຈະຖືກສະແດງດ້ວຍສີທີ່ຈາງລົງ."

#. wwojr
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"hd_id9141819\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To exit a group"
msgstr "ວິທີອອກຈາກກຸ່ມ"

#. ytVTd
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id6354869\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Right-click any object of the group. In Calc or Writer, commands are in a submenu <emph>Group</emph>, while in Impress or Draw, they are at the toplevel of the context menu."
msgstr "ຄລິກຂວາໃສ່ວັດຖຸໃດໜຶ່ງໃນກຸ່ມ. ໃນ Calc ຫຼື Writer, ຄຳສັ່ງຈະຢູ່ໃນເມນູຍ່ອຍ <emph>ກຸ່ມ</emph>, ສ່ວນໃນ Impress ຫຼື Draw, ພວກມັນຈະຢູ່ຊັ້ນເທິງສຸດຂອງເມນູລັດ."

#. 8XxJJ
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id2685323\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Exit Group</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ອອກຈາກກຸ່ມ</emph>."

#. nF24F
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id6042664\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To exit a group in Draw or Impress, you can also double-click anywhere outside the group."
msgstr "ເພື່ອອອກຈາກກຸ່ມໃນ Draw ຫຼື Impress, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດດັບເບິ້ນຄລິກໃສ່ບ່ອນໃດກໍໄດ້ທີ່ຢູ່ນອກກຸ່ມ."

#. zGXNe
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"hd_id7889950\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To ungroup a group"
msgstr "ວິທີຍົກເລີກການຈັດກຸ່ມ"

#. sEPrg
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id3236182\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Right-click any object of the group. In Calc or Writer, commands are in a submenu <emph>Group</emph>, while in Impress or Draw, they are at the toplevel of the context menu."
msgstr "ຄລິກຂວາໃສ່ວັດຖຸໃດໜຶ່ງໃນກຸ່ມ. ໃນ Calc ຫຼື Writer, ຄຳສັ່ງຈະຢູ່ໃນເມນູຍ່ອຍ <emph>ກຸ່ມ</emph>, ສ່ວນໃນ Impress ຫຼື Draw, ພວກມັນຈະຢູ່ຊັ້ນເທິງສຸດຂອງເມນູລັດ."

#. GqpZo
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id1251258\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Ungroup</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ຍົກເລີກການຈັດກຸ່ມ</emph>."

#. 4arDu
#: groups.xhp
msgctxt ""
"groups.xhp\n"
"par_id8111819\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Now you can select and edit all objects as individual objects."
msgstr "ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂທຸກວັດຖຸເປັນວັດຖຸແຍກຕ່າງຫາກໄດ້ແລ້ວ."

#. m7yV2
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Editing Hyperlinks"
msgstr "ການແກ້ໄຂການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ"

#. FjGVS
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"bm_id3153910\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>hyperlinks; editing</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>links; editing hyperlinks</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>editing; hyperlinks</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>text attributes; hyperlinks</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>buttons;editing hyperlink buttons</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>URL;changing hyperlink URLs</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ; ການແກ້ໄຂ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ລິ້ງ; ການແກ້ໄຂການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການແກ້ໄຂ; ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຄຸນລັກສະນະຂໍ້ຄວາມ; ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ປຸ່ມ; ການແກ້ໄຂປຸ່ມການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>URL; ການປ່ຽນແປງ URL ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</bookmark_value>"

#. SkQGu
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153910\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"hyperlink_edit\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/hyperlink_edit.xhp\">Editing Hyperlinks</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"hyperlink_edit\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/hyperlink_edit.xhp\">ການແກ້ໄຂການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</link></variable>"

#. FNBDB
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id4124881\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>-click a hyperlink in a Writer document, your web browser opens with the requested web address. If you don't use a mouse, position the cursor inside the hyperlink and open the context menu by Shift+F10, then choose Open Hyperlink."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>-ຄລິກ ໃສ່ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງໃນເອກະສານ Writer, ບຣາວເຊີເວັບຂອງທ່ານຈະເປີດຂຶ້ນພ້ອມກັບທີ່ຢູ່ເວັບທີ່ຕ້ອງການ. ຖ້າທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ໃຊ້ເມົາສ໌, ໃຫ້ວາງເຄີເຊີໄວ້ໃນການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ ແລະ ເປີດເມນູລັດດ້ວຍ Shift+F10, ຈາກນັ້ນເລືອກ ເປີດການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ."

#. 9ugjp
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145071\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Changing the text of a hyperlink"
msgstr "ການປ່ຽນຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ"

#. cyGqJ
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id3166410\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In Writer documents, you can click anywhere into a hyperlink and edit the visible text."
msgstr "ໃນເອກະສານ Writer, ທ່ານສາມາດຄລິກໃສ່ບ່ອນໃດກໍໄດ້ໃນການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນ."

#. 5JDBm
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id2690511\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you leave the hyperlink by positioning the cursor elsewhere, only the visible text changes."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານອອກຈາກການເຊື່ອມໂຍງໂດຍການວາງເຄີເຊີໄວ້ບ່ອນອື່ນ, ຈະມີພຽງແຕ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນເທົ່ານັ້ນທີ່ປ່ຽນແປງ."

#. bU4xF
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id1983092\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you leave the hyperlink by entering a space character directly following the last character, the AutoCorrect - if enabled - will change the target URL to be the same as the visible text."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານອອກຈາກການເຊື່ອມໂຍງໂດຍການປ້ອນຍະວ່າງຖັດຈາກຕົວອັກສອນສຸດທ້າຍໂດຍກົງ, ລະບົບແກ້ໄຂອັດຕະໂນມັດ (ຖ້າເປີດໃຊ້ງານ) ຈະປ່ຽນ URL ປາຍທາງໃຫ້ຄືກັນກັບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນ."

#. kCdeG
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id333262\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In all document types, you can open the Hyperlink dialog to edit a hyperlink. First set the cursor into the hyperlink or directly in front of the hyperlink, then click the Hyperlink icon on the Standard bar."
msgstr "ໃນເອກະສານທຸກປະເພດ, ທ່ານສາມາດເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບການເຊື່ອມໂຍງເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂການເຊື່ອມໂຍງໄດ້. ທຳອິດໃຫ້ວາງເຄີເຊີໄວ້ໃນການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ ຫຼື ທາງໜ້າຂອງການເຊື່ອມໂຍງໂດຍກົງ, ຈາກນັ້ນຄລິກໃສ່ໄອຄອນການເຊື່ອມໂຍງໃນແຖບມາດຕະຖານ."

#. 8pXKy
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"hd_id3158432\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Changing the URL of a hyperlink"
msgstr "ການປ່ຽນ URL ຂອງການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ"

#. GqyXN
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id3150503\n"
"help.text"
msgid "As described above, open <link href=\"text/shared/02/09070000.xhp\">Hyperlink Dialog</link>."
msgstr "ຕາມທີ່ໄດ້ອະທິບາຍໄວ້ຂ້າງເທິງ, ໃຫ້ເປີດ <link href=\"text/shared/02/09070000.xhp\">ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</link>."

#. V89FX
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148686\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Changing the attribute of all hyperlinks"
msgstr "ການປ່ຽນຄຸນລັກສະນະຂອງການເຊື່ອມໂຍງທັງໝົດ"

#. MwCds
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id3148943\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open the Styles window."
msgstr "ເປີດໜ້າຕ່າງລັກສະນະ (Styles)."

#. 2Arq5
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_idN10826\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the Character Styles icon."
msgstr "ຄລິກໃສ່ໄອຄອນລັກສະນະຕົວອັກສອນ (Character Styles)."

#. kdaL4
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_idN1082C\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Right-click the “Internet Link” or “Visited Internet Link” character style, and choose <menuitem>Edit Style</menuitem>."
msgstr "ຄລິກຂວາໃສ່ລັກສະນະຕົວອັກສອນ “Internet Link” ຫຼື “Visited Internet Link”, ແລ້ວເລືອກ <menuitem>ແກ້ໄຂລັກສະນະ</menuitem>."

#. YkLWs
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_idN10834\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the dialog, select the new attributes, and click <emph>OK</emph>."
msgstr "ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ, ເລືອກຄຸນລັກສະນະໃໝ່, ແລ້ວຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>."

#. VZCfb
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147530\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Editing a hyperlink button"
msgstr "ການແກ້ໄຂປຸ່ມການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ"

#. rCCJN
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id901565307899796\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Hyperlink buttons must be edited in Form design mode."
msgstr "ປຸ່ມການເຊື່ອມໂຍງຈະຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການແກ້ໄຂໃນໂໝດການອອກແບບຟອມ."

#. ZiK7F
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id641565307910254\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select menu <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"WRITER\"><menuitem>Form - Design mode</menuitem> or choose </caseinline></switchinline> <menuitem>View - Toolbars</menuitem> and enable the Form Controls toolbar, click on the Design Mode icon and click on the button. The button handles shows."
msgstr "ເລືອກເມນູ <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"WRITER\"><menuitem>ຟອມ - ໂໝດການອອກແບບ</menuitem> ຫຼື ເລືອກ </caseinline></switchinline> <menuitem>ມຸມມອງ - ແຖບເຄື່ອງມື</menuitem> ແລະ ເປີດໃຊ້ງານແຖບເຄື່ອງມືການຄວບຄຸມຟອມ, ຄລິກໃສ່ໄອຄອນໂໝດການອອກແບບ ແລະ ຄລິກໃສ່ປຸ່ມ. ປຸ່ມຈັດການຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນ."

#. xTmQW
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id961565308003935\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open context menu and select <menuitem>Control Properties</menuitem>."
msgstr "ເປີດເມນູລັດ ແລະ ເລືອກ <menuitem>ຄຸນສົມບັດການຄວບຄຸມ</menuitem>."

#. hToHs
#: hyperlink_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id811565308009651\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Edit the property in the control dialog box."
msgstr "ແກ້ໄຂຄຸນສົມບັດໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບການຄວບຄຸມ."

#. GjZJA
#: hyperlink_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_insert.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Inserting Hyperlinks"
msgstr "ການແຊກການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ"

#. ydY5T
#: hyperlink_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_insert.xhp\n"
"bm_id3150789\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>hyperlinks; inserting</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>links; inserting</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>inserting; hyperlinks</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ; ການແຊກ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ລິ້ງ; ການແຊກ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການແຊກ; ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</bookmark_value>"

#. mb3NF
#: hyperlink_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_insert.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150789\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"hyperlink_insert\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/hyperlink_insert.xhp\">Inserting Hyperlinks</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"hyperlink_insert\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/hyperlink_insert.xhp\">ການແຊກການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</link></variable>"

#. y4YkT
#: hyperlink_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_insert.xhp\n"
"par_id3149095\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can insert hyperlinks in two ways: as text or as a button. In both cases, the visible text can be different from the URL."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດແຊກການເຊື່ອມໂຍງໄດ້ສອງວິທີ: ເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ເປັນປຸ່ມ. ໃນທັງສອງກໍລະນີ, ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນສາມາດແຕກຕ່າງຈາກ URL ໄດ້."

#. hQf7h
#: hyperlink_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_insert.xhp\n"
"par_id3149811\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Place the text cursor in the document at the point where you want to insert the hyperlink or select the text that you want to put the hyperlink on. Select <emph>Hyperlink</emph> command from the <emph>Insert</emph> menu. Alternatively click on the <image id=\"img_id3149763\" src=\"cmd/sc_hyperlinkdialog.png\" width=\"0.222inch\" height=\"0.222inch\"><alt id=\"alt_id3149763\">Icon</alt></image> Hyperlink icon on the <emph>Standard</emph> toolbar. The <link href=\"text/shared/02/09070000.xhp\">Hyperlink dialog</link> appears."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນເອກະສານບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແຊກການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ ຫຼື ເລືອກຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃສ່ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ. ເລືອກຄຳສັ່ງ <emph>ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</emph> ຈາກເມນູ <emph>ແຊກ</emph>. ຫຼື ຄລິກໃສ່ໄອຄອນ <image id=\"img_id3149763\" src=\"cmd/sc_hyperlinkdialog.png\" width=\"0.222inch\" height=\"0.222inch\"><alt id=\"alt_id3149763\">ໄອຄອນ</alt></image> ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ ໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມື <emph>ມາດຕະຖານ</emph>. <link href=\"text/shared/02/09070000.xhp\">ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</link> ຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນ."

#. E8dZA
#: hyperlink_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_insert.xhp\n"
"par_id3154685\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To jump to a specific line in a text document, first enter a bookmark at that position (<emph>Insert - Bookmark</emph>)."
msgstr "ເພື່ອໂດດໄປຫາແຖວສະເພາະໃນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ທຳອິດໃຫ້ປ້ອນບຸກມາກ (bookmark) ຢູ່ຕຳແໜ່ງນັ້ນ (<emph>ແຊກ - ບຸກມາກ</emph>)."

#. dUFRE
#: hyperlink_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_insert.xhp\n"
"par_idN1076D\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To jump to a cell in a spreadsheet, first enter a name for the cell (<emph>Sheet - Named Ranges and Expressions - Define</emph>)."
msgstr "ເພື່ອໂດດໄປຫາເຊວໃນສະເປຣດຊີດ, ທຳອິດໃຫ້ປ້ອນຊື່ສຳລັບເຊວນັ້ນ (<emph>ຊີດ - ກຳນົດຊ່ວງ ແລະ ສົມຜົນ - ກຳນົດ</emph>)."

#. k9rm5
#: hyperlink_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_insert.xhp\n"
"par_id3152887\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Hyperlinks can also be inserted by drag-and-drop from the Navigator. Hyperlinks can refer to references, headings, graphics, tables, objects, directories or bookmarks."
msgstr "ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງຍັງສາມາດແຊກໄດ້ໂດຍການລາກ ແລະ ວາງຈາກຕົວນຳທາງ (Navigator). ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງສາມາດອ້າງອີງເຖິງການອ້າງອີງ, ຫົວຂໍ້, ຮູບພາບ, ຕາຕະລາງ, ວັດຖຸ, ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີ ຫຼື ບຸກມາກ."

#. bbdmu
#: hyperlink_insert.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_insert.xhp\n"
"par_id3146975\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you wish to insert in a text a hyperlink that refers to Table 1, drag the entry Table 1 from the Navigator and drop it in the text. To do this, the <emph>Insert as Hyperlink</emph> drag mode must be selected in the Navigator."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການແຊກການເຊື່ອມໂຍງໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ອ້າງອີງເຖິງ ຕາຕະລາງ 1, ໃຫ້ລາກລາຍການ ຕາຕະລາງ 1 ຈາກຕົວນຳທາງແລ້ວວາງລົງໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ເພື່ອເຮັດສິ່ງນີ້, ຈະຕ້ອງເລືອກໂໝດການລາກ <emph>ແຊກເປັນການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</emph> ໃນຕົວນຳທາງ."

#. ZkEzB
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Relative and Absolute Links"
msgstr "ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງແບບສຳພັດ ແລະ ແບບສຳບູນ"

#. SFHrE
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"bm_id3147399\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>absolute hyperlinks</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>relative hyperlinks</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>hyperlinks; relative and absolute</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>hyperlinks, see also links</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງແບບສຳບູນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງແບບສຳພັດ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ; ແບບສຳພັດ ແລະ ແບບສຳບູນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ, ເບິ່ງ ລິ້ງ ນຳ</bookmark_value>"

#. tL4Wk
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147399\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"hyperlink_rel_abs\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\">Relative and Absolute Links</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"hyperlink_rel_abs\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\">ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງແບບສຳພັດ ແລະ ແບບສຳບູນ</link></variable>"

#. GYPtz
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"par_id3153345\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you include hyperlinks, two factors must be taken into account: whether they are set as relative or absolute on saving, and whether or not the file is present."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານຮວມເອົາການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ, ຕ້ອງຄຳນຶງເຖິງສອງປັດໄຈ: ພວກມັນຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນແບບສຳພັດ ຫຼື ແບບສຳບູນໃນຕອນບັນທຶກ, ແລະ ໄຟລ໌ນັ້ນມີຢູ່ແທ້ຫຼືບໍ່."

#. BUhmk
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"par_id3147008\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</caseinline><defaultinline>Tools - Options</defaultinline></switchinline> - <link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010200.xhp\"><emph>Load/Save - General</emph></link> and specify in the <emph>Save URLs relative to</emph> field if $[officename] creates <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000005.xhp#saving\">relative or absolute hyperlinks</link>. Relative linking is only possible when the document you are working on and the link destination are on the same drive."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">%PRODUCTNAME - ຄ່າກຳນົດ</caseinline><defaultinline>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</defaultinline></switchinline> - <link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010200.xhp\"><emph>ໂຫຼດ/ບັນທຶກ - ທົ່ວໄປ</emph></link> ແລະ ລະບຸໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ບັນທຶກ URL ສຳພັດກັບ</emph> ວ່າ $[officename] ຈະສ້າງ <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000005.xhp#saving\">ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງແບບສຳພັດ ຫຼື ແບບສຳບູນ</link>. ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງແບບສຳພັດຈະເຮັດໄດ້ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອເອກະສານທີ່ທ່ານກຳລັງເຮັດວຽກຢູ່ ແລະ ປາຍທາງຂອງລິ້ງຢູ່ໃນໄດຣຟ໌ດຽວກັນ."

#. Ue6zh
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"par_id3145382\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You should create the same directory structure on your hard disk as that which exists in the web space hosted by your Internet provider. Call the root directory for the homepage on your hard disk \"homepage\", for example. The start file is then \"index.html\", the full path being \"C:\\homepage\\index.html\" (assuming Windows operating system). The URL on your Internet provider's server might then be as follows: \"http://www.myprovider.com/mypage/index.html\". With relative addressing, you indicate the link relative to the location of the output document. For example, if you placed all the graphics for your homepage in a subfolder called \"C:\\homepage\\images\", you would need to give the following path to access the graphic \"picture.gif\": \"images\\picture.gif\". This is the relative path, starting from the location of the file \"index.html\". On the provider's server, you would place the picture in the folder \"mypage/images\". When you transfer the document \"index.html\" to the provider's server through the <emph>File - Save As</emph> dialog, and if you have marked the option <emph>Copy local images to Internet</emph> under <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - Load/Save - HTML Compatibility</emph>, $[officename] will automatically copy the graphic to the correct directory on the server."
msgstr "ທ່ານຄວນສ້າງໂຄງສ້າງໄດເຣັກທໍຣີໃນຮາດດິດຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ຄືກັບທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນພື້ນທີ່ເວັບຂອງຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການອິນເຕີເນັດຂອງທ່ານ. ຕົວຢ່າງ, ຕັ້ງຊື່ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີຮາກສຳລັບໂຮມເພຈໃນຮາດດິດຂອງທ່ານວ່າ \"homepage\". ໄຟລ໌ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຈະເປັນ \"index.html\", ເສັ້ນທາງເຕັມແມ່ນ \"C:\\homepage\\index.html\" (ສຳລັບລະບົບປະຕິບັດການ Windows). URL ໃນເຊີເວີຂອງຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການອິນເຕີເນັດອາດຈະເປັນ: \"http://www.myprovider.com/mypage/index.html\". ດ້ວຍການກຳນົດທີ່ຢູ່ແບບສຳພັດ, ທ່ານລະບຸລິ້ງໃຫ້ສຳພັດກັບຕຳແໜ່ງຂອງເອກະສານຜົນລິດ. ຕົວຢ່າງ, ຖ້າທ່ານວາງຮູບພາບທັງໝົດສຳລັບໂຮມເພຈຂອງທ່ານໄວ້ໃນໂຟນເດີຍ່ອຍຊື່ \"C:\\homepage\\images\", ທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງໃຫ້ເສັ້ນທາງດັ່ງນີ້ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງຮູບພາບ \"picture.gif\": \"images\\picture.gif\". ນີ້ຄືເສັ້ນທາງແບບສຳພັດ, ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຈາກຕຳແໜ່ງຂອງໄຟລ໌ \"index.html\". ໃນເຊີເວີຂອງຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການ, ທ່ານຈະວາງຮູບພາບໄວ້ໃນໂຟນເດີ \"mypage/images\". ເມື່ອທ່ານສົ່ງເອກະສານ \"index.html\" ໄປຍັງເຊີເວີຂອງຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການຜ່ານກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ບັນທຶກເປັນ</emph>, ແລະ ຖ້າທ່ານໄດ້ໝາຍເອົາຕົວເລືອກ <emph>ຄັດລອກຮູບພາບທ້ອງຖິ່ນໄປຍັງອິນເຕີເນັດ</emph> ພາຍໃຕ້ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ຄ່າກຳນົດ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - ໂຫຼດ/ບັນທຶກ - ຄວາມເຂົ້າກັນໄດ້ກັບ HTML</emph>, $[officename] ຈະຄັດລອກຮູບພາບໄປຍັງໄດເຣັກທໍຣີທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງໃນເຊີເວີໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. bDwjd
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"par_id3159158\n"
"help.text"
msgid "An absolute path such as \"C:\\homepage\\graphics\\picture.gif\" would no longer function on the provider server. Neither a server nor the computer of a reader needs to have a C hard drive: operating systems such as Unix or macOS do not recognize drive letters, and even if the folder homepage\\graphics existed, your picture would not be available. It is better to use relative addressing for file links."
msgstr "ເສັ້ນທາງແບບສຳບູນເຊັ່ນ \"C:\\homepage\\graphics\\picture.gif\" ຈະບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ໃນເຊີເວີຂອງຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການ. ທັງເຊີເວີ ແລະ ຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງຜູ້ອ່ານບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີໄດຣຟ໌ C: ລະບົບປະຕິບັດການເຊັ່ນ Unix ຫຼື macOS ບໍ່ຮູ້ຈັກຕົວອັກສອນໄດຣຟ໌, ແລະ ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າມີໂຟນເດີ homepage\\graphics ຢູ່, ຮູບພາບຂອງທ່ານກໍຈະບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້. ສະນັ້ນ ມັນຈະດີກວ່າຖ້າໃຊ້ການກຳນົດທີ່ຢູ່ແບບສຳພັດສຳລັບລິ້ງໄຟລ໌."

#. 3Rjas
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"par_id3154046\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A link to a web page, for example, \"www.example.com\" or \"www.myprovider.com/mypage/index.html\" is an absolute link."
msgstr "ລິ້ງໄປຫາເວັບເພຈ, ຕົວຢ່າງ: \"www.example.com\" ຫຼື \"www.myprovider.com/mypage/index.html\" ແມ່ນລິ້ງແບບສຳບູນ."

#. bTRZi
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"par_id3155450\n"
"help.text"
msgid "$[officename] also reacts differently, depending on whether the file referred to in the link exists, and where it is located. $[officename] checks every new link and sets a target and protocol automatically. The result can be seen in the generated HTML code after saving the source document."
msgstr "$[officename] ຍັງມີການຕອບສະໜອງທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ, ຂຶ້ນຢູ່ກັບວ່າໄຟລ໌ທີ່ອ້າງອີງໃນລິ້ງນັ້ນມີຢູ່ແທ້ບໍ່ ແລະ ມັນຕັ້ງຢູ່ໃສ. $[officename] ຈະກວດສອບທຸກໆລິ້ງໃໝ່ ແລະ ຕັ້ງຄ່າປາຍທາງ ແລະ ໂປຣໂຕຄໍໃຫ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ຜົນລິດສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ໃນລະຫັດ HTML ທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນຫຼັງຈາກບັນທຶກເອກະສານຕົ້ນສະບັບ."

#. E4iaR
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"par_id3145317\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following rules apply: A relative reference (\"graphic/picture.gif\") is only possible when both files exist on the same drive. If the files are on different drives in your local file system, the absolute reference follows the \"file:\" protocol (\"file:///data1/xyz/picture.gif\"). If the files are on different servers or if the target of the link is not available, the absolute reference uses the \"http:\" protocol (\"http://data2/abc/picture.gif\")."
msgstr "ມີກົດເກນດັ່ງນີ້: ການອ້າງອີງແບບສຳພັດ (\"graphic/picture.gif\") ຈະເຮັດໄດ້ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອທັງສອງໄຟລ໌ຢູ່ໃນໄດຣຟ໌ດຽວກັນ. ຖ້າໄຟລ໌ຢູ່ໃນໄດຣຟ໌ທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນໃນລະບົບໄຟລ໌ທ້ອງຖິ່ນຂອງທ່ານ, ການອ້າງອີງແບບສຳບູນຈະໃຊ້ໂປຣໂຕຄໍ \"file:\" (\"file:///data1/xyz/picture.gif\"). ຖ້າໄຟລ໌ຢູ່ໃນເຊີເວີທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ ຫຼື ຖ້າປາຍທາງຂອງລິ້ງບໍ່ພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານ, ການອ້າງອີງແບບສຳບູນຈະໃຊ້ໂປຣໂຕຄໍ \"http:\" (\"http://data2/abc/picture.gif\")."

#. qB8Yx
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"par_id3153541\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Be sure to organize all files for your homepage on the same drive as the start file of the homepage. In this way, $[officename] can set the protocol and target so that the reference on the server is always correct."
msgstr "ກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າໄດ້ຈັດລະບຽບໄຟລ໌ທັງໝົດສຳລັບໂຮມເພຈຂອງທ່ານໄວ້ໃນໄດຣຟ໌ດຽວກັນກັບໄຟລ໌ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງໂຮມເພຈ. ດ້ວຍວິທີນີ້, $[officename] ຈະສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າໂປຣໂຕຄໍ ແລະ ປາຍທາງ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ການອ້າງອີງໃນເຊີເວີຖືກຕ້ອງສະເໝີ."

#. 4E2tA
#: hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlink_rel_abs.xhp\n"
"par_id3153897\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you rest your mouse on a hyperlink, a help tip displays the absolute reference, since $[officename] uses absolute path names internally. The complete path and address can only be seen when you view the result of the HTML export, by loading the HTML file as \"Text\" or opening it with a text editor."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານວາງເມົາສ໌ໄວ້ເທິງການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ, ຄຳແນະນຳຈະສະແດງການອ້າງອີງແບບສຳບູນ, ເນື່ອງຈາກ $[officename] ໃຊ້ຊື່ເສັ້ນທາງແບບສຳບູນພາຍໃນລະບົບ. ເສັ້ນທາງ ແລະ ທີ່ຢູ່ທີ່ສົມບູນຈະສາມາດເຫັນໄດ້ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອທ່ານເບິ່ງຜົນຂອງການສົ່ງອອກ HTML, ໂດຍການໂຫຼດໄຟລ໌ HTML ເປັນ \"ຂໍ້ຄວາມ\" ຫຼື ເປີດມັນດ້ວຍຕົວແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#. qxJsq
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Adding Clickable Hotspots to Images"
msgstr "ການເພີ່ມຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງທີ່ຄລິກໄດ້ໃຫ້ກັບຮູບພາບ"

#. B6fGi
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"bm_id3150502\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>ImageMap; editor</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>editors; ImageMap editor</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>images; ImageMap</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>pictures; ImageMap</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>hotspots;adding to images</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>URL;in pictures</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ (ImageMap); ຕົວແກ້ໄຂ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຕົວແກ້ໄຂ; ຕົວແກ້ໄຂແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຮູບພາບ; ແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຮູບພາບ; ແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງ; ການເພີ່ມໃສ່ຮູບພາບ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>URL; ໃນຮູບພາບ</bookmark_value>"

#. 2hvMi
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN10631\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"imagemap\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/imagemap.xhp\">Adding Clickable Hotspots to Images</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"imagemap\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/imagemap.xhp\">ການເພີ່ມຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງທີ່ຄລິກໄດ້ໃຫ້ກັບຮູບພາບ</link></variable>"

#. ACvQ6
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN1064F\n"
"help.text"
msgid "An ImageMap allows you to attach URLs to specific areas, called hotspots, on a picture in your document. An image map is a group of one or more hotspots."
msgstr "ແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ (ImageMap) ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດແນບ URL ໃສ່ພື້ນທີ່ສະເພາະ, ທີ່ເອີ້ນວ່າ ຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງ (hotspots), ໃນຮູບພາບໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ. ແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບແມ່ນກຸ່ມຂອງຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງໜຶ່ງ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍຈຸດ."

#. bFeED
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN1066C\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can draw three types of hotspots: rectangles, ellipses, and polygons. When you click a hotspot, the URL is opened in the browser window or frame that you specify. You can also specify the text that appears when your mouse rests on the hotspot."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດແຕ້ມຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງໄດ້ສາມປະເພດ: ຮູບສີ່ແຈສາກ, ຮູບວົງມົນ/ວົງຮີ, ແລະ ຮູບຫຼາຍແຈ. ເມື່ອທ່ານຄລິກໃສ່ຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງ, URL ຈະຖືກເປີດໃນໜ້າຕ່າງບຣາວເຊີ ຫຼື ເຟຣມທີ່ທ່ານລະບຸ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດລະບຸຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນເມື່ອທ່ານວາງເມົາສ໌ໄວ້ເທິງຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງນັ້ນ."

#. Cb6FC
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN10677\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To add a clickable hotspot to an image"
msgstr "ວິທີການເພີ່ມຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງທີ່ຄລິກໄດ້ໃຫ້ກັບຮູບພາບ"

#. YvCKg
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN1067E\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Position the cursor where you want the ImageMap in your document."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີໃນບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ມີແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ."

#. AuLFm
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN10682\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Insert - Image</emph>, select and insert a bitmap image."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ແຊກ - ຮູບພາບ</emph>, ເລືອກ ແລະ ແຊກຮູບພາບແບບບິດແມບ."

#. jGSkL
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN1068A\n"
"help.text"
msgid "With the image selected, choose <menuitem>Tools - ImageMap</menuitem> to open the <link href=\"text/shared/01/02220000.xhp\">ImageMap Editor</link>, which displays the selected image and contains the hotspot editing tools."
msgstr "ໃນຂະນະທີ່ເລືອກຮູບພາບຢູ່, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <menuitem>ເຄື່ອງມື - ແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ</menuitem> ເພື່ອເປີດ <link href=\"text/shared/01/02220000.xhp\">ຕົວແກ້ໄຂແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ</link>, ເຊິ່ງຈະສະແດງຮູບພາບທີ່ເລືອກ ແລະ ມີເຄື່ອງມືແກ້ໄຂຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງ."

#. Es34e
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN106A0\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the icons in the ImageMap Editor to draw a hotspot shape, for example a rectangle, over the image at the background."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ໄອຄອນໃນຕົວແກ້ໄຂແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບເພື່ອແຕ້ມຮູບຮ່າງຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງ, ຕົວຢ່າງເຊັ່ນ ຮູບສີ່ແຈສາກ, ທັບລົງເທິງຮູບພາບພື້ນຫຼັງ."

#. EBGj6
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN106A3\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can see an extended help text on the functions of each icon when you enable Extended Help in <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME - General</emph>."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເບິ່ງຂໍ້ຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບການເຮັດວຽກຂອງແຕ່ລະໄອຄອນໄດ້ ເມື່ອທ່ານເປີດໃຊ້ງານ ການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອເພີ່ມເຕີມ ໃນ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ຄ່າກຳນົດ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME - ທົ່ວໄປ</emph>."

#. R2YVB
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN106AB\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the \"Address\" URL that will be shown in a Web browser when the user clicks the hotspot."
msgstr "ປ້ອນ URL \"ທີ່ຢູ່\" ທີ່ຈະຖືກສະແດງໃນເວັບບຣາວເຊີເມື່ອຜູ້ໃຊ້ຄລິກໃສ່ຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງ."

#. Dgf3X
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN106AF\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Optionally, enter the \"Text\" that will be shown as a tip when the user points the mouse to the hotspot."
msgstr "ທາງເລືອກອື່ນ, ທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນ \"ຂໍ້ຄວາມ\" ທີ່ຈະສະແດງເປັນຄຳແນະນຳເມື່ອຜູ້ໃຊ້ວາງເມົາສ໌ໄວ້ທີ່ຈຸດເຊື່ອມໂຍງ."

#. j8WAr
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN106B3\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the Apply button to apply your changes, and close the ImageMap Editor."
msgstr "ຄລິກປຸ່ມ ນຳໃຊ້ ເພື່ອນຳໃຊ້ການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງທ່ານ, ແລະ ປິດຕົວແກ້ໄຂແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ."

#. 7kkzm
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN106B7\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Save the document in the %PRODUCTNAME or HTML format."
msgstr "ບັນທຶກເອກະສານໃນຮູບແບບ %PRODUCTNAME ຫຼື HTML."

#. eSegh
#: imagemap.xhp
msgctxt ""
"imagemap.xhp\n"
"par_idN106BA\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You may save the ImageMap as a file and upload that file to a Web server, for example."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ, ທ່ານອາດຈະບັນທຶກແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບເປັນໄຟລ໌ ແລະ ອັບໂຫຼດໄຟລ໌ນັ້ນໄປຍັງເວັບເຊີເວີ."

#. LkKHd
#: import_ms.xhp
msgctxt ""
"import_ms.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opening documents saved in other formats"
msgstr "ການເປີດເອກະສານທີ່ບັນທຶກໃນຮູບແບບອື່ນ"

#. Yq2q3
#: import_ms.xhp
msgctxt ""
"import_ms.xhp\n"
"bm_id3153988\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>Microsoft Office;opening Microsoft documents</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>documents; importing</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>importing; documents in other formats</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>opening; documents from other formats</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>loading; documents from other formats</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>converting;Microsoft documents</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>saving; default file formats</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>defaults;document formats in file dialogs</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>file formats; saving always in other formats</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>Microsoft Office; as default file format</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>files;importing</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>XML converters</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>converters; XML</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>Document Converter Wizard</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>wizards; document converter</bookmark_value> <bookmark_value>converters; document converter</bookmark_value>         <bookmark_value>files, see also documents</bookmark_value>"
