#. QFdQX
#: integratinguno.xhp
msgctxt ""
"integratinguno.xhp\n"
"par_id3147571\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Programmers can write and integrate their own UNO (Universal Network Objects) components to $[officename]. Those new components can be added to the $[officename] menus and toolbars; we call them \"Add-Ons\"."
msgstr "ນັກຂຽນໂປຣແກຣມສາມາດຂຽນ ແລະ ເຊື່ອມໂຍງສ່ວນປະກອບ UNO (Universal Network Objects) ຂອງຕົນເອງເຂົ້າໃນ $[officename]. ສ່ວນປະກອບໃໝ່ເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນສາມາດເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນເມນູ ແລະ ແຖບເຄື່ອງມືຂອງ $[officename] ໄດ້; ພວກເຮົາເອີ້ນພວກມັນວ່າ \"ສ່ວນເສີມ (Add-Ons)\"."

#. QMrQN
#: integratinguno.xhp
msgctxt ""
"integratinguno.xhp\n"
"par_id3154751\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The integration of new components is supported by some tools and services. Details can be found in the $[officename] Developer's Guide. The three main steps are as follows:"
msgstr "ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງສ່ວນປະກອບໃໝ່ໄດ້ຮັບການສະໜັບສະໜູນໂດຍບາງເຄື່ອງມື ແລະ ບໍລິການ. ລາຍລະອຽດສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ໃນ ຄູ່ມືນັກພັດທະນາ $[officename]. ສາມຂັ້ນຕອນຫຼັກມີດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. xXCX9
#: integratinguno.xhp
msgctxt ""
"integratinguno.xhp\n"
"par_id3153748\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Register the new components within $[officename]. This can be accomplished using the tool <item type=\"literal\">unopkg</item>, which can be found in {installpath}<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"UNIX\">/ </caseinline><defaultinline>\\</defaultinline></switchinline>program."
msgstr "ລົງທະບຽນສ່ວນປະກອບໃໝ່ພາຍໃນ $[officename]. ສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງມື <item type=\"literal\">unopkg</item>, ເຊິ່ງຕັ້ງຢູ່ໃນ {installpath}<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"UNIX\">/ </caseinline><defaultinline>\\</defaultinline></switchinline>program."

#. KcTA5
#: integratinguno.xhp
msgctxt ""
"integratinguno.xhp\n"
"par_id3153345\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Integrate the new components as services. The ProtocolHandler and JobDispatch services assist you; more information can be found in the $[officename] Developer's Guide."
msgstr "ເຊື່ອມໂຍງສ່ວນປະກອບໃໝ່ໃຫ້ເປັນບໍລິການ. ບໍລິການ ProtocolHandler ແລະ JobDispatch ຈະຊ່ວຍທ່ານ; ຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ໃນ ຄູ່ມືນັກພັດທະນາ $[officename]."

#. WMmTx
#: integratinguno.xhp
msgctxt ""
"integratinguno.xhp\n"
"par_id3166460\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Change the user interface (menus or toolbars). This can be done almost automatically by writing an XML text file that describes the changes. More information can be found in the $[officename] Developer's Guide."
msgstr "ປ່ຽນແປງສ່ວນຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ (ເມນູ ຫຼື ແຖບເຄື່ອງມື). ສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ເກືອບອັດຕະໂນມັດໂດຍການຂຽນໄຟລ໌ຂໍ້ຄວາມ XML ທີ່ອະທິບາຍເຖິງການປ່ຽນແປງ. ຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ໃນ ຄູ່ມືນັກພັດທະນາ $[officename]."

#. TPxRB
#: integratinguno.xhp
msgctxt ""
"integratinguno.xhp\n"
"par_id3151110\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The Add-Ons can extend the functionality of $[officename]. They are not related to the <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"CALC\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060112.xhp\">Add-Ins</link></caseinline><defaultinline>Add-Ins</defaultinline></switchinline> that provide new functions for $[officename] Calc."
msgstr "Add-Ons ສາມາດຂະຫຍາຍຄວາມສາມາດຂອງ $[officename] ໄດ້. ພວກມັນບໍ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບ <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"CALC\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060112.xhp\">Add-Ins</link></caseinline><defaultinline>Add-Ins</defaultinline></switchinline> ທີ່ໃຫ້ຟັງຊັນໃໝ່ສຳລັບ $[officename] Calc."

#. CAFw3
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Shortcuts (%PRODUCTNAME Accessibility)"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມລັດ (ການເຂົ້າເຖິງ %PRODUCTNAME)"

#. DCFvC
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"bm_id3158421\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>accessibility;general shortcuts</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>shortcut keys; %PRODUCTNAME accessibility</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການເຂົ້າເຖິງ; ປຸ່ມລັດທົ່ວໄປ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ປຸ່ມລັດ; ການເຂົ້າເຖິງ %PRODUCTNAME</bookmark_value>"

#. c2Cjk
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3158421\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"keyboard\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/keyboard.xhp\">Shortcuts (<item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Accessibility)</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"keyboard\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/keyboard.xhp\">ປຸ່ມລັດ (ການເຂົ້າເຖິງ <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item>)</link></variable>"

#. 2drEq
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3159201\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can control <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> without using a mouse device, using only the keyboard."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດຄວບຄຸມ <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> ໄດ້ໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ເມົາສ໌, ໂດຍໃຊ້ພຽງແຕ່ຄີບອດເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. 3CkxR
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3149177\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On each module's main help page (for example, the <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Writer or <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Calc main help page) there is a link to access the keyboard shortcuts' help for that module."
msgstr "ໃນໜ້າຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຫຼັກຂອງແຕ່ລະໂມດູນ (ຕົວຢ່າງ: ໜ້າຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຫຼັກຂອງ <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Writer ຫຼື <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Calc) ຈະມີລິ້ງເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອກ່ຽວກັບປຸ່ມລັດຄີບອດສຳລັບໂມດູນນັ້ນ."

#. CEGCd
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145382\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In addition, under the keyword \"Accessibility\" you find step-by-step instructions about how to control the selected module without a mouse device."
msgstr "ນອກຈາກນີ້, ພາຍໃຕ້ຄຳສຳຄັນ \"ການເຂົ້າເຖິງ (Accessibility)\" ທ່ານຈະພົບຄຳແນະນຳເທື່ອລະຂັ້ນຕອນກ່ຽວກັບວິທີການຄວບຄຸມໂມດູນທີ່ເລືອກໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ເມົາສ໌."

#. jmhLi
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3166460\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Working with the <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> user interface without mouse"
msgstr "ການເຮັດວຽກກັບສ່ວນຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຂອງ <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> ໂດຍບໍ່ໃຊ້ເມົາສ໌"

#. csMc5
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154749\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Activating menu bar, toolbars, windows, and document"
msgstr "ການເປີດໃຊ້ງານແຖບເມນູ, ແຖບເຄື່ອງມື, ໜ້າຕ່າງ, ແລະ ເອກະສານ"

#. Rdd2d
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3156329\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Repeatedly pressing F6 switches the focus and circles through the following objects:"
msgstr "ການກົດປຸ່ມ F6 ຫຼາຍໆຄັ້ງຈະເປັນການສະຫຼັບຈຸດສຸມ (focus) ວົນໄປຕາມວັດຖຸດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. jkqTB
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3150669\n"
"help.text"
msgid "menu bar,"
msgstr "ແຖບເມນູ,"

#. ghGQY
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3149234\n"
"help.text"
msgid "every toolbar from top to bottom and from left to right,"
msgstr "ແຕ່ລະແຖບເຄື່ອງມື ຈາກເທິງລົງລຸ່ມ ແລະ ຈາກຊ້າຍຫາຂວາ,"

#. 5ECrD
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3147618\n"
"help.text"
msgid "every free window from left to right,"
msgstr "ແຕ່ລະໜ້າຕ່າງອິດສະຫຼະ ຈາກຊ້າຍຫາຂວາ,"

#. BkrzX
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154514\n"
"help.text"
msgid "document"
msgstr "ເອກະສານ"

#. F2PEi
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153252\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press Shift+F6 to switch through objects in the opposite direction."
msgstr "ກົດ Shift+F6 ເພື່ອສະຫຼັບຜ່ານວັດຖຸໃນທິດທາງກົງກັນຂ້າມ."

#. 2gobT
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3152473\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+F6 to switch to the document."
msgstr "ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+F6 ເພື່ອສະຫຼັບໄປຫາເອກະສານ."

#. RGGHU
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3152360\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press F10 to switch to the menu bar and back."
msgstr "ກົດ F10 ເພື່ອສະຫຼັບໄປຫາແຖບເມນູ ແລະ ກັບຄືນ."

#. 9tkak
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153896\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Escape closes an open submenu, a toolbar, or the current free window."
msgstr "ປຸ່ມ Escape ໃຊ້ເພື່ອປິດເມນູຍ່ອຍທີ່ເປີດຢູ່, ແຖບເຄື່ອງມື, ຫຼື ໜ້າຕ່າງອິດສະຫຼະປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. FCgDe
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3161656\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Calling a menu command"
msgstr "ການເອີ້ນໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງເມນູ"

#. YYSxF
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3151056\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> or F6 or F10 to select the first menu (the <emph>File</emph> menu). With right arrow, the next menu to the right is selected; with left arrow, the previous menu."
msgstr "ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> ຫຼື F6 ຫຼື F10 ເພື່ອເລືອກເມນູທຳອິດ (ເມນູ <emph>ໄຟລ໌</emph>). ໃຊ້ລູກສອນຂວາເພື່ອເລືອກເມນູຖັດໄປທາງຂວາ; ໃຊ້ລູກສອນຊ້າຍເພື່ອເລືອກເມນູກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້."

#. GS4EY
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153381\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Arrow down opens a selected menu. Any additional arrow down and up arrow move the selection through the menu commands. With right arrow you open any existing submenus."
msgstr "ລູກສອນລົງໃຊ້ເພື່ອເປີດເມນູທີ່ເລືອກ. ການກົດລູກສອນລົງ ແລະ ລູກສອນຂຶ້ນຕື່ມອີກຈະເປັນການເຄື່ອນຍ້າຍການເລືອກຜ່ານຄຳສັ່ງເມນູຕ່າງໆ. ໃຊ້ລູກສອນຂວາເພື່ອເປີດເມນູຍ່ອຍທີ່ມີຢູ່."

#. S43Fv
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3148798\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press Enter to execute the selected menu command."
msgstr "ກົດ Enter ເພື່ອປະຕິບັດຕາມຄຳສັ່ງເມນູທີ່ເລືອກ."

#. kqXuG
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147086\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Executing an icon command"
msgstr "ການປະຕິບັດຄຳສັ່ງໄອຄອນ"

#. xSbDy
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3148922\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press F6 repeatedly until the first icon on the toolbar is selected. Use the right and left arrows to select an icon on a horizontal toolbar. Similarly, use the up and down arrows to select an icon on a vertical toolbar. The Home key selects the first icon on a toolbar and the End key, the last."
msgstr "ກົດ F6 ຫຼາຍໆຄັ້ງຈົນກ່ວາໄອຄອນທຳອິດໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມືຈະຖືກເລືອກ. ໃຊ້ລູກສອນຂວາ ແລະ ຊ້າຍເພື່ອເລືອກໄອຄອນໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມືລວງນອນ. ໃນທຳນອງດຽວກັນ, ໃຊ້ລູກສອນຂຶ້ນ ແລະ ລົງເພື່ອເລືອກໄອຄອນໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມືລວງຕັ້ງ. ປຸ່ມ Home ໃຊ້ເລືອກໄອຄອນທຳອິດໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມື ແລະ ປຸ່ມ End ໃຊ້ເລືອກໄອຄອນສຸດທ້າຍ."

#. 7nP2Z
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3144433\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press Enter to execute the selected icon. If the selected icon normally demands a consecutive mouse action, such as inserting a rectangle, then pressing the Enter key is not sufficient: in these cases press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Enter."
msgstr "ກົດ Enter ເພື່ອປະຕິບັດງານໄອຄອນທີ່ເລືອກ. ຖ້າໄອຄອນທີ່ເລືອກນັ້ນປົກກະຕິແລ້ວຕ້ອງມີການກະທຳຂອງເມົາສ໌ຕໍ່ເນື່ອງ ເຊັ່ນ ການແຊກຮູບສີ່ແຈສາກ, ການກົດ Enter ພຽງຢ່າງດຽວແມ່ນບໍ່ພໍ: ໃນກໍລະນີເຫຼົ່ານີ້ໃຫ້ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Enter."

#. C72Yu
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153968\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Pressing <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Enter on an icon for creating a draw object. A draw object will be placed into the middle of the view, with a predefined size."
msgstr "ການກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Enter ໃສ່ໄອຄອນສຳລັບສ້າງວັດຖຸພາບແຕ້ມ. ວັດຖຸພາບແຕ້ມຈະຖືກວາງໄວ້ເຄິ່ງກາງຂອງມຸມມອງ ດ້ວຍຂະໜາດທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ລ່ວງໜ້າ."

#. 3DcDc
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3150449\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Enter on the Selection tool to select the first draw object in the document. If you want to edit, size, or move the selected draw object, first use <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+F6 to set the focus into the document."
msgstr "ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Enter ໃສ່ເຄື່ອງມືການເລືອກ ເພື່ອເລືອກວັດຖຸພາບແຕ້ມທຳອິດໃນເອກະສານ. ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການແກ້ໄຂ, ປ່ຽນຂະໜາດ, ຫຼື ຍ້າຍວັດຖຸພາບແຕ້ມທີ່ເລືອກ, ທຳອິດໃຫ້ໃຊ້ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+F6 ເພື່ອຕັ້ງຈຸດສຸມໃສ່ເອກະສານ."

#. ESLAN
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3151041\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If a toolbar is longer than can be displayed on screen, it shows an icon at the right or lower edge. Select the toolbar and press PageUp or PageDown to display the remaining icons."
msgstr "ຖ້າແຖບເຄື່ອງມືຍາວກວ່າທີ່ສາມາດສະແດງໃນໜ້າຈໍໄດ້, ມັນຈະສະແດງໄອຄອນຢູ່ຂອບຂວາ ຫຼື ຂອບລຸ່ມ. ເລືອກແຖບເຄື່ອງມືແລ້ວກົດ PageUp ຫຼື PageDown ເພື່ອສະແດງໄອຄອນທີ່ເຫຼືອ."

#. VYnbu
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150440\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Special hints for toolbars"
msgstr "ຄຳແນະນຳພິເສດສຳລັບແຖບເຄື່ອງມື"

#. gF4DA
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3149983\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press the down arrow or right arrow to open the selected toolbar. This is equivalent to a mouse click. In the toolbar use the right arrow and left arrow keys. The Home and End keys select the first and last icon in the toolbar, respectively."
msgstr "ກົດລູກສອນລົງ ຫຼື ລູກສອນຂວາເພື່ອເປີດແຖບເຄື່ອງມືທີ່ເລືອກ. ສິ່ງນີ້ທຽບເທົ່າກັບການຄລິກເມົາສ໌. ໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມື ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມລູກສອນຂວາ ແລະ ຊ້າຍ. ປຸ່ມ Home ແລະ End ໃຊ້ເລືອກໄອຄອນທຳອິດ ແລະ ສຸດທ້າຍໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມືຕາມລຳດັບ."

#. Ky9sF
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145365\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Close the toolbar with Esc. It is not possible to move the toolbar without a mouse."
msgstr "ປິດແຖບເຄື່ອງມືດ້ວຍ Esc. ມັນເປັນໄປບໍ່ໄດ້ທີ່ຈະຍ້າຍແຖບເຄື່ອງມືໂດຍບໍ່ໃຊ້ເມົາສ໌."

#. QUtqD
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3151119\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Selection from a combo box"
msgstr "ການເລືອກຈາກກ່ອງຄອມໂບ (Combo box)"

#. wHmx2
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3146986\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id3148645\" src=\"media/helpimg/zellvor.png\" width=\"1.15in\" height=\"0.3165in\" localize=\"true\"><alt id=\"alt_id3148645\">Combo box</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id3148645\" src=\"media/helpimg/zellvor.png\" width=\"1.15in\" height=\"0.3165in\" localize=\"true\"><alt id=\"alt_id3148645\">ກ່ອງຄອມໂບ</alt></image>"

#. CG43T
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3149666\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the combo box. Press Enter."
msgstr "ເລືອກກ່ອງຄອມໂບ. ກົດ Enter."

#. eymZS
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3155366\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the down arrow or Page Down key to scroll down the combo box entries, or the up arrow or Page Up key to scroll upwards. The Home key takes you to the first entry and the End key takes you to the last entry."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ລູກສອນລົງ ຫຼື ປຸ່ມ Page Down ເພື່ອເລື່ອນລົງເບິ່ງລາຍການໃນກ່ອງຄອມໂບ, ຫຼື ໃຊ້ລູກສອນຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ປຸ່ມ Page Up ເພື່ອເລື່ອນຂຶ້ນ. ປຸ່ມ Home ຈະນຳທ່ານໄປຫາລາຍການທຳອິດ ແລະ ປຸ່ມ End ຈະນຳທ່ານໄປຫາລາຍການສຸດທ້າຍ."

#. JWWir
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145749\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press Enter to execute the selected entry."
msgstr "ກົດ Enter ເພື່ອເລືອກລາຍການນັ້ນ."

#. p6ws2
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150685\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Selection in Tables"
msgstr "ການເລືອກໃນຕາຕະລາງ"

#. 3XWAB
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154320\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In several windows, dialogs, and in the table control field, there are tables to select data, for instance, in the right part of the <link href=\"text/shared/guide/database_main.xhp\">Data Source View</link>. The following keys are used for selections in these tables:"
msgstr "ໃນຫຼາຍໜ້າຕ່າງ, ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ, ແລະ ໃນຊ່ອງຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ, ຈະມີຕາຕະລາງເພື່ອເລືອກຂໍ້ມູນ, ຕົວຢ່າງ: ໃນສ່ວນຂວາຂອງ <link href=\"text/shared/guide/database_main.xhp\">ມຸມມອງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ</link>. ປຸ່ມຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ແມ່ນໃຊ້ສຳລັບການເລືອກໃນຕາຕະລາງເຫຼົ່ານີ້:"

#. gcpwK
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154014\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Spacebar: switches from selection of the current row and cancellation of any selection, but not if the current cell is in edit mode."
msgstr "Spacebar: ສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງການເລືອກແຖວປັດຈຸບັນ ແລະ ການຍົກເລີກການເລືອກໃດໆ, ແຕ່ຈະໃຊ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖ້າເຊວປັດຈຸບັນຢູ່ໃນໂໝດແກ້ໄຂ."

#. JW7D6
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3147396\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+spacebar: switches between selection of the current row and cancellation of this selection."
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+spacebar: ສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງການເລືອກແຖວປັດຈຸບັນ ແລະ ການຍົກເລີກການເລືອກນີ້."

#. GXFNH
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3149488\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Shift+spacebar: switches between selection of the current column and cancellation of this selection."
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Shift+spacebar: ສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງການເລືອກຄໍລຳປັດຈຸບັນ ແລະ ການຍົກເລີກການເລືອກນີ້."

#. EgAEL
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3156286\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+Up Arrow or <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+Down Arrow: moves the window separator between table and form, for instance in the bibliography database."
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+ລູກສອນຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+ລູກສອນລົງ: ຍ້າຍຕົວແບ່ງໜ້າຕ່າງລະຫວ່າງຕາຕະລາງ ແລະ ຟອມ, ຕົວຢ່າງ: ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນບັນນານຸກົມ."

#. dJvRL
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145251\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In a table control or in the data source view, the Tab key moves to the next column. To move to the next control, press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab. To move to the previous control, press Shift+<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab."
msgstr "ໃນການຄວບຄຸມຕາຕະລາງ ຫຼື ໃນມຸມມອງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ, ປຸ່ມ Tab ຈະຍ້າຍໄປຫາຄໍລຳຖັດໄປ. ເພື່ອຍ້າຍໄປຫາການຄວບຄຸມຖັດໄປ, ໃຫ້ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab. ເພື່ອຍ້າຍໄປຫາການຄວບຄຸມກ່ອນໜ້າ, ໃຫ້ກົດ Shift+<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab."

#. dE4w5
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150592\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Size and Position of Windows and Dialogs"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ ແລະ ຕຳແໜ່ງຂອງໜ້າຕ່າງ ແລະ ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ"

#. 8qGEW
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153221\n"
"help.text"
msgid "First press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+spacebar."
msgstr "ທຳອິດໃຫ້ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+spacebar."

#. FBLcn
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3148456\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A system menu opens with menu commands like <emph>Move</emph>, <emph>Resize</emph> and <emph>Close</emph>."
msgstr "ເມນູລະບົບຈະເປີດຂຶ້ນພ້ອມກັບຄຳສັ່ງເມນູ ເຊັ່ນ <emph>ຍ້າຍ</emph>, <emph>ປ່ຽນຂະໜາດ</emph> ແລະ <emph>ປິດ</emph>."

#. ujmrq
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3149400\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose a command (down arrow, then Enter)."
msgstr "ເລືອກຄຳສັ່ງ (ລູກສອນລົງ, ແລ້ວກົດ Enter)."

#. GtEXo
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3155083\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Now you can use the arrow keys to move or resize the dialog or window."
msgstr "ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ປຸ່ມລູກສອນເພື່ອຍ້າຍ ຫຼື ປ່ຽນຂະໜາດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ ຫຼື ໜ້າຕ່າງໄດ້ແລ້ວ."

#. vKnPK
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3147497\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press Enter to accept the change. Press Escape to cancel the changes."
msgstr "ກົດ Enter ເພື່ອຍອມຮັບການປ່ຽນແປງ. ກົດ Escape ເພື່ອຍົກເລີກການປ່ຽນແປງ."

#. GdqRD
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146988\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Docking and Undocking Windows and Toolbars"
msgstr "ການລັອກ ແລະ ການປົດລັອກໜ້າຕ່າງ ແລະ ແຖບເຄື່ອງມື"

#. esDv2
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3147176\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press F6 until the window or toolbar is selected."
msgstr "ກົດ F6 ຈົນກ່ວາໜ້າຕ່າງ ຫຼື ແຖບເຄື່ອງມືຈະຖືກເລືອກ."

#. nQg7G
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153707\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Shift+F10."
msgstr "ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Shift+F10."

#. AzECR
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154479\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Selecting objects"
msgstr "ການເລືອກວັດຖຸ"

#. EfvnX
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3148993\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press Shift+F4 to select the first object in the current document. When an object is selected, press Tab to select the next object, or press Esc to go back to the text."
msgstr "ກົດ Shift+F4 ເພື່ອເລືອກວັດຖຸທຳອິດໃນເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນ. ເມື່ອວັດຖຸຖືກເລືອກແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ກົດ Tab ເພື່ອເລືອກວັດຖຸຖັດໄປ, ຫຼື ກົດ Esc ເພື່ອ返回ຫາຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#. oLnTz
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3152962\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Edit Objects"
msgstr "ແກ້ໄຂວັດຖຸ"

#. qGxK2
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3156379\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A selected OLE object can be activated with the Enter key."
msgstr "ວັດຖຸ OLE ທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ສາມາດເປີດໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ດ້ວຍປຸ່ມ Enter."

#. sE76L
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155766\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Edit Position and Size of Objects"
msgstr "ແກ້ໄຂຕຳແໜ່ງ ແລະ ຂະໜາດຂອງວັດຖຸ"

#. bU8KB
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3148405\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the arrow keys to move the selected object by one grid resolution unit."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມລູກສອນເພື່ອຍ້າຍວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກໄປເທື່ອລະໜຶ່ງຫົວໜ່ວຍຄວາມລະອຽດຂອງເສັ້ນຕາຕະລາງ (grid)."

#. owurq
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145619\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Set the grid resolution unit with <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Writer - Grid</emph> in the <emph>Resolution</emph> area. If you enter a number greater than 1 in the <emph>Subdivision</emph> area, you must press the arrow key as often as the number states to move the selected object by one grid resolution unit."
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຄ່າຫົວໜ່ວຍຄວາມລະອຽດຂອງເສັ້ນຕາຕະລາງໄດ້ທີ່ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ຄ່າກຳນົດ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Writer - ເສັ້ນຕາຕະລາງ</emph> ໃນສ່ວນ <emph>ຄວາມລະອຽດ (Resolution)</emph>. ຖ້າທ່ານປ້ອນຕົວເລກທີ່ຫຼາຍກວ່າ 1 ໃນສ່ວນ <emph>ການແບ່ງຍ່ອຍ (Subdivision)</emph>, ທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງກົດປຸ່ມລູກສອນຫຼາຍຄັ້ງຕາມຈຳນວນຕົວເລກນັ້ນ ເພື່ອຍ້າຍວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກໄປໜຶ່ງຫົວໜ່ວຍຄວາມລະອຽດ."

#. 6Vt2A
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3166450\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> and arrow keys to move the selected object by one pixel."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> ແລະ ປຸ່ມລູກສອນ ເພື່ອຍ້າຍວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກໄປເທື່ອລະໜຶ່ງພິກເຊວ (pixel)."

#. 4FDVv
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3147345\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab to enter the handle edit mode. The upper left handle is the active handle, it starts blinking. Use <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab to select the next handle. Press Escape to exit the handle edit mode."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab ເພື່ອເຂົ້າສູ່ໂໝດແກ້ໄຂຈຸດຈັດການ. ຈຸດຈັດການມຸມຊ້າຍເທິງຈະເປັນຈຸດທີ່ໃຊ້ງານຢູ່ ແລະ ຈະເລີ່ມກະພິບ. ໃຊ້ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab ເພື່ອເລືອກຈຸດຈັດການຖັດໄປ. ກົດ Escape ເພື່ອອອກຈາກໂໝດແກ້ໄຂຈຸດຈັດການ."

#. Js3F6
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3149565\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the handle edit mode, the arrow keys move the selected handle, which changes the object size."
msgstr "ໃນໂໝດແກ້ໄຂຈຸດຈັດການ, ປຸ່ມລູກສອນຈະຍ້າຍຈຸດຈັດການທີ່ເລືອກ ເຊິ່ງຈະເປັນການປ່ຽນແປງຂະໜາດຂອງວັດຖຸ."

#. t4yuN
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147361\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Edit the Anchors of Objects"
msgstr "ແກ້ໄຂຈຸດຍຶດ (Anchors) ຂອງວັດຖຸ"

#. 5uZDF
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3148534\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can move the anchor of an object with the arrow keys. First enter the handle edit mode and select the anchor. Depending on the type of anchor, you can then move the anchor in different directions."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດຍ້າຍຈຸດຍຶດຂອງວັດຖຸໄດ້ດ້ວຍປຸ່ມລູກສອນ. ທຳອິດໃຫ້ເຂົ້າສູ່ໂໝດແກ້ໄຂຈຸດຈັດການ ແລະ ເເລືອກຈຸດຍຶດ. ຂຶ້ນຢູ່ກັບປະເພດຂອງຈຸດຍຶດ, ທ່ານສາມາດຍ້າຍຈຸດຍຶດໄປໃນທິດທາງຕ່າງໆໄດ້."

#. uFgP5
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3163808\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the object."
msgstr "ເລືອກວັດຖຸ."

#. B5tPs
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3150646\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the handle edit mode with <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab."
msgstr "ເຂົ້າສູ່ໂໝດແກ້ໄຂຈຸດຈັດການດ້ວຍ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab."

#. dyTrD
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3150940\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The upper left handle starts blinking. Press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab several times, until no handle blinks. This signals that now the anchor of the object is activated. <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"WRITER\">In text documents you can press Shift+<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+A to activate the anchor directly.</caseinline></switchinline>"
msgstr "ຈຸດຈັດການມຸມຊ້າຍເທິງຈະເລີ່ມກະພິບ. ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Tab ຫຼາຍໆຄັ້ງ ຈົນກ່ວາຈະບໍ່ມີຈຸດຈັດການໃດກະພິບ. ນີ້ແມ່ນສັນຍານບອກວ່າຕອນນີ້ຈຸດຍຶດຂອງວັດຖຸໄດ້ຖືກເປີດໃຊ້ງານແລ້ວ. <switchinline select=\"appl\"><caseinline select=\"WRITER\">ໃນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ ທ່ານສາມາດກົດ Shift+<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+A ເພື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ງານຈຸດຍຶດໂດຍກົງ.</caseinline></switchinline>"

#. sGjud
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153919\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the arrow keys to move the anchor. The object follows the anchor as appropriate."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມລູກສອນເພື່ອຍ້າຍຈຸດຍຶດ. ວັດຖຸຈະເຄື່ອນຍ້າຍຕາມຈຸດຍຶດຕາມຄວາມເໝາະສົມ."

#. uyvCb
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3152582\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can change the anchor of the selected object for example in the object's context menu."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດປ່ຽນຈຸດຍຶດຂອງວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກໄດ້ ຕົວຢ່າງ: ໃນເມນູລັດຂອງວັດຖຸນັ້ນ."

#. fC9GZ
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3148393\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the object is anchored <emph>To Paragraph</emph>, the arrow keys move the object to the previous or next paragraph."
msgstr "ຖ້າວັດຖຸຖືກຍຶດໄວ້ <emph>ກັບຫຍໍ້ໜ້າ</emph>, ປຸ່ມລູກສອນຈະຍ້າຍວັດຖຸໄປຫາຫຍໍ້ໜ້າກ່ອນໜ້າ ຫຼື ຖັດໄປ."

#. z6hBG
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145615\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the object is anchored<emph> To page</emph>, the keys Page Up or Page Down move it to the previous or next page."
msgstr "ຖ້າວັດຖຸຖືກຍຶດໄວ້ <emph>ກັບໜ້າ</emph>, ປຸ່ມ Page Up ຫຼື Page Down ຈະຍ້າຍວັດຖຸໄປຫາໜ້າກ່ອນໜ້າ ຫຼື ຖັດໄປ."

#. Ez4QD
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145135\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the object is anchored <emph>To character</emph>, the Arrow keys move it through the current paragraph."
msgstr "ຖ້າວັດຖຸຖືກຍຶດໄວ້ <emph>ກັບຕົວອັກສອນ</emph>, ປຸ່ມລູກສອນຈະຍ້າຍວັດຖຸຜ່ານຫຍໍ້ໜ້າປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. fjjjA
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145256\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the object is anchored<emph> As character</emph>, no anchor icon exists. You cannot move the object."
msgstr "ຖ້າວັດຖຸຖືກຍຶດໄວ້ <emph>ເປັນຕົວອັກສອນ</emph>, ຈະບໍ່ມີໄອຄອນຈຸດຍຶດປະກົດຂຶ້ນ. ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດຍ້າຍວັດຖຸໄດ້."

#. AFkk8
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3149527\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the object is anchored <emph>To frame</emph>, the Arrow keys move it to the next frame in the respective direction."
msgstr "ຖ້າວັດຖຸຖືກຍຶດໄວ້ <emph>ກັບເຟຣມ</emph>, ປຸ່ມລູກສອນຈະຍ້າຍວັດຖຸໄປຫາເຟຣມຖັດໄປໃນທິດທາງນັ້ນໆ."

#. hoD4g
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154492\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Controlling the Data Source View"
msgstr "ການຄວບຄຸມມຸມມອງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. rQDqx
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3150515\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline> + Shift + F4 opens and closes the data source view."
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline> + Shift + F4 ໃຊ້ເປີດ ແລະ ປິດມຸມມອງແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. 3xgK2
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3159109\n"
"help.text"
msgid "F6: switches between document and toolbars."
msgstr "F6: ສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງເອກະສານ ແລະ ແຖບເຄື່ອງມື."

#. eFCow
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153229\n"
"help.text"
msgid "+ (plus key): expands the selected entry in the data source explorer."
msgstr "+ (ປຸ່ມບວກ): ຂະຫຍາຍລາຍການທີ່ເລືອກໃນຕົວສຳຫຼວດແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. 58L73
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3150312\n"
"help.text"
msgid "- (minus key): collapses the selected entry in the data source explorer."
msgstr "- (ປຸ່ມລົບ): ຫຍໍ້ລາຍການທີ່ເລືອກໃນຕົວສຳຫຼວດແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. J5kBH
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154368\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Shift+E: switches between data source explorer and table."
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Shift+E: ສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງຕົວສຳຫຼວດແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ຕາຕະລາງ."

#. cgt4D
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147171\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Shortcuts in the Query Design Window"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມລັດໃນໜ້າຕ່າງການອອກແບບຄຳຖາມ (Query Design)"

#. FEQVg
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3152455\n"
"help.text"
msgid "F6: switches between object bar, table view, and selection area."
msgstr "F6: ສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງແຖບວັດຖຸ, ມຸມມອງຕາຕະລາງ, ແລະ ພື້ນທີ່ການເລືອກ."

#. Fb8AD
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3151180\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+Up arrow or <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+Down arrow: moves the border between table view and selection area up or down."
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+ລູກສອນຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+ລູກສອນລົງ: ຍ້າຍຂອບເຂດລະຫວ່າງມຸມມອງຕາຕະລາງ ແລະ ພື້ນທີ່ການເລືອກຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ລົງ."

#. TKgfU
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3156288\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Keys in the Table View (upper area of the query design) and in the Relations window"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມຕ່າງໆໃນມຸມມອງຕາຕະລາງ (ສ່ວນເທິງຂອງການອອກແບບຄຳຖາມ) ແລະ ໃນໜ້າຕ່າງຄວາມສຳພັນ (Relations)"

#. U3DKR
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3156166\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Arrow key: moves the selected table in the direction of the arrow."
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+ປຸ່ມລູກສອນ: ຍ້າຍຕາຕະລາງທີ່ເລືອກໄປຕາມທິດທາງຂອງລູກສອນ."

#. dYmZj
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3147310\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Shift+Arrow key: resizes the selected table in the table view."
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Shift+ປຸ່ມລູກສອນ: ປ່ຽນຂະໜາດຕາຕະລາງທີ່ເລືອກໃນມຸມມອງຕາຕະລາງ."

#. FRZ72
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3152986\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Del: removes the selected table or connection from the table view."
msgstr "Del: ລຶບຕາຕະລາງ ຫຼື ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ທີ່ເລືອກອອກຈາກມຸມມອງຕາຕະລາງ."

#. rucmF
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145384\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Tab: switches between tables and connections in the table view."
msgstr "Tab: ສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງຕາຕະລາງ ແລະ ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ໃນມຸມມອງຕາຕະລາງ."

#. vPBuT
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154529\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter: when a connection is selected, the Enter key opens the <emph>Properties</emph> dialog of the connection."
msgstr "Enter: ເມື່ອການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຖືກເລືອກ, ປຸ່ມ Enter ຈະເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ຄຸນສົມບັດ</emph> ຂອງການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ນັ້ນ."

#. HCnZa
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3159624\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter: when a table is selected, the Enter key enters the first data field from the list box into the selection area."
msgstr "Enter: ເມື່ອຕາຕະລາງຖືກເລືອກ, ປຸ່ມ Enter ຈະນຳເອົາຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນທຳອິດຈາກກ່ອງລາຍການເຂົ້າສູ່ພື້ນທີ່ການເລືອກ."

#. ACvTB
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153816\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Keys in the Selection Area (bottom area of the query design)"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມຕ່າງໆໃນພື້ນທີ່ການເລືອກ (ສ່ວນລຸ່ມຂອງການອອກແບບຄຳຖາມ)"

#. mbsWx
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3152896\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+Left Arrow or Right Arrow: moves the selected column to the left or to the right."
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline>+ລູກສອນຊ້າຍ ຫຼື ລູກສອນຂວາ: ຍ້າຍຄໍລຳທີ່ເລືອກໄປທາງຊ້າຍ ຫຼື ທາງຂວາ."

#. Gr6zg
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146152\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Keys in the Table Design Window"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມຕ່າງໆໃນໜ້າຕ່າງການອອກແບບຕາຕະລາງ"

#. tcHgm
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3151243\n"
"help.text"
msgid "F6: switches between toolbar, column view, and properties area."
msgstr "F6: ສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງແຖບເຄື່ອງມື, ມຸມມອງຄໍລຳ, ແລະ ພື້ນທີ່ຄຸນສົມບັດ."

#. xeLPP
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145075\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Controlling the ImageMap Editor"
msgstr "ການຄວບຄຸມຕົວແກ້ໄຂແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ (ImageMap Editor)"

#. SVn5z
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3159096\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press Tab to select an icon. If you selected one of the icons from <emph>Rectangle</emph> to <emph>Freeform Polygon</emph> and you press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command                           </caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Enter</keycode>, an object of the selected type is created in default size."
msgstr "ກົດ Tab ເພື່ອເລືອກໄອຄອນ. ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກໄອຄອນໃດໜຶ່ງຕັ້ງແຕ່ <emph>ຮູບສີ່ແຈສາກ</emph> ຈົນເຖິງ <emph>ຮູບຫຼາຍແຈແບບອິດສະຫຼະ</emph> ແລະ ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command </caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Enter</keycode>, ວັດຖຸປະເພດທີ່ເລືອກຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນຂະໜາດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ."

#. go9cM
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3156016\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you press <keycode>Enter</keycode> while the icon <emph>Select</emph> is selected, the focus is set into the image window of the ImageMap Editor. Press <keycode>Esc</keycode> to set the focus back to the icons and input boxes."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານກົດ <keycode>Enter</keycode> ໃນຂະນະທີ່ໄອຄອນ <emph>ເລືອກ</emph> ຖືກເລືອກຢູ່, ຈຸດສຸມຈະຖືກຕັ້ງໃສ່ໜ້າຕ່າງຮູບພາບຂອງຕົວແກ້ໄຂແຜນຜັງຮູບພາບ. ກົດ <keycode>Esc</keycode> ເພື່ອຕັ້ງຈຸດສຸມກັບຄືນຫາໄອຄອນ ແລະ ຊ່ອງປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. 2DD3n
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3149587\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the <emph>Select</emph> icon is selected and you press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Enter</keycode>, the first object in the image window gets selected."
msgstr "ຖ້າໄອຄອນ <emph>ເລືອກ</emph> ຖືກເລືອກຢູ່ ແລະ ທ່ານກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Enter</keycode>, ວັດຖຸທຳອິດໃນໜ້າຕ່າງຮູບພາບຈະຖືກເລືອກ."

#. 3Wh8W
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154343\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the icon <emph>Edit Points</emph> to switch into the point edit mode for polygons and back."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ໄອຄອນ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂຈຸດ</emph> ເພື່ອສະຫຼັບເຂົ້າສູ່ໂໝດແກ້ໄຂຈຸດສຳລັບຮູບຫຼາຍແຈ ແລະ ກັບຄືນ."

#. aGQmN
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3147073\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Tab</keycode> in the image window to select the next point. Use <keycode>Shift+</keycode><switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Tab</keycode> to select the previous point."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Tab</keycode> ໃນໜ້າຕ່າງຮູບພາບເພື່ອເລືອກຈຸດຖັດໄປ. ໃຊ້ <keycode>Shift+</keycode><switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Tab</keycode> ເພື່ອເລືອກຈຸດກ່ອນໜ້າ."

#. 7BdLu
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153285\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the Delete key with the focus in the image window to delete the selected object."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ Delete ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຈຸດສຸມຢູ່ໃນໜ້າຕ່າງຮູບພາບ ເພື່ອລຶບວັດຖຸທີ່ເລືອກ."

#. vG5xx
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145377\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Controlling the Help"
msgstr "ການຄວບຄຸມສ່ວນຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ"

#. Rf4nG
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3149441\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press Shift+F1 to display the <link href=\"text/shared/main0108.xhp\">Extended Tips</link> for the currently selected command, icon or control."
msgstr "ກົດ Shift+F1 ເພື່ອສະແດງ <link href=\"text/shared/main0108.xhp\">ຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມ</link> ສຳລັບຄຳສັ່ງ, ໄອຄອນ ຫຼື ຕົວຄວບຄຸມທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. tB7qW
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154960\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Navigating the main help pages"
msgstr "ການນຳທາງໃນໜ້າຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຫຼັກ"

#. SABZN
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3151300\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the main help pages, use Tab to jump to the next hyperlink or Shift+Tab to jump to the previous link."
msgstr "ໃນໜ້າຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຫຼັກ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ Tab ເພື່ອໂດດໄປຫາການເຊື່ອມໂຍງຖັດໄປ ຫຼື Shift+Tab ເພື່ອໂດດໄປຫາລິ້ງກ່ອນໜ້າ."

#. EjxQD
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3155537\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press Enter to execute the selected hyperlink."
msgstr "ກົດ Enter ເພື່ອເປີດການເຊື່ອມໂຍງທີ່ເລືອກ."

#. 3G77H
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154912\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press Backspace above the Enter key to return to the previous help page."
msgstr "ກົດ Backspace (ຢູ່ເທິງປຸ່ມ Enter) ເພື່ອກັບຄືນຫາໜ້າຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້."

#. DGCD3
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150894\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Controlling the Text Import dialog (CSV file import)"
msgstr "ການຄວບຄຸມກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບການນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ຄວາມ (ການນຳເຂົ້າໄຟລ໌ CSV)"

#. UWvvM
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153975\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Ruler"
msgstr "ໄມ້ບັນທັດ"

#. yPj3T
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3152869\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Left or Right Arrow: go one position to the left or to the right"
msgstr "ລູກສອນຊ້າຍ ຫຼື ຂວາ: ໄປໜຶ່ງຕຳແໜ່ງທາງຊ້າຍ ຫຼື ທາງຂວາ"

#. DAQJ5
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3151000\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Left Arrow</keycode> or <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Right Arrow</keycode>: jump to the previous or to the next split"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+ລູກສອນຊ້າຍ</keycode> ຫຼື <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+ລູກສອນຂວາ</keycode>: ໂດດໄປຫາການແບ່ງກ່ອນໜ້າ ຫຼື ຖັດໄປ"

#. a7Hg8
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3159203\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+Left Arrow</keycode> or <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+Right Arrow</keycode>: move a split one position to the left or to the right"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+ລູກສອນຊ້າຍ</keycode> ຫຼື <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+ລູກສອນຂວາ</keycode>: ຍ້າຍການແບ່ງໄປໜຶ່ງຕຳແໜ່ງທາງຊ້າຍ ຫຼື ທາງຂວາ"

#. xVvaL
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154538\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Home or End: jump to the first or the last possible position"
msgstr "Home ຫຼື End: ໂດດໄປຫາຕຳແໜ່ງທຳອິດ ຫຼື ສຸດທ້າຍທີ່ເປັນໄປໄດ້"

#. BjuQx
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3155382\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Home</keycode> or <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+End</keycode>: jump to the first or the last split"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Home</keycode> ຫຼື <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+End</keycode>: ໂດດໄປຫາການແບ່ງທຳອິດ ຫຼື ສຸດທ້າຍ"

#. 6CuHs
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3155894\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<keycode>Shift+</keycode><switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Home</keycode> or <keycode>Shift+</keycode><switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+End</keycode>: move split to the first or to the last position"
msgstr "<keycode>Shift+</keycode><switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Home</keycode> ຫຼື <keycode>Shift+</keycode><switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+End</keycode>: ຍ້າຍການແບ່ງໄປຫາຕຳແໜ່ງທຳອິດ ຫຼື ສຸດທ້າຍ"

#. yxCwG
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145195\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Space key: insert or remove a split"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມຍະວ່າງ: ແຊກ ຫຼື ລຶບການແບ່ງອອກ"

#. ABCqE
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154647\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Insert key: insert a split (leave existing splits unchanged)"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມ Insert: ແຊກການແບ່ງ (ຮັກສາການແບ່ງທີ່ມີຢູ່ໄວ້ຄືເກົ່ວ)"

#. NJqDM
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154765\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Delete key: delete a split"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມ Delete: ລຶບການແບ່ງອອກ"

#. 3i6AT
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154650\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Shift+Delete: delete all splits"
msgstr "Shift+Delete: ລຶບການແບ່ງທັງໝົດອອກ"

#. TjKpg
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145368\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Up Arrow or Down Arrow: scroll table down or up one row"
msgstr "ລູກສອນຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ລູກສອນລົງ: ເລື່ອນຕາຕະລາງຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ລົງເທື່ອລະແຖວ"

#. FFTNR
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3155914\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Page Up or Page Down: scroll table down or up one page"
msgstr "Page Up ຫຼື Page Down: ເລື່ອນຕາຕະລາງຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ລົງເທື່ອລະໜ້າ"

#. jCoBc
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3147492\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Escape key (during mouse drag): cancel drag, move split to old position"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມ Escape (ໃນລະຫວ່າງລາກເມົາສ໌): ຍົກເລີກການລາກ, ຍ້າຍການແບ່ງກັບຄືນຫາຕຳແໜ່ງເກົ່າ"

#. GBGVF
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145216\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Preview"
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ"

#. k4PDB
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3155148\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Left Arrow or Right Arrow: select left or right column and clear other selections"
msgstr "ລູກສອນຊ້າຍ ຫຼື ລູກສອນຂວາ: ເລືອກຄໍລຳຊ້າຍ ຫຼື ຂວາ ແລະ ລຶບການເລືອກອື່ນໆອອກ"

#. mv3ff
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3150780\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Left Arrow</keycode> or <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Right Arrow</keycode>: move focus to the left or to the right column (does not change selection)"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+ລູກສອນຊ້າຍ</keycode> ຫຼື <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+ລູກສອນຂວາ</keycode>: ຍ້າຍຈຸດສຸມໄປຫາຄໍລຳຊ້າຍ ຫຼື ຂວາ (ບໍ່ປ່ຽນແປງການເລືອກ)"

#. FySem
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153811\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Shift+Left Arrow or Shift+Right Arrow: expand or shrink the selected range"
msgstr "Shift+ລູກສອນຊ້າຍ ຫຼື Shift+ລູກສອນຂວາ: ຂະຫຍາຍ ຫຼື ຫຍໍ້ຊ່ວງທີ່ເລືອກ"

#. tEBDC
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3146962\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+Left Arrow</keycode> or <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+Right Arrow</keycode>: expand or shrink the selected range (does not change other selections)"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+ລູກສອນຊ້າຍ</keycode> ຫຼື <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+ລູກສອນຂວາ</keycode>: ຂະຫຍາຍ ຫຼື ຫຍໍ້ຊ່ວງທີ່ເລືອກ (ບໍ່ປ່ຽນແປງການເລືອກອື່ນໆ)"

#. DbNiK
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3147512\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<keycode>Home</keycode> or <keycode>End</keycode>: select the first or the last column (use <keycode>Shift</keycode> or <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> as with cursor keys)"
msgstr "<keycode>Home</keycode> ຫຼື <keycode>End</keycode>: ເລືອກຄໍລຳທຳອິດ ຫຼື ສຸດທ້າຍ (ໃຊ້ <keycode>Shift</keycode> ຫຼື <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline> ຄືກັບປຸ່ມເຄີເຊີ)"

#. 8F5dq
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154733\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Shift+Space key: select the range from the last selected column to the current column"
msgstr "Shift+ປຸ່ມຍະວ່າງ: ເລືອກຊ່ວງຕັ້ງແຕ່ຄໍລຳສຸດທ້າຍທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ຈົນເຖິງຄໍລຳປັດຈຸບັນ"

#. ZaRPr
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3154171\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+Space</keycode> key: select the range from the last selected column to the current column (does not change other selections)"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Shift+ປຸ່ມຍະວ່າງ</keycode>: ເລືອກຊ່ວງຕັ້ງແຕ່ຄໍລຳສຸດທ້າຍທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ຈົນເຖິງຄໍລຳປັດຈຸບັນ (ບໍ່ປ່ຽນແປງການເລືອກອື່ນໆ)"

#. mCZzB
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3156368\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+A</keycode>: select all columns"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+A</keycode>: ເລືອກທຸກຄໍລຳ"

#. GErPh
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3151192\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Shift+F10: open a context menu"
msgstr "Shift+F10: ເປີດເມນູລັດ"

#. iFCKi
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3150416\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+1</keycode> ... <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+7</keycode>: set the 1st ... 7th column type for the selected columns"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+1</keycode> ... <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+7</keycode>: ຕັ້ງຄ່າປະເພດຄໍລຳທີ 1 ... 7 ສຳລັບຄໍລຳທີ່ເລືອກ"

#. S7mnM
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3166442\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Up Arrow or Down Arrow: scroll table down or up one row"
msgstr "ລູກສອນຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ລູກສອນລົງ: ເລື່ອນຕາຕະລາງຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ລົງເທື່ອລະແຖວ"

#. SncEK
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3146103\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Page Up or Page Down: scroll table down or up one page"
msgstr "Page Up ຫຼື Page Down: ເລື່ອນຕາຕະລາງຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ລົງເທື່ອລະໜ້າ"

#. p6erp
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3145116\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Home</keycode> or <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+End</keycode>: scroll to the top or bottom of a table"
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+Home</keycode> ຫຼື <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline><keycode>+End</keycode>: ເລື່ອນໄປຫາສ່ວນເທິງສຸດ ຫຼື ສ່ວນລຸ່ມສຸດຂອງຕາຕະລາງ"

#. FYdWx
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153298\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Controlling the Insert - Special Character Dialog"
msgstr "ການຄວບຄຸມກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ ແຊກ - ອັກຂະລະພິເສດ"

#. nBvFy
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153073\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Tab switches through all controls in the dialog."
msgstr "Tab ໃຊ້ສະຫຼັບຜ່ານທຸກຕົວຄວບຄຸມໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ."

#. pjUA8
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153295\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+Down Arrow opens a combo box. Enter selects the current entry in the combo box."
msgstr "<switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+ລູກສອນລົງ ໃຊ້ເປີດກ່ອງຄອມໂບ. Enter ໃຊ້ເລືອກລາຍການປັດຈຸບັນໃນກ່ອງຄອມໂບ."

#. copKh
#: keyboard.xhp
msgctxt ""
"keyboard.xhp\n"
"par_id3153958\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Arrow buttons move through the main selection area. Spacebar adds the current character to the list of characters to be inserted."
msgstr "ປຸ່ມລູກສອນໃຊ້ເຄີື່ອນຍ້າຍຜ່ານພື້ນທີ່ການເລືອກຫຼັກ. Spacebar ໃຊ້ເພີ່ມອັກຂະລະປັດຈຸບັນເຂົ້າໃນລາຍການອັກຂະລະທີ່ຈະແຊກ."

#. usAJE
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Creating and Printing Labels and Business Cards"
msgstr "ການສ້າງ ແລະ ການພິມປ້າຍຊື່ ແລະ ນາມບັດ"

#. sVe5Y
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"bm_id3150774\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>labels; creating and synchronizing</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>business cards; creating and synchronizing</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>synchronizing;labels and business cards</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ປ້າຍຊື່; ການສ້າງ ແລະ ການປະສານສົມທົບ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ນາມບັດ; ການສ້າງ ແລະ ການປະສານສົມທົບ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການປະສານສົມທົບ; ປ້າຍຊື່ ແລະ ນາມບັດ</bookmark_value>"

#. XNFQ4
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150774\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"labels\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/labels.xhp\">Creating and Printing Labels and Business Cards</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"labels\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/labels.xhp\">ການສ້າງ ແລະ ການພິມປ້າຍຊື່ ແລະ ນາມບັດ</link></variable>"

#. a2rtY
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153345\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Designing Business Cards Through a Dialog"
msgstr "ການອອກແບບນາມບັດຜ່ານກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ"

#. SxEpR
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3146798\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <link href=\"text/shared/01/01010300.xhp\"><emph>File - New - Business Cards</emph></link> to open the<emph> Business Cards </emph>dialog, which allows you to choose how your business cards will look."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <link href=\"text/shared/01/01010300.xhp\"><emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ໃໝ່ - ນາມບັດ</emph></link> ເພື່ອເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ນາມບັດ</emph>, ເຊິ່ງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານເລືອກຮູບແບບຂອງນາມບັດຂອງທ່ານໄດ້."

#. WD8J3
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147654\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Designing Labels and Business Cards"
msgstr "ການອອກແບບປ້າຍຊື່ ແລະ ນາມບັດ"

#. kPfrw
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3152349\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can design both labels and business cards through the <emph>Labels</emph> dialog."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດອອກແບບໄດ້ທັງປ້າຍຊື່ ແລະ ນາມບັດຜ່ານກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ປ້າຍຊື່</emph>."

#. uhXze
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3153880\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <link href=\"text/shared/01/01010200.xhp\"><emph>File - New - Labels</emph></link> to open the <emph>Labels</emph> dialog."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <link href=\"text/shared/01/01010200.xhp\"><emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ໃໝ່ - ປ້າຍຊື່</emph></link> ເພື່ອເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ປ້າຍຊື່</emph>."

#. LgAEm
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3149233\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the <emph>Labels</emph> tab, under <emph>Format</emph>, define the label format."
msgstr "ໃນແທັບ <emph>ປ້າຍຊື່</emph>, ພາຍໃຕ້ <emph>ຮູບແບບ</emph>, ໃຫ້ກຳນົດຮູບແບບຂອງປ້າຍຊື່."

#. KaQqW
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3145674\n"
"help.text"
msgid "$[officename] Writer contains many formats of commercially available sheets for labels, badges, and business cards. You can also add other, user-defined formats."
msgstr "$[officename] Writer ມີຮູບແບບແຜ່ນປ້າຍຊື່, ບັດປະຈຳຕົວ, ແລະ ນາມບັດ ທີ່ມີວາງຈຳໜ່າຍທົ່ວໄປຫຼາຍຮູບແບບ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເພີ່ມຮູບແບບອື່ນໆທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ກຳນົດເອງໄດ້."

#. Ua5BG
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3143271\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the <emph>Labels</emph> tab, under <emph>Inscription</emph>, you can choose what you want written on the labels."
msgstr "ໃນແທັບ <emph>ປ້າຍຊື່</emph>, ພາຍໃຕ້ <emph>ຂໍ້ຄວາມຈາລຶກ</emph>, ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກສິ່ງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຂຽນໃສ່ໃນປ້າຍຊື່ໄດ້."

#. 5NA5N
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3145610\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This often involves database fields, so that the labels can be printed with varying content, when sending \"Form Letters\" for example. It is also possible to have the same text printed on every label."
msgstr "ສິ່ງນີ້ມັກຈະກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ປ້າຍຊື່ສາມາດພິມດ້ວຍເນື້ອຫາທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນໄດ້, ຕົວຢ່າງເຊັ່ນ ເມື່ອສົ່ງ \"ຈົດໝາຍວຽນ\". ນອກຈາກນີ້ຍັງສາມາດພິມຂໍ້ຄວາມດຽວກັນໃສ່ທຸກໆປ້າຍຊື່ໄດ້."

#. BryGK
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3151385\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the <emph>Database </emph>and <emph>Table </emph>list boxes to select the database and table from which the data fields are obtained. Click on the arrow button to transfer the selected data field into the inscription area. Press Enter to insert a line break. You can also enter spaces and any other fixed text."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ກ່ອງລາຍການ <emph>ຖານຂໍ້ມູນ</emph> ແລະ <emph>ຕາຕະລາງ</emph> ເພື່ອເລືອກຖານຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ຕາຕະລາງທີ່ຈະດຶງຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນມາ. ຄລິກໃສ່ປຸ່ມລູກສອນເພື່ອຍ້າຍຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເລືອກເຂົ້າສູ່ພື້ນທີ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ກົດ Enter ເພື່ອຂຶ້ນແຖວໃໝ່. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດປ້ອນຍະວ່າງ ແລະ ຂໍ້ຄວາມຄົງທີ່ອື່ນໆໄດ້."

#. 5EjYe
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3147560\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the <emph>Format</emph> tab you can define your own label formats, not covered by the predefined formats. To do this, select \"User\" from the <emph>Type</emph> list box. On the <emph>Options</emph> tab, you can specify whether all labels or only certain ones are to be created."
msgstr "ໃນແທັບ <emph>ຮູບແບບ</emph> ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດຮູບແບບປ້າຍຊື່ຂອງທ່ານເອງໄດ້ ຖ້າບໍ່ມີໃນຮູບແບບທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ລ່ວງໜ້າ. ເພື່ອເຮັດສິ່ງນີ້, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ \"ຜູ້ໃຊ້\" ຈາກກ່ອງລາຍການ <emph>ປະເພດ</emph>. ໃນແທັບ <emph>ຕົວເລືອກ</emph>, ທ່ານສາມາດລະບຸໄດ້ວ່າຈະສ້າງປ້າຍຊື່ທັງໝົດ ຫຼື ສະເພາະບາງອັນ."

#. JxMzr
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3150358\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the <emph>Options</emph> tab page, make sure that the <emph>Synchronize contents</emph> box is selected. If this is selected, a label only has to be entered (on the top left label) and edited once."
msgstr "ໃນໜ້າແທັບ <emph>ຕົວເລືອກ</emph>, ກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າໄດ້ໝາຍທີ່ຊ່ອງ <emph>ປະສານສົມທົບເນື້ອຫາ</emph>. ຖ້າເລືອກສິ່ງນີ້, ທ່ານພຽງແຕ່ປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນໃສ່ປ້າຍຊື່ດຽວ (ປ້າຍຊື່ມຸມຊ້າຍເທິງສຸດ) ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂພຽງຄັ້ງດຽວ."

#. b7yqa
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3149767\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click on <emph>New Document</emph> to create a new document with the settings you have entered."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ <emph>ເອກະສານໃໝ່</emph> ເພື່ອສ້າງເອກະສານໃໝ່ຕາມການຕັ້ງຄ່າທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ປ້ອນໄວ້."

#. L2m7L
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3156424\n"
"help.text"
msgid "As soon as you click on <emph>New Document</emph>, you will see a small window with the <emph>Synchronize Labels</emph> button. Enter the first label. When you click on the <emph>Synchronize Labels</emph> button, the current individual label is copied to all the other labels on the sheet."
msgstr "ທັນທີທີ່ທ່ານຄລິກໃສ່ <emph>ເອກະສານໃໝ່</emph>, ທ່ານຈະເຫັນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມຂະໜາດນ້ອຍທີ່ມີປຸ່ມ <emph>ປະສານສົມທົບປ້າຍ</emph>. ປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນໃສ່ປ້າຍທຳອິດ. ເມື່ອທ່ານຄລິກໃສ່ປຸ່ມ <emph>ປະສານສົມທົບປ້າຍ</emph>, ປ້າຍປັດຈຸບັນຈະຖືກສຳເນົາໄປໃສ່ປ້າຍອື່ນໆທັງໝົດໃນແຜ່ນງານ."

#. EKfDW
#: labels.xhp
msgctxt ""
"labels.xhp\n"
"par_id3150449\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/01/01010300.xhp\">Business Cards</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/01/01010300.xhp\">ນາມບັດ</link>"

#. goNpN
