msgctxt ""
"macro_recording.xhp\n"
"par_id4269234\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Window switching is not recorded."
msgstr "ການສະຫຼັບປ່ອງຢ້ຽມແມ່ນບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກບັນທຶກ."

#. YAhXo
#: macro_recording.xhp
msgctxt ""
"macro_recording.xhp\n"
"par_id8014465\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Actions that are not related to the document contents are not recorded. For example, changes made in the Options dialog, macro organizer, customizing."
msgstr "ການກະທຳທີ່ບໍ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບເນື້ອໃນເອກະສານແມ່ນບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກບັນທຶກ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ການປ່ຽນແປງໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບຕົວເລືອກ, ຕົວຈັດການມາໂຄຣ, ການປັບແຕ່ງ."

