"help.text"
msgid "Saving Documents by Default in Microsoft Office Formats"
msgstr "ການຕັ້ງຄ່າໃຫ້ບັນທຶກເອກະສານເປັນຮູບແບບ Microsoft Office ໂດຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ"

#. RBiDC
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"par_id3144760\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - </emph><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010200.xhp\"><emph>Load/Save - General</emph></link>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - </emph><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01010200.xhp\"><emph>ໂຫຼດ/ບັນທຶກ - ທົ່ວໄປ</emph></link>."

#. uZx9i
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"par_id3148453\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Default file format and ODF settings</emph> area, first select a document type, then select the file type for saving."
msgstr "ໃນສ່ວນ <emph>ຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ແລະ ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ ODF</emph>, ທຳອິດໃຫ້ເລືອກປະເພດເອກະສານ, ແລ້ວເລືອກປະເພດໄຟລ໌ສຳລັບການບັນທຶກ."

#. 2NnEW
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"par_id3149807\n"
"help.text"
msgid "From now on, if you save a document, the <emph>File type </emph>will be set according to your choice. Of course, you still can select another file type in the file save dialog."
msgstr "ຈາກນີ້ໄປ, ຖ້າເຈົ້າບັນທຶກເອກະສານ, <emph>ປະເພດໄຟລ໌</emph> ຈະຖືກຕັ້ງຕາມທີ່ເຈົ້າເລືອກໄວ້. ແນ່ນອນວ່າ ເຈົ້າຍັງສາມາດເລືອກປະເພດໄຟລ໌ອື່ນໄດ້ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌."

#. tsAPB
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"hd_id3156423\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Opening Microsoft Office Files by Default"
msgstr "ການເປີດໄຟລ໌ Microsoft Office ໂດຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ"

#. 3B3X3
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153092\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Converting Many Microsoft Office Files into OpenDocument Format"
msgstr "ການແປງໄຟລ໌ Microsoft Office ຫຼາຍໆໄຟລ໌ໃຫ້ເປັນຮູບແບບ OpenDocument"

#. RQFV5
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"par_id3146986\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <emph>Document Converter Wizard</emph> will copy and convert all Microsoft Office files in a folder into $[officename] documents in the OpenDocument file format. You can specify the folder to be read, and the folder where the converted files are to be saved."
msgstr "<emph>ຕົວຊ່ວຍແປງເອກະສານ (Document Converter Wizard)</emph> ຈະສຳເນົາ ແລະ ແປງໄຟລ໌ Microsoft Office ທັງໝົດໃນໂຟນເດີໃຫ້ເປັນເອກະສານ $[officename] ໃນຮູບແບບ OpenDocument. ເຈົ້າສາມາດກຳນົດໂຟນເດີຕົ້ນທາງ ແລະ ໂຟນເດີທີ່ຈະບັນທຶກໄຟລ໌ທີ່ແປງແລ້ວໄດ້."

#. goskv
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"par_id3150486\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <link href=\"text/shared/autopi/01130000.xhp\"><emph>File - Wizards - Document Converter</emph></link> to start the wizard."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <link href=\"text/shared/autopi/01130000.xhp\"><emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ຕົວຊ່ວຍ - ຕົວແປງເອກະສານ</emph></link> ເພື່ອເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ."

#. V3ANF
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154319\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Macros in Microsoft Office and $[officename]"
msgstr "ມາໂຄຣໃນ Microsoft Office ແລະ $[officename]"

#. 8egxs
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"par_id3154921\n"
"help.text"
msgid "With a few exceptions, Microsoft Office and $[officename] cannot run the same macro code. Microsoft Office uses VBA (Visual Basic for Applications) code, and $[officename] uses Basic code based on the $[officename] API (Application Program Interface) environment. Although the programming language is the same, the objects and methods are different."
msgstr "ໂດຍມີຂໍ້ຍົກເວັ້ນບາງຢ່າງ, Microsoft Office ແລະ $[officename] ບໍ່ສາມາດລັນໂຄ້ດມາໂຄຣອັນດຽວກັນໄດ້. Microsoft Office ໃຊ້ໂຄ້ດ VBA, ສ່ວນ $[officename] ໃຊ້ໂຄ້ດ Basic ທີ່ອີງໃສ່ API ຂອງ $[officename]. ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າພາສາໂປຣແກຣມຈະຄືກັນ, ແຕ່ວັດຖຸ (objects) ແລະ ວິທີການ (methods) ແມ່ນແຕກຕ່າງກັນ."

#. AqkGQ
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"par_id0804200804173539\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The most recent versions of %PRODUCTNAME can run some Excel Visual Basic scripts if you enable this feature at <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><item type=\"menuitem\">%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</item></caseinline><defaultinline><item type=\"menuitem\">Tools - Options</item></defaultinline></switchinline><item type=\"menuitem\"> - Load/Save - VBA Properties</item>."
msgstr "%PRODUCTNAME ເວີຊັນຫຼ້າສຸດສາມາດລັນບາງ Excel Visual Basic scripts ໄດ້ ຖ້າເຈົ້າເປີດໃຊ້ງານທີ່ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><item type=\"menuitem\">%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</item></caseinline><defaultinline><item type=\"menuitem\">ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</item></defaultinline></switchinline><item type=\"menuitem\"> - ໂຫຼດ/ບັນທຶກ - ຄຸນສົມບັດ VBA</item>."

#. A9WHS
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"par_id3152577\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you use macros in one of the applications and want to use the same functionality in the other application, you must edit the macros. $[officename] can load the macros that are contained within Microsoft Office files and you can then view and edit the macro code in the $[officename] <link href=\"text/shared/main0600.xhp\">Basic IDE</link> editor."
msgstr "ຖ້າເຈົ້າໃຊ້າມໂຄຣໃນແອັບພລິເຄຊັນໜຶ່ງ ແລະ ຕ້ອງການໃຊ້ງານແບບດຽວກັນໃນອີກແອັບພລິເຄຊັນໜຶ່ງ, ເຈົ້າຕ້ອງແກ້ໄຂມາໂຄຣນັ້ນ. $[officename] ສາມາດໂຫຼດມາໂຄຣຈາກໄຟລ໌ Microsoft Office ໄດ້ ແລະ ເຈົ້າສາມາດເບິ່ງ ຫຼື ແກ້ໄຂໂຄ້ດໄດ້ໃນຕົວແກ້ໄຂ <link href=\"text/shared/main0600.xhp\">Basic IDE</link> ຂອງ $[officename]."

#. 8N7fC
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"hd_id3152596\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can choose to preserve or delete VBA macros"
msgstr "ເຈົ້າສາມາດເລືອກທີ່ຈະຮັກສາໄວ້ ຫຼື ລຶບມາໂຄຣ VBA ໄດ້"

#. Gcvg9
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"par_id3153144\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open a Microsoft Office document that contains VBA macro code. Change only the normal contents (text, cells, graphics), and do not edit the macros. Save the document as a Microsoft Office file type. Open the file in Microsoft Office, and the VBA macros will run as before."
msgstr "ເມື່ອເປີດເອກະສານ Microsoft Office ທີ່ມີໂຄ້ດມາໂຄຣ VBA, ຖ້າເຈົ້າແກ້ໄຂສະເພາະເນື້ອໃນທົ່ວໄປ (ຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນ, ກຣາຟິກ) ໂດຍບໍ່ແກ້ໄຂມາໂຄຣ, ແລ້ວບັນທຶກເປັນໄຟລ໌ Microsoft Office ຄືເກົ່າ, ມາໂຄຣ VBA ນັ້ນຈະຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ຕາມປົກກະຕິເມື່ອເປີດໃນ Microsoft Office."

#. JEu5S
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"par_id3150011\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You may delete the VBA macros from the Microsoft Office file on loading or on saving."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າສາມາດເລືອກລຶບມາໂຄຣ VBA ອອກຈາກໄຟລ໌ Microsoft Office ໄດ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ໂຫຼດ ຫຼື ບັນທຶກ."

#. xB9AG
#: ms_user.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ms_user.xhp\n"
"par_id3155366\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - </emph><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01130100.xhp\"><emph>Load/Save - VBA Properties</emph></link> to set the VBA macro handling of $[officename]."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - </emph><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01130100.xhp\"><emph>ໂຫຼດ/ບັນທຶກ - ຄຸນສົມບັດ VBA</emph></link> ເພື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າການຈັດການມາໂຄຣ VBA ຂອງ $[officename]."

#. DhrJv
#: navigator.xhp
msgctxt ""
"navigator.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Navigator for Document Overview"
msgstr "ຕົວນຳທາງສຳລັບພາບຮວມເອກະສານ"

#. hHA7Z
#: navigator.xhp
msgctxt ""
"navigator.xhp\n"
"bm_id3147008\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>documents; contents as lists</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>Navigator; contents as lists</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ເອກະສານ; ເນື້ອໃນໃນຮູບແບບລາຍການ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕົວນຳທາງ; ເນື້ອໃນໃນຮູບແບບລາຍການ</bookmark_value>"

#. CHGXj
#: navigator.xhp
msgctxt ""
"navigator.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147008\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"navigator\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/navigator.xhp\">Navigator for Document Overview</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"navigator\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/navigator.xhp\">ຕົວນຳທາງສຳລັບພາບຮວມເອກະສານ</link></variable>"

#. J58D6
#: navigator.xhp
msgctxt ""
"navigator.xhp\n"
"par_id3154823\n"
"help.text"
msgid "All contents of the Navigator window are referred to here as \"categories,\" whether headings, sheets, tables, frames, graphics, OLE objects, sections, hyperlinks, references, indexes, comments, or drawing objects."
msgstr "ເນື້ອໃນທັງໝົດໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມຕົວນຳທາງຈະຖືກເອີ້ນວ່າ \"ໝວດໝູ່,\" ບໍ່ວ່າຈະເປັນ ຫົວຂໍ້, ແຜ່ນງານ, ຕາຕະລາງ, ເຟຣມ, ກຣາຟິກ, ວັດຖຸ OLE, ສ່ວນຕ່າງໆ, ໄຮເປີລິ້ງ, ການອ້າງອີງ, ດັດຊະນີ, ຄຳເຫັນ ຫຼື ວັດຖຸແຕ້ມ."

#. EseGu
#: navigator.xhp
msgctxt ""
"navigator.xhp\n"
"par_id3153662\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The Navigator displays types of objects contained in a document. If a plus sign appears next to a category, this indicates that at least one object of this kind exists. If you rest the mouse pointer on the category name, the number of objects is displayed in an extended tip."
msgstr "ຕົວນຳທາງຈະສະແດງປະເພດຂອງວັດຖຸທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນເອກະສານ. ຖ້າມີເຄື່ອງໝາຍບວກ (+) ຢູ່ທາງໜ້າໝວດໝູ່, ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າມີວັດຖຸປະເພດນັ້ນຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງຢ່າງ. ຖ້າເຈົ້າເອົາເຄີເຊີໄປວາງໄວ້ເທິງຊື່ໝວດໝູ່, ມັນຈະສະແດງຈຳນວນວັດຖຸທີ່ມີ."

#. AECi8
#: navigator.xhp
msgctxt ""
"navigator.xhp\n"
"par_id3146797\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open a category by clicking on the plus sign. If you only want to view the entries in a certain category, select the category and click the <emph>Content Navigation View</emph> icon. Until you click the icon again, only the objects of this category will be displayed."
msgstr "ເປີດໝວດໝູ່ໂດຍການຄລິກເຄື່ອງໝາຍບວກ. ຖ້າເຈົ້າຕ້ອງການເບິ່ງສະເພາະເນື້ອໃນໃນໝວດໝູ່ໃດໜຶ່ງ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກໝວດໝູ່ນັ້ນແລ້ວຄລິກໄອຄອນ <emph>ມຸມມອງການນຳທາງເນື້ອໃນ</emph>."

#. dcze2
#: navigator.xhp
msgctxt ""
"navigator.xhp\n"
"par_id3166461\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You may dock the Navigator to any document border or turn it back into a free window (double click on the gray area). You can change the size of the Navigator when it is a free window."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າສາມາດນຳຕົວນຳທາງໄປຕິດ (dock) ໄວ້ກັບຂອບຂອງເອກະສານ ຫຼື ປ່ຽນໃຫ້ເປັນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມລອຍຄືເກົ່າໄດ້ (ໂດຍການດັບເບິ້ລຄລິກໃສ່ພື້ນທີ່ສີເທົາ). ເຈົ້າສາມາດປ່ຽນຂະໜາດຂອງຕົວນຳທາງໄດ້ເມື່ອມັນເປັນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມລອຍ."

#. sBSUi
#: navigator_setcursor.xhp
msgctxt ""
"navigator_setcursor.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Navigation to Quickly Reach Objects"
msgstr "ການນຳທາງເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງວັດຖຸຢ່າງວ່ອງໄວ"

#. BDBCc
#: navigator_setcursor.xhp
msgctxt ""
"navigator_setcursor.xhp\n"
"bm_id3150774\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>Document Map, see Navigator</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>cursor;quickly moving to an object</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>objects;quickly moving to</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>navigating;in documents</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>Navigator;working with</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ແຜນຜັງເອກະສານ, ເບິ່ງ ຕົວນຳທາງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ເຄີເຊີ;ການຍ້າຍໄປຫາວັດຖຸຢ່າງໄວ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ວັດຖຸ;ການຍ້າຍໄປຫາຢ່າງໄວ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການນຳທາງ;ໃນເອກະສານ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕົວນຳທາງ;ການເຮັດວຽກກັບ</bookmark_value>"

#. E54vB
#: navigator_setcursor.xhp
msgctxt ""
