"par_idN10743\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Contents that are stored on the clipboard can be pasted into your document using different formats. In %PRODUCTNAME you can choose how to paste the contents using a dialog or a drop-down icon."
msgstr "ເນື້ອໃນໃນຄລິບບອດສາມາດວາງລົງໃນເອກະສານໄດ້ຫຼາຍຮູບແບບ. ໃນ %PRODUCTNAME ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກວິທີການວາງໄດ້ຜ່ານປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ ຫຼື ໄອຄອນເມນູລົງ."

#. YEsGc
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN10746\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The available options depend on the contents of the clipboard."
msgstr "ຕົວເລືອກທີ່ມີແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບເນື້ອໃນທີ່ຢູ່ໃນຄລິບບອດ."

#. UWDBZ
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"hd_id3144547360\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In Writer text documents, you can press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command+Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl+Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+Shift+V to paste the contents of the clipboard as unformatted text."
msgstr "ໃນ Writer, ທ່ານສາມາດກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command+Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl+Alt</defaultinline></switchinline>+Shift+V ເພື່ອວາງຂໍ້ຄວາມແບບບໍ່ມີຮູບແບບ."

#. FqBxZ
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN10748\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If a text cut or copied from Writer is surrounded by spaces it will be considered as a set of words. When pasted, Writer will surround it smartly by spaces to keep it as a set of words: separated by spaces from other characters but avoiding any duplication of spaces. If the text is pasted as Unformatted Text, this consideration is ignored and the text is pasted as is, without adding any spaces."
msgstr "ຖ້າຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຄັດລອກມາມີຊ່ອງຫວ່າງລ້ອມຮອບ, ເມື່ອວາງ Writer ຈະຈັດການຊ່ອງຫວ່າງໃຫ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດເພື່ອບໍ່ໃຫ້ມີຊ່ອງຫວ່າງຊ້ຳກັນ. ແຕ່ຖ້າວາງແບບບໍ່ມີຮູບແບບ (Unformatted Text), ມັນຈະວາງຂໍ້ຄວາມຕາມຕົ້ນສະບັບໂດຍບໍ່ມີການປັບແຕ່ງໃດໆ."

#. BEuwF
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN10749\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Pasting clipboard contents using an icon menu"
msgstr "ການວາງເນື້ອໃນຈາກຄລິບບອດໂດຍໃຊ້ເມນູໄອຄອນ"

#. bAUhX
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN10750\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the arrow next to the <emph>Paste</emph> icon on the Standard Bar to open the menu."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ລູກສອນຂ້າງໄອຄອນ <emph>ວາງ</emph> ໃນແຖບມາດຕະຖານເພື່ອເປີດເມນູ."

#. gmd8d
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN10758\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select one of the options."
msgstr "ເລືອກຕົວເລືອກໃດໜຶ່ງ."

#. MYQDD
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN1075B\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you do not like the result, click the <emph>Undo</emph> icon and then paste again with another option."
msgstr "ຖ້າບໍ່ພໍໃຈກັບຜົນທີ່ໄດ້, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໄອຄອນ <emph>ຍົກເລີກ (Undo)</emph> ແລ້ວລອງວາງໃໝ່ດ້ວຍຕົວເລືອກອື່ນ."

#. nFhpt
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN10762\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Pasting clipboard contents using a dialog"
msgstr "ການວາງເນື້ອໃນຈາກຄລິບບອດໂດຍໃຊ້ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ"

#. tJtqm
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN10769\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Edit - Paste special</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂ - ວາງແບບພິເສດ</emph>."

#. 3QcUF
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN10771\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select one of the options and click <emph>OK</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກຕົວເລືອກໃດໜຶ່ງ ແລ້ວຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>."

#. H8WvY
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN10774\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you are in a spreadsheet and the contents of the clipboard are spreadsheet cells, then a different <emph>Paste Special</emph> dialog appears. Use the <emph>Paste Special</emph> dialog to copy cells using basic or advanced options."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຢູ່ໃນສະເປຣດຊີດ ແລະ ເນື້ອໃນແມ່ນຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນ, ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ວາງແບບພິເສດ</emph> ຈະມີຕົວເລືອກເພີ່ມເຕີມສຳລັບຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. nFapF
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN1077E\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Transpose</emph>: swaps the rows and the columns of the cell range to be pasted."
msgstr "<emph>ສະຫຼັບແຖວ ແລະ ຖັນ (Transpose)</emph>: ສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງແຖວ ແລະ ຖັນຂອງຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈະວາງ."

#. CgQFS
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN10785\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Link</emph>: pastes the cell range as a link. If the source file changes, the pasted cells change also."
msgstr "<emph>ລິ້ງ (Link)</emph>: ວາງຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນໃນຮູບແບບການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ. ຖ້າໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນທາງປ່ຽນແປງ, ຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ວາງໄວ້ກໍຈະປ່ຽນຕາມ."

#. sHuP5
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN1078C\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The other options are explained in the help, when you call the <link href=\"text/shared/01/02070000.xhp\">Paste Special</link> dialog from within %PRODUCTNAME Calc."
msgstr "ຕົວເລືອກອື່ນໆແມ່ນໄດ້ອະທິບາຍໄວ້ໃນສ່ວນຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຂອງ <link href=\"text/shared/01/02070000.xhp\">ວາງແບບພິເສດ</link> ໃນ Calc."

#. mQsXN
#: pasting.xhp
msgctxt ""
"pasting.xhp\n"
"par_idN107BA\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/01/02070000.xhp\">Paste Special</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/01/02070000.xhp\">ວາງແບບພິເສດ</link>"

