msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການປ້ອງກັນ; ເນື້ອຫາ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ເນື້ອຫາທີ່ຖືກປ້ອງກັນ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ການປ້ອງກັນເນື້ອຫາ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ການເຂົ້າລະຫັດເນື້ອຫາ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ລະຫັດຜ່ານສຳລັບປ້ອງກັນເນື້ອຫາ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ຄວາມປອດໄພ;ການປ້ອງກັນເນື້ອຫາ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ປຸ່ມຄວບຄຸມແບບຟອມ; ການປ້ອງກັນ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ວັດຖຸຮູບແຕ້ມ;ການປ້ອງກັນ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ວັດຖຸ OLE;ການປ້ອງກັນ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ຮູບພາບ;ການປ້ອງກັນ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ເຟຣມ;ການປ້ອງກັນ</bookmark_value>"

#. ors5t
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155364\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"protection\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/protection.xhp\">Protecting Contents in <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item></link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"protection\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/protection.xhp\">ການປ້ອງກັນເນື້ອຫາໃນ <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item></link></variable>"

#. srHbB
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3153394\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following is an overview of the different ways of protecting contents in <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> from being modified, deleted or viewed."
msgstr "ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ແມ່ນພາບລວມຂອງວິທີຕ່າງໆໃນການປ້ອງກັນເນື້ອຫາໃນ <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> ຈາກການຖືກແກ້ໄຂ, ລຶບ ຫຼື ການເບິ່ງ."

#. na6k7
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146957\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Protecting Documents With Passwords When Saving"
msgstr "ການປ້ອງກັນເອກະສານດ້ວຍລະຫັດຜ່ານໃນເວລາບັນທຶກ"

#. 4wCBL
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3150775\n"
"help.text"
msgid "All documents that are saved in <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000021.xhp\">OpenDocument format</link> can be saved with a password. Documents that are saved with a password cannot be opened without the password. The content is secured so that it cannot be read with an external editor. This applies to content, graphics and OLE objects."
msgstr "ທຸກເອກະສານທີ່ບັນທຶກໃນ <link href=\"text/shared/00/00000021.xhp\">ຮູບແບບ OpenDocument</link> ສາມາດບັນທຶກດ້ວຍລະຫັດຜ່ານໄດ້. ເອກະສານທີ່ບັນທຶກດ້ວຍລະຫັດຜ່ານຈະບໍ່ສາມາດເປີດໄດ້ຖ້າບໍ່ມີລະຫັດຜ່ານ. ເນື້ອຫາຈະຖືກປ້ອງກັນເພື່ອບໍ່ໃຫ້ສາມາດອ່ານໄດ້ດ້ວຍໂປຣແກຣມແກ້ໄຂພາຍນອກ. ນີ້ລວມເຖິງເນື້ອຫາ, ຮູບພາບ ແລະ ວັດຖຸ OLE."

#. i9B3Z
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3166410\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Turning on protection"
msgstr "ການເປີດໃຊ້ການປ້ອງກັນ"

#. QGCEL
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3145121\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>File - Save As</emph> and mark the <emph>Save with password</emph> check box. Save the document."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ບັນທຶກເປັນ</emph> ແລະ ໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງ <emph>ບັນທຶກດ້ວຍລະຫັດຜ່ານ</emph>. ຈາກນັ້ນບັນທຶກເອກະສານ."

#. 8YAs7
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3154286\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Turning off protection"
msgstr "ການປິດໃຊ້ການປ້ອງກັນ"

#. vEQSp
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3148492\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open the document, entering the correct password. Choose <emph>File - Save As</emph> and clear the <emph>Save with password</emph> check box."
msgstr "ເປີດເອກະສານ, ປ້ອນລະຫັດຜ່ານທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ເລືອກ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ບັນທຶກເປັນ</emph> ແລະ ຍົກເລີກການໝາຍຫ້ອງ <emph>ບັນທຶກດ້ວຍລະຫັດຜ່ານ</emph>."

#. MwB7s
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id761632164002322\n"
"help.text"
msgid "It is possible to use OpenPGP to define private and public keys to be used to encrypt %PRODUCTNAME documents. Read <link href=\"text/shared/guide/openpgp.xhp\">Encrypting Documents with OpenPGP</link> to learn more on how to set up OpenPGP encryption keys."
msgstr "ເປັນໄປໄດ້ທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ OpenPGP ເພື່ອກຳນົດຄີສ່ວນຕົວ ແລະ ຄີສາທາລະນະສຳລັບໃຊ້ເຂົ້າລະຫັດເອກະສານ %PRODUCTNAME. ອ່ານ <link href=\"text/shared/guide/openpgp.xhp\">ການເຂົ້າລະຫັດເອກະສານດ້ວຍ OpenPGP</link> ເພື່ອຮຽນຮູ້ເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບວິທີຕັ້ງຄ່າຄີການເຂົ້າລະຫັດ OpenPGP."

#. HfUCF
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149294\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Protecting Revision Marking"
msgstr "ການປ້ອງກັນການໝາຍການແກ້ໄຂ"

#. pH6Gw
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3161646\n"
"help.text"
msgid "With every change made in <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Calc and <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Writer, the review function records who made the change. This function can be turned on with protection, so that it can only be turned off when the correct password is entered. Until then, all changes will continue to be recorded. Acceptance or rejection of changes is not possible."
msgstr "ໃນທຸກໆການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ເກີດຂຶ້ນໃນ <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Calc ແລະ <item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> Writer, ຟີເຈີການກວດສອບຈະບັນທຶກວ່າໃຜເປັນຜູ້ປ່ຽນແປງ. ຟີເຈີນີ້ສາມາດເປີດໃຊ້ພ້ອມກັບການປ້ອງກັນໄດ້ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ມັນຖືກປິດໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອປ້ອນລະຫັດຜ່ານທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ຈົນກວ່າຈະເຖິງເວລານັ້ນ, ທຸກໆການປ່ຽນແປງຈະຖືກບັນທຶກໄວ້ຕໍ່ເນື່ອງ ແລະ ຈະບໍ່ສາມາດຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ປະຕິເສດການປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້."

#. hj3oS
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3154684\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Turning on protection"
msgstr "ການເປີດໃຊ້ການປ້ອງກັນ"

#. L4fae
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3153104\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Edit - Track Changes - Protect</emph>. Enter and confirm a password of at least one character."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂ - ຕິດຕາມການປ່ຽນແປງ - ປ້ອງກັນ</emph>. ປ້ອນ ແລະ ຢືນຢັນລະຫັດຜ່ານຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງຕົວອັກສອນ."

#. 388a9
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3144760\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Turning off protection"
msgstr "ການປິດໃຊ້ການປ້ອງກັນ"

#. ZguB2
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3152920\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Edit - Track Changes - Protect</emph>. Enter the correct password."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂ - ຕິດຕາມການປ່ຽນແປງ - ປ້ອງກັນ</emph>. ປ້ອນລະຫັດຜ່ານທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. TktAz
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155113\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Protecting Frames, Graphics, and OLE Objects"
msgstr "ການປ້ອງກັນເເຟຣມ, ຮູບພາບ ແລະ ວັດຖຸ OLE"

#. DACWQ
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3153703\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can protect the content, position and size of inserted graphics. The same applies to frames (in Writer) and OLE objects."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອງກັນເນື້ອຫາ, ຕຳແໜ່ງ ແລະ ຂະໜາດຂອງຮູບພາບທີ່ແຊກໄວ້ໄດ້. ເຊັ່ນດຽວກັນກັບເຟຣມ (ໃນ Writer) ແລະ ວັດຖຸ OLE."

#. rjbc2
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3147131\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Turning on protection"
msgstr "ການເປີດໃຊ້ການປ້ອງກັນ"

#. CGNdW
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3150088\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For example, for graphics inserted in Writer: Choose <emph>Format - Image - Properties - Position and Size</emph> tab. Under <emph>Protect</emph>, mark <emph>Contents</emph>, <emph>Position</emph> and/or <emph>Size</emph>."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ, ສຳລັບຮູບພາບທີ່ແຊກໃນ Writer: ເລືອກແທັບ <emph>ຮູບແບບ - ຮູບພາບ - ຄຸນສົມບັດ - ຕຳແໜ່ງ ແລະ ຂະໜາດ</emph>. ພາຍໃຕ້ <emph>ປ້ອງກັນ</emph>, ໃຫ້ໝາຍເອົາ <emph>ເນື້ອຫາ</emph>, <emph>ຕຳແໜ່ງ</emph> ແລະ/ຫຼື <emph>ຂະໜາດ</emph>."

#. 2qB2F
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3147510\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Turning off protection"
msgstr "ການປິດໃຊ້ການປ້ອງກັນ"

#. LPebA
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3153657\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For example, for graphics inserted in Writer: Choose <emph>Format - Image - Properties - Position and Size</emph> tab. Under <emph>Protect</emph>, unmark as appropriate."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ, ສຳລັບຮູບພາບທີ່ແຊກໃນ Writer: ເລືອກແທັບ <emph>ຮູບແບບ - ຮູບພາບ - ຄຸນສົມບັດ - ຕຳແໜ່ງ ແລະ ຂະໜາດ</emph>. ພາຍໃຕ້ <emph>ປ້ອງກັນ</emph>, ໃຫ້ຍົກເລີກການໝາຍຕາມຄວາມເໝາະສົມ."

#. o2ioR
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"hd_id3152992\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Protecting Drawing Objects and Form Objects"
msgstr "ການປ້ອງກັນວັດຖຸຮູບແຕ້ມ ແລະ ວັດຖຸແບບຟອມ"

#. E6X38
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3166429\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The draw objects that you insert into your documents with the <emph>Drawing </emph>toolbar can be protected from being accidentally moved or changed in size. You can do the same with form objects inserted with the <emph>Form Controls</emph> toolbar."
msgstr "ວັດຖຸຮູບແຕ້ມທີ່ທ່ານແຊກລົງໃນເອກະສານດ້ວຍແຖບເຄື່ອງມື <emph>ຮູບແຕ້ມ</emph> ສາມາດປ້ອງກັນບໍ່ໃຫ້ມີການເຄື່ອນຍ້າຍ ຫຼື ປ່ຽນຂະໜາດໂດຍບັງເອີນໄດ້. ທ່ານສາມາດເຮັດແບບດຽວກັນກັບວັດຖຸແບບຟອມທີ່ແຊກດ້ວຍແຖບເຄື່ອງມື <emph>ການຄວບຄຸມແບບຟອມ</emph> ໄດ້."

#. 2CqEx
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3153226\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Turning on protection"
msgstr "ການເປີດໃຊ້ການປ້ອງກັນ"

#. EASQQ
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3148815\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Format - Object - Position and Size </emph>- <emph>Position and Size</emph> tab. Mark the <emph>Position</emph> or <emph>Size</emph> check box."
msgstr "ເລືອກແທັບ <emph>ຮູບແບບ - ວັດຖຸ - ຕຳແໜ່ງ ແລະ ຂະໜາດ </emph>- <emph>ຕຳແໜ່ງ ແລະ ຂະໜາດ</emph>. ໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງ <emph>ຕຳແໜ່ງ</emph> ຫຼື <emph>ຂະໜາດ</emph>."

#. uQeNg
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3156289\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Turning off protection"
msgstr "ການປິດໃຊ້ການປ້ອງກັນ"

#. jQEDR
#: protection.xhp
msgctxt ""
"protection.xhp\n"
"par_id3154991\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Format - Object - Position and Size </emph>- <emph>Position and Size</emph> tab. Unmark the <emph>Position</emph> or <emph>Size</emph> check box."
msgstr "ເລືອກແທັບ <emph>ຮູບແບບ - ວັດຖຸ - ຕຳແໜ່ງ ແລະ ຂະໜາດ </emph>- <emph>ຕຳແໜ່ງ ແລະ ຂະໜາດ</emph>. ຍົກເລີກການໝາຍຫ້ອງ <emph>ຕຳແໜ່ງ</emph> ຫຼື <emph>ຂະໜາດ</emph>."

#. FuBFK
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Redaction"
msgstr "ການປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນ (Redaction)"

#. Fb9ty
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"bm_id821562797360035\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>spreadsheet; redacting contents</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>presentations; redacting contents</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>text documents; redacting contents</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>redaction</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ສະເປຣດຊີດ; ການປົກປິດເນື້ອຫາ</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>ການນຳສະເໜີ; ການປົກປິດເນື້ອຫາ</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>ເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ; ການປົກປິດເນື້ອຫາ</bookmark_value>        <bookmark_value>ການປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນ</bookmark_value>"

#. iLC7P
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"hd_id171562795247717\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"redaction_h1\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/redaction.xhp\">Redaction</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"redaction_h1\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/redaction.xhp\">ການປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນ (Redaction)</link></variable>"

#. 4DfDB
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id471562795247717\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"redaction_desc\"><ahelp hid=\".\">Redacting documents blocks out words or portions of a document for authorized use or viewing.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"redaction_desc\"><ahelp hid=\".\">ການປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນໃນເອກະສານແມ່ນການປິດບັງຄຳສັບ ຫຼື ບາງສ່ວນຂອງເອກະສານ ເພື່ອການນຳໃຊ້ ຫຼື ການເບິ່ງທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບອະນຸຍາດເທົ່ານັ້ນ.</ahelp></variable>"

#. sB25i
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id291647277725275\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Redaction protects sensitive information and helps enterprises and organizations to comply with regulations on confidentiality or privacy."
msgstr "ການປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນຊ່ວຍປ້ອງກັນຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ລະອຽດອ່ອນ ແລະ ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທຸລະກິດ ແລະ ອົງກອນສາມາດປະຕິບັດຕາມກົດລະບຽບກ່ຽວກັບຄວາມລັບ ຫຼື ຄວາມເປັນສ່ວນຕົວ."

#. QdoMp
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id961562795751821\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <menuitem>Tools - Redact</menuitem>"
msgstr "ເລືອກ <menuitem>ເຄື່ອງມື - ປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນ</menuitem>"

#. JBRpx
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"hd_id281562795791927\n"
"help.text"
msgid "How redaction works in %PRODUCTNAME?"
msgstr "ການປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນເຮັດວຽກແນວໃດໃນ %PRODUCTNAME?"

#. PEEvZ
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id791562795799809\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The current document is exported to a drawing document edited in %PRODUCTNAME Draw. The redacted text or contents is removed from the drawing document and replaced by the redaction block of pixels, preventing any attempt to restore or copy the original contents. The redacted drawing document is often exported to PDF for publication or sharing."
msgstr "ເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນຈະຖືກສົ່ງອອກໄປເປັນເອກະສານຮູບແຕ້ມທີ່ແກ້ໄຂໃນ %PRODUCTNAME Draw. ຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ເນື້ອຫາທີ່ຖືກປົກປິດຈະຖືກຍ້າຍອອກຈາກເອກະສານຮູບແຕ້ມ ແລະ ແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍບລັອກພິກເຊວການປົກປິດ ເພື່ອປ້ອງກັນການພະຍາຍາມກູ້ຄືນ ຫຼື ຄັດລອກເນື້ອຫາຕົ້ນສະບັບ. ເອກະສານຮູບແຕ້ມທີ່ປົກປິດແລ້ວມັກຈະຖືກສົ່ງອອກເປັນ PDF ເພື່ອການເຜີຍແຜ່ ຫຼື ການແບ່ງປັນ."

#. 7a2gY
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id671562795811658\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When redacting, the redaction shapes are transparent and in gray so the user can see what is being redacted."
msgstr "ໃນຂະນະທີ່ປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນ, ຮູບຊົງການປົກປິດຈະມີຄວາມໂປ່ງໃສ ແລະ ເປັນສີເທົາ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດເຫັນໄດ້ວ່າສ່ວນໃດທີ່ກຳລັງຖືກປົກປິດ."

#. HNkTB
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id81562795822462\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The source document (text, spreadsheet or presentation) is not affected by redaction and can continue to be edited."
msgstr "ເອກະສານຕົ້ນທາງ (ຂໍ້ຄວາມ, ສະເປຣດຊີດ ຫຼື ການນຳສະເໜີ) ຈະບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບຜົນກະທົບຈາກການປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂຕໍ່ໄປໄດ້."

#. LDDyY
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id411562795827608\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Save and share the in-redaction copies of the document with peers either in the modifiable (drawing) or the verbatim (PDF) format at your option."
msgstr "ບັນທຶກ ແລະ ແບ່ງປັນສຳເນົາເອກະສານທີ່ກຳລັງປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນກັບເພື່ອນຮ່ວມງານ ບໍ່ວ່າຈະຢູ່ໃນຮູບແບບທີ່ແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ (ຮູບແຕ້ມ) ຫຼື ຮູບແບບທີ່ຄົງເດີມ (PDF) ຕາມທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ."

#. 4C7qW
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"hd_id221562796409113\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The redaction toolbar"
msgstr "ແຖບເຄື່ອງມືປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. ti4GD
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id441562796415026\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The redaction toolbar consist of four tools"
msgstr "ແຖບເຄື່ອງມືປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນປະກອບດ້ວຍສີ່ເຄື່ອງມື"

#. fUsGb
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id691562796423552\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"cmd/sc_rect.svg\" id=\"img_id41562796484514\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id151562796484514\">Rectangle Redaction tool icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"cmd/sc_rect.svg\" id=\"img_id41562796484514\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id151562796484514\">ໄອຄອນເຄື່ອງມືປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນແບບສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມ</alt></image>"

#. UYBBQ
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id731562796423552\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <emph>Rectangle Redaction</emph> tool is used to mark the content for redaction by drawing transparent rectangles covering the content. Use the handles to resize the redaction rectangle."
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມື <emph>ການປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນແບບສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມ</emph> ໃຊ້ເພື່ອໝາຍເນື້ອຫາທີ່ຈະປົກປິດ ໂດຍການແຕ້ມຮູບສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມໂປ່ງໃສທັບເນື້ອຫາ. ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມຈັບເພື່ອປ່ຽນຂະໜາດຂອງຮູບສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມການປົກປິດ."

#. jEFws
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id401562796560552\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"cmd/sc_freeline_unfilled.svg\" id=\"img_id4156296484514\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id15152796484514\">Freeform Redaction tool icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"cmd/sc_freeline_unfilled.svg\" id=\"img_id4156296484514\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id15152796484514\">ໄອຄອນເຄື່ອງມືປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນແບບອິດສະຫຼະ</alt></image>"

#. mx6Ta
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id641562796560552\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <emph>Freeform Redaction</emph> tool allows the user to mark the content for redaction by drawing free-form lines or polygons covering the content."
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມື <emph>ການປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນແບບອິດສະຫຼະ</emph> ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດໝາຍເນື້ອຫາທີ່ຈະປົກປິດ ໂດຍການແຕ້ມເສັ້ນແບບອິດສະຫຼະ ຫຼື ຮູບຫຼາຍຫຼ່ຽມທັບເນື້ອຫາ."

#. fAQEW
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id961562796701222\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"cmd/sc_redactedexportwhite.svg\" id=\"img_id4156296484514\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id15152796484514\">White Redacted Export tool icon</alt></image>                    <image src=\"cmd/sc_redactedexportblack.svg\" id=\"img_id4156296484514\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id15152796484514\">Black Redacted Export tool icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"cmd/sc_redactedexportwhite.svg\" id=\"img_id4156296484514\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id15152796484514\">ໄອຄອນເຄື່ອງມືສົ່ງອອກການປົກປິດສີຂາວ</alt></image>                    <image src=\"cmd/sc_redactedexportblack.svg\" id=\"img_id4156296484514\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id15152796484514\">ໄອຄອນເຄື່ອງມືສົ່ງອອກການປົກປິດສີດຳ</alt></image>"

#. EUfoB
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id231562796701222\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <emph>Redacted Export</emph> button box has two options:"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມ <emph>ການສົ່ງອອກການປົກປິດ</emph> ມີສອງຕົວເລືອກ:"

#. iFMK3
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id551562796791417\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Redacted Export (Black)</emph>: finalize your document by converting the semitransparent redaction shapes to opaque black and export as pixels in the PDF file."
msgstr "<emph>ສົ່ງອອກການປົກປິດ (ສີດຳ)</emph>: ເຮັດໃຫ້ເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານສຳເລັດ ໂດຍການປ່ຽນຮູບຊົງການປົກປິດທີ່ໂປ່ງໃສໃຫ້ເປັນສີດຳທຶບ ແລະ ສົ່ງອອກເປັນພິກເຊວໃນໄຟລ໌ PDF."

#. HSvWX
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id191562796822685\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Redacted Export (White)</emph>: finalize your document by converting the semitransparent redaction shapes to opaque white shapes, and export as pixels in the PDF file."
msgstr "<emph>ສົ່ງອອກການປົກປິດ (ສີຂາວ)</emph>: ເຮັດໃຫ້ເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານສຳເລັດ ໂດຍການປ່ຽນຮູບຊົງການປົກປິດທີ່ໂປ່ງໃສໃຫ້ເປັນສີຂາວທຶບ ແລະ ສົ່ງອອກເປັນພິກເຊວໃນໄຟລ໌ PDF."

#. 2w5mE
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id961562796947231\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"cmd/sc_exportdirecttopdf.svg\" id=\"img_id4156296484514\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id15152796484514\">Direct Export to PDF icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"cmd/sc_exportdirecttopdf.svg\" id=\"img_id4156296484514\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id15152796484514\">ໄອຄອນການສົ່ງອອກເປັນ PDF ໂດຍກົງ</alt></image>"

#. wqjEG
#: redaction.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redaction.xhp\n"
"par_id901562796947232\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Direct Export to PDF</emph>: Makes an in-redaction copy of the document in PDF to share as a verbatim copy for review"
msgstr "<emph>ສົ່ງອອກເປັນ PDF ໂດຍກົງ</emph>: ສ້າງສຳເນົາເອກະສານທີ່ກຳລັງປົກປິດຂໍ້ມູນໃນຮູບແບບ PDF ເພື່ອແບ່ງປັນເປັນສຳເນົາຄົງເດີມສຳລັບການກວດສອບ"

#. CigEo
#: redlining.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Recording and Displaying Changes"
msgstr "ການບັນທຶກ ແລະ ການສະແດງການປ່ຽນແປງ"

#. LEFZi
#: redlining.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining.xhp\n"
"bm_id3150499\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>marking changes</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>highlighting changes</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>changes; review function</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>review function; recording changes example</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>Track Changes, see review function</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການໝາຍການປ່ຽນແປງ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ການເນັ້ນການປ່ຽນແປງ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ການປ່ຽນແປງ; ຟີເຈີການກວດສອບ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຟີເຈີການກວດສອບ; ຕົວຢ່າງການບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຕິດຕາມການປ່ຽນແປງ, ເບິ່ງຟີເຈີການກວດສອບ</bookmark_value>"

#. UWUn8
#: redlining.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150499\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"redlining\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/redlining.xhp\">Recording and Displaying Changes</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"redlining\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/redlining.xhp\">ການບັນທຶກ ແລະ ການສະແດງການປ່ຽນແປງ</link></variable>"

#. zuywD
#: redlining.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining.xhp\n"
"par_id4013794\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The review function is available in %PRODUCTNAME for text documents and spreadsheet documents."
msgstr "ຟີເຈີການກວດສອບມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ໃນ %PRODUCTNAME ສຳລັບເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ ແລະ ເອກະສານສະເປຣດຊີດ."

#. jWfVn
#: redlining.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining.xhp\n"
"par_id3153681\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When several authors are working on the same text or spreadsheet, the review function records and displays who made the various changes. On the final edit of the document, it is then possible to look at each individual change and decide whether it should be accepted or rejected."
msgstr "ເມື່ອມີຜູ້ຂຽນຫຼາຍຄົນເຮັດວຽກໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ສະເປຣດຊີດດຽວກັນ, ຟີເຈີການກວດສອບຈະບັນທຶກ ແລະ ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນວ່າໃຜເປັນຜູ້ປ່ຽນແປງຫຍັງແດ່. ໃນການແກ້ໄຂຂັ້ນສຸດທ້າຍຂອງເອກະສານ, ທ່ານສາມາດເບິ່ງແຕ່ລະການປ່ຽນແປງ ແລະ ຕັດສິນໃຈວ່າຈະຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ປະຕິເສດ."

#. Q9PAH
#: redlining.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining.xhp\n"
"par_id3147008\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For example: You are an editor and are delivering your latest report. But before publication the report must be read by the senior editor and the proofreader, and both will add their changes. The senior editor writes \"clarify\" after one paragraph and crosses out another entirely. The proofreader corrects the spelling of your document."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ: ທ່ານເປັນບັນນາທິການ ແລະ ກຳລັງສົ່ງລາຍງານຫຼ້າສຸດຂອງທ່ານ. ແຕ່ກ່ອນຈະເຜີຍແຜ່, ລາຍງານຕ້ອງຖືກອ່ານໂດຍບັນນາທິການອາວຸໂສ ແລະ ຜູ້ກວດແກ້ຄຳຜິດ, ເຊິ່ງທັງສອງຈະເພີ່ມການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງພວກເຂົາ. ບັນນາທິການອາວຸໂສອາດຈະຂຽນຄຳວ່າ \"ເຮັດໃຫ້ແຈ້ງຂຶ້ນ\" ຫຼັງຈາກວັກໃດໜຶ່ງ ແລະ ຂີດຂ້າອີກວັກໜຶ່ງອອກທັງໝົດ. ສ່ວນຜູ້ກວດແກ້ຄຳຜິດຈະແກ້ໄຂການສະກົດຄຳໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ."

#. sZdoa
#: redlining.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining.xhp\n"
"par_id3150774\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The edited document comes back to you, and you can incorporate or ignore the suggestions of the two reviewers."
msgstr "ເອກະສານທີ່ຖືກແກ້ໄຂແລ້ວຈະຖືກສົ່ງກັບຄືນມາຫາທ່ານ, ແລະ ທ່ານສາມາດລວມເອົາ ຫຼື ບໍ່ສົນໃຈຄຳແນະນຳຂອງຜູ້ກວດສອບທັງສອງໄດ້."

#. QC87c
#: redlining.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining.xhp\n"
"par_id3146957\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Let's say you also emailed a copy of the report to a good friend and colleague who has done research on a similar topic in the past. You asked for a few suggestions, and the document is now returned by email with your colleague's suggestions."
msgstr "ສົມມຸດວ່າທ່ານຍັງໄດ້ສົ່ງສຳເນົາລາຍງານທາງອີເມລ໌ຫາໝູ່ສະໜິດ ແລະ ເພື່ອນຮ່ວມງານທີ່ເຄີຍເຮັດການຄົ້ນຄວ້າໃນຫົວຂໍ້ທີ່ຄ້າຍຄືກັນ. ທ່ານໄດ້ຂໍຄຳແນະນຳບາງຢ່າງ, ແລະ ຕອນນີ້ເອກະສານຖືກສົ່ງກັບຄືນມາທາງອີເມລ໌ພ້ອມກັບຄຳແນະນຳຂອງເພື່ອນຮ່ວມງານຂອງທ່ານ."

#. CoW6n
#: redlining.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining.xhp\n"
"par_id3147088\n"
"help.text"
msgid "As all your colleagues and the managers in your company work with $[officename], you can produce a final version of the document from the results you get back."
msgstr "ເນື່ອງຈາກເພື່ອນຮ່ວມງານ ແລະ ຜູ້ຈັດການທັງໝົດໃນບໍລິສັດຂອງທ່ານເຮັດວຽກດ້ວຍ $[officename], ທ່ານຈຶ່ງສາມາດສ້າງເອກະສານເວີຊັນສຸດທ້າຍຈາກຜົນທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບກັບຄືນມາໄດ້."

#. u5Umr
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Accepting or Rejecting Changes"
msgstr "ການຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ການປະຕິເສດການປ່ຽນແປງ"

#. yyZeG
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"bm_id3150247\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>changes; accepting or rejecting</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>review function;accepting or rejecting changes</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການປ່ຽນແປງ; ການຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ການປະຕິເສດ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ຟີເຈີການກວດສອບ;ການຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ການປະຕິເສດການປ່ຽນແປງ</bookmark_value>"

#. wNAkX
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150247\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"redlining_accept\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/redlining_accept.xhp\">Accepting or Rejecting Changes</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"redlining_accept\"><link href=\"text/shared/guide/redlining_accept.xhp\">ການຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ການປະຕິເສດການປ່ຽນແປງ</link></variable>"

#. E3Aos
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"par_id1491134\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The review function is available in %PRODUCTNAME for text documents and spreadsheet documents."
msgstr "ຟີເຈີການກວດສອບມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ໃນ %PRODUCTNAME ສຳລັບເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ ແລະ ເອກະສານສະເປຣດຊີດ."

#. G5EFY
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"par_id1110200810120034\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In Writer text documents you can also accept or reject changes by choosing commands from the context menu."
msgstr "ໃນເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ Writer ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ປະຕິເສດການປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້ ໂດຍການເລືອກຄຳສັ່ງຈາກເມນູຄລິກຂວາ."

#. aFGSw
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"par_id3147571\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you edit a document in which others have made changes, you can accept or reject the changes individually or all together."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານແກ້ໄຂເອກະສານທີ່ຄົນອື່ນໄດ້ປ່ຽນແປງໄວ້, ທ່ານສາມາດຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ປະຕິເສດການປ່ຽນແປງເປັນແຕ່ລະອັນ ຫຼື ທັງໝົດພ້ອມກັນໄດ້."

#. nzi2M
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"par_id3147008\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you have put multiple copies of the document in circulation, first merge these into one document (see <link href=\"text/shared/guide/redlining_docmerge.xhp\">Merging Versions</link>)."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານໄດ້ສົ່ງສຳເນົາເອກະສານອອກໄປຫຼາຍສະບັບ, ໃຫ້ຮວມສຳເນົາເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນເຂົ້າເປັນເອກະສານດຽວກ່ອນ (ເບິ່ງ <link href=\"text/shared/guide/redlining_docmerge.xhp\">ການຮວມເວີຊັນ</link>)."

#. Rk8jv
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"par_id3153748\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open the document and choose <emph>Edit - Track Changes - Manage</emph>. The <emph>Manage Changes</emph> dialog appears."
msgstr "ເປີດເອກະສານ ແລະ ເລືອກ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂ - ຕິດຕາມການປ່ຽນແປງ - ຈັດການ</emph>. ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ຈັດການການປ່ຽນແປງ</emph> ຈະປາກົດຂຶ້ນ."

#. 3Qapx
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"par_id3156346\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select a change on the <emph>List</emph> tab. The change is selected and displayed in the document and you can now enter your decision with one of the buttons."
msgstr "ເລືອກການປ່ຽນແປງໃນແທັບ <emph>ລາຍການ</emph>. ການປ່ຽນແປງຈະຖືກເລືອກ ແລະ ສະແດງໃນເອກະສານ ແລະ ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດຕັດສິນໃຈໂດຍການຄລິກປຸ່ມໃດໜຶ່ງໄດ້."

#. xCy6A
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"par_id3147209\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If one author has modified another author's change, you will see the changes hierarchically arranged with a plus sign for opening up the hierarchy."
msgstr "ຖ້າຜູ້ຂຽນຄົນໜຶ່ງໄດ້ແກ້ໄຂການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງຜູ້ຂຽນອີກຄົນ, ທ່ານຈະເຫັນການປ່ຽນແປງຖືກຈັດລຽງຕາມລຳດັບຊັ້ນ ໂດຍມີເຄື່ອງໝາຍບວກເພື່ອເປີດເບິ່ງລຳດັບຊັ້ນ."

#. bynhF
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"par_id3148474\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the list of changes is too long, you can switch to the <emph>Filter</emph> tab in the dialog and specify that you only want to see the changes of certain authors, or only the changes of the last day, or that you want the list to be restricted in some other way."
msgstr "ຖ້າລາຍການການປ່ຽນແປງຍາວເກີນໄປ, ທ່ານສາມາດສະຫຼັບໄປທີ່ແທັບ <emph>ຕົວຕອງ</emph> ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ ແລະ ລະບຸວ່າທ່ານຕ້ອງການເຫັນສະເພາະການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງຜູ້ຂຽນບາງຄົນ, ຫຼື ສະເພາະການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງມື້ທີ່ຜ່ານມາ, ຫຼື ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຈຳກັດລາຍການໃນຮູບແບບອື່ນໆ."

#. oj94V
#: redlining_accept.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_accept.xhp\n"
"par_id3143271\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Color-coded entries display the result of the filter that is set. Entries in black can be accepted or rejected and match the filter criteria. Entries in blue do not themselves match the filter criteria, but have subentries that are included by the filter. Gray entries cannot be accepted or rejected and do not match the filter criterion. Green entries do match the filter but cannot be accepted or rejected."
msgstr "ລາຍການທີ່ແຍກຕາມສີຈະສະແດງຜົນຂອງຕົວຕອງທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້. ລາຍການສີດຳສາມາດຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ປະຕິເສດໄດ້ ແລະ ກົງກັບເງື່ອນໄຂຕົວຕອງ. ລາຍການສີຟ້າແມ່ນໂຕມັນເອງບໍ່ກົງກັບເງື່ອນໄຂຕົວຕອງ ແຕ່ມີລາຍການຍ່ອຍທີ່ກົງກັບຕົວຕອງ. ລາຍການສີເທົາບໍ່ສາມາດຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ປະຕິເສດໄດ້ ແລະ ບໍ່ກົງກັບເງື່ອນໄຂຕົວຕອງ. ລາຍການສີຂຽວກົງກັບຕົວຕອງແຕ່ບໍ່ສາມາດຍອມຮັບ ຫຼື ປະຕິເສດໄດ້."

#. BsZbA
#: redlining_doccompare.xhp
msgctxt ""
"redlining_doccompare.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Comparing Versions of a Document"
msgstr "ການປຽບທຽບເວີຊັນຂອງເອກະສານ"

#. 4Hv7i
