msgctxt ""
"start_parameters.xhp\n"
"par_id3153360\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Replace <emph>{install}</emph> with the path to your installation of %PRODUCTNAME software (for example, <emph>C:\\Program Files\\%PRODUCTNAME</emph>). Use <emph>soffice.exe</emph> instead of <emph>soffice.com</emph>, when you do not need console (e.g., you do not use command-line interface for headless operations)."
msgstr "ປ່ຽນ <emph>{install}</emph> ເປັນເສັ້ນທາງທີ່ເຈົ້າຕິດຕັ້ງຊອບແວ %PRODUCTNAME (ຕົວຢ່າງ: <emph>C:\\Program Files\\%PRODUCTNAME</emph>). ໃຊ້ <emph>soffice.exe</emph> ແທນ <emph>soffice.com</emph> ເມື່ອເຈົ້າບໍ່ຕ້ອງການໃຊ້ console (ເຊັ່ນ: ເມື່ອເຈົ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ໃຊ້ command-line interface ສຳລັບການເຮັດວຽກແບບ headless)."

