msgctxt ""
"start_parameters.xhp\n"
"par_id3150828\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the file name contains spaces, then it must be enclosed in quotation marks."
msgstr "ຖ້າຊື່ໄຟລ໌ມີຍະວ່າງ, ຕ້ອງໃສ່ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳເວົ້າຂອບຊື່ໄຟລ໌ນັ້ນໄວ້."

