msgstr "ລາຍການ <link href=\"text/shared/guide/pdf_params.xhp\">ຕົວເລືອກຕົວກັ່ນຕອງສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ PDF</link>."

#. EiUnD
#: start_parameters.xhp
msgctxt ""
"start_parameters.xhp\n"
"par_id315053q\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Batch print files to file. If <emph>--outdir</emph> is not specified, then current working directory is used as output_dir."
msgstr "ສັ່ງພິມໄຟລ໌ແບບກຸ່ມ (Batch print) ລົງໃນໄຟລ໌. ຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸ <emph>--outdir</emph>, ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີເຮັດວຽກປັດຈຸບັນຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນ output_dir."

#. rDfJb
#: start_parameters.xhp
msgctxt ""
