#. myVDG
#: tabs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tabs.xhp\n"
"par_id3154150\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Double-click the ruler to open the <link href=\"text/shared/01/05030300.xhp\"><emph>Paragraph</emph></link> dialog."
msgstr "ຄລິກສອງບາດໃສ່ໄມ້ບັນທັດເພື່ອເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <link href=\"text/shared/01/05030300.xhp\"><emph>ຫຍໍ້ໜ້າ</emph></link>."

#. NKHUs
#: tabs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tabs.xhp\n"
"par_id3154145\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Double-click the white area of the ruler to set one tab. The <emph>Paragraph</emph> dialog appears with the <emph>Tabs</emph> tab page open."
msgstr "ຄລິກສອງບາດໃສ່ພື້ນທີ່ສີຂາວຂອງໄມ້ບັນທັດເພື່ອຕັ້ງແທັບໜຶ່ງອັນ. ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ຫຍໍ້ໜ້າ</emph> ຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນພ້ອມກັບເປີດແທັບໜ້າ <emph>ແທັບ</emph> ໃຫ້."

#. oCQAh
#: tabs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tabs.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145748\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Moving Tabs on the Ruler"
msgstr "ການຍ້າຍແທັບເທິງໄມ້ບັນທັດ"

#. 5GeAW
#: tabs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tabs.xhp\n"
"par_id3145264\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Move individual tab stops on the ruler using the mouse."
msgstr "ຍ້າຍຈຸດຢຸດແທັບແຕ່ລະອັນເທິງໄມ້ບັນທັດໂດຍໃຊ້ເມົາສ໌."

#. dFZJk
#: tabs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tabs.xhp\n"
"par_id3159156\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To move several tab stops on the ruler, press the Shift key before you click a tab. Drag one tab while continuing to press Shift to move that tab as well as all the tabs to the right of it. The spacing between those tabs remains the same."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຍ້າຍຈຸດຢຸດແທັບຫຼາຍອັນເທິງໄມ້ບັນທັດ, ໃຫ້ກົດປຸ່ມ Shift ຄ້າງໄວ້ກ່ອນຈະຄລິກໃສ່ແທັບ. ລາກແທັບໜຶ່ງອັນໃນຂະນະທີ່ຍັງກົດ Shift ຄ້າງໄວ້ ເພື່ອຍ້າຍແທັບນັ້ນລວມເຖິງແທັບທັງໝົດທີ່ຢູ່ເບື້ອງຂວາຂອງມັນ. ໄລຍະຫ່າງລະຫວ່າງແທັບເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນຈະຍັງຄືເກົ່າ."

#. qx9CM
#: tabs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tabs.xhp\n"
"par_id3147349\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline> when you drag a tab on the ruler to move that tab and all the tabs to the right of it. This results in the spacing between those tabs changing proportionally to their distance from the margin."
msgstr "ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Command</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl</defaultinline></switchinline> ໃນເວລາທີ່ເຈົ້າລາກແທັບເທິງໄມ້ບັນທັດ ເພື່ອຍ້າຍແທັບນັ້ນ ແລະ ແທັບທັງໝົດທີ່ຢູ່ເບື້ອງຂວາຂອງມັນ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ໄລຍະຫ່າງລະຫວ່າງແທັບເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນປ່ຽນແປງຕາມສັດສ່ວນຂອງໄລຍະຫ່າງຈາກຂອບ."

#. auJot
#: tabs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tabs.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146146\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Changing the Properties of Tabs"
msgstr "ການປ່ຽນຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງແທັບ"

#. r6Bhd
#: tabs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tabs.xhp\n"
"par_id3145646\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To change tab type, click the tab you want to change on the ruler, then right-click to open the context menu."
msgstr "ເພື່ອປ່ຽນປະເພດແທັບ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໃສ່ແທັບທີ່ຕ້ອງການປ່ຽນເທິງໄມ້ບັນທັດ, ແລ້ວຄລິກຂວາເພື່ອເປີດເມນູລັດ."

#. aS2C9
#: tabs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tabs.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154729\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Deleting Tabs"
msgstr "ການລຶບແທັບ"

#. AzsqF
#: tabs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"tabs.xhp\n"
"par_id3148879\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To delete a tab, hold down the mouse button while you drag the tab outside the ruler."
msgstr "ເພື່ອລຶບແທັບ, ໃຫ້ກົດປຸ່ມເມົາສ໌ຄ້າງໄວ້ແລ້ວລາກແທັບນັ້ນອອກໄປນອກໄມ້ບັນທັດ."

