#. H2oiU
#: usingthemes.xhp
msgctxt ""
"usingthemes.xhp\n"
"par_id511691113013612\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Format the document using the fixed theme attribute name such as colors, fonts and other format settings."
msgstr "ຈັດຮູບແບບເອກະສານໂດຍໃຊ້ຊື່ຄຸນລັກສະນະທີມທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ ເຊັ່ນ: ສີ, ຟອນ ແລະ ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຮູບແບບອື່ນໆ."

