"par_idN109E0\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Create an XSLT transformation <emph>stylesheet</emph> that maps the elements of the external XML format to the elements of the OpenDocument XML file format and back again."
msgstr "ສ້າງ XSLT transformation <emph>stylesheet</emph> ທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງອົງປະກອບຂອງຮູບແບບ XML ພາຍນອກກັບອົງປະກອບຂອງຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ OpenDocument XML ໄປ ແລະ ກັບ."

#. Eh2JN
#: xsltfilter_create.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xsltfilter_create.xhp\n"
"par_idN109E8\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Create a template that assigns %PRODUCTNAME styles to elements in the external XML format when you import a file in this format into %PRODUCTNAME."
msgstr "ສ້າງແມ່ແບບທີ່ກຳນົດສະໄຕລ໌ຂອງ %PRODUCTNAME ໃຫ້ກັບອົງປະກອບໃນຮູບແບບ XML ພາຍນອກ ເມື່ອທ່ານນຳເຂົ້າໄຟລ໌ໃນຮູບແບບນີ້ເຂົ້າໃນ %PRODUCTNAME."

#. cbKGc
#: xsltfilter_create.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xsltfilter_create.xhp\n"
"par_idN109EC\n"
"help.text"
