msgstr "ຕົວລະບຸນີ້ນຳໃຊ້ເພື່ອລະບຸປະເພດໄຟລ໌ຕອນນຳເຂົ້າ."

#. ervud
#: xsltfilter_create.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xsltfilter_create.xhp\n"
"par_idN10A32\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>XSLT for export</emph> box, enter the path and file name of the XSLT stylesheet that defines the transformation from OpenDocument format to the external format."
msgstr "ໃນກ່ອງ <emph>XSLT ສຳລັບການສົ່ງອອກ</emph>, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນເສັ້ນທາງ ແລະ ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຂອງ XSLT stylesheet ທີ່ກຳນົດການແປງຈາກຮູບແບບ OpenDocument ໄປຫາຮູບແບບພາຍນອກ."

#. X6FE5
#: xsltfilter_create.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xsltfilter_create.xhp\n"
"par_idN10A38\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>XSLT for import</emph> box, enter the path and file name to the XSLT stylesheet that defines the transformation from the external format to OpenDocument format."
msgstr "ໃນກ່ອງ <emph>XSLT ສຳລັບການນຳເຂົ້າ</emph>, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນເສັ້ນທາງ ແລະ ຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຂອງ XSLT stylesheet ທີ່ກຳນົດການແປງຈາກຮູບແບບພາຍນອກໄປຫາຮູບແບບ OpenDocument."

#. 3JnjC
#: xsltfilter_create.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xsltfilter_create.xhp\n"
"par_idN10A3E\n"
"help.text"
msgid "(Optional) In the <emph>Template for import</emph> box, enter the path and name of the template that defines the %PRODUCTNAME styles that are used in the imported file."
msgstr "(ທາງເລືອກ) ໃນກ່ອງ <emph>ແມ່ແບບສຳລັບການນຳເຂົ້າ</emph>, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນເສັ້ນທາງ ແລະ ຊື່ຂອງແມ່ແບບທີ່ກຳນົດສະໄຕລ໌ຂອງ %PRODUCTNAME ທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ໃນໄຟລ໌ທີ່ນຳເຂົ້າ."

#. AdBLL
#: xsltfilter_create.xhp
